(711, 'exs5av-swdw', NULL, '\"Take Charge\" : By Gaurav Marya, Group Chairman, Franchise India', 30, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Less than 200 pages of lucid text will empower you with the attitude needed to build a growth fantasy! Entrepreneurship is a mental attitude - a mindset. It is the sense of responsibility that comes from the ownership of an enterprise. We are talking about intellectual and emotional ownership, not mere legal ownership. An entrepreneur mindset is about owning our dreams, our flights of fancy. We need to picture our castles-in-the-air completely, smell our khayali pulao, and then discover the means of making it come true. A big fantasy with a feasible action plan is vision. The vision gives us the courage to own the risk and the generosity to share the rewards of our enterprise. When this vision engages the individual members of our team, a conviction runs through our enterprise. It is conviction and integrity that builds the dream team. takecharge! is about owning a dream and making it a realityrntakecharge! is about how to build a team that works for the vision of one that\\\'s shared by all. takecharge! is about 10 Entrepreneur Mindset Strategies that will build excellence in enterpriserntakecharge! is about the attitude that powered Vijay Kumar to tell Mr R K Gupta, \\\"Meh paanch lakh ka sauda karne aaya hoon, aur meri jaib meh paanch phuti kaudiya bhi nahin hai (I have come to do a deal for five hundred thousand rupees, when I don\\\'t even have five busted bits in my pocket)\\\" (Trishul, 1978) takecharge! challenges the reader to demand more from the self and always look higher!rnrnThe closest thing to a born entrepreneur, Gaurav Marya started his first enterprise at the age of 16. Over the years he has started and sold more than a dozen more. The businesses ranged from mobile phones, career advisory, restaurants to the entertainment business. It was at the age of 24 that he found the focus that allowed him to retain his variety of interests in a successful manner. During a trip to the US in 1998, he saw how franchising had impacted the business scene there. He recognized that franchising was the fastest way of building entrepreneurship. In 1999 Gaurav set up Franchise India, which is today the largest integrated franchise and retail solution company in Asia.', 'entrepreneur business Gaurav Marya franchise ', '9.05', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 5, 7762, 'A', '2012-11-21 16:44:21', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(712, 'Wkq9B_XOnFA', NULL, 'Bala R Girisaballa at Small Business Congress 2010', 32, '', NULL, '', 0, 'SMALL BUSINESS CONGRESS 2010', 'SMALL BUSINESS CONGRESS entrepreneur ', '2.05', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 3, 2121, 'A', '2012-11-21 16:48:16', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(714, 'YFo3DlAlkAs', NULL, 'Vikash Mittal at Indian Restaurant Congress 2012', 31, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Indian Restaurant Congress 2012\r\n\r\nIndia`s Biggest National Restaurant forum in its 2nd edition focusing all the Restaurant professionals, Owners , Operators and stake holders from Restaurant industry to have a deliberate discussion on the growth of Restaurant Business in India. To discuss on the real time challenges ( in terms of Operation and financials ), imbibing best industry practices, Restaurant Franchising Know how, Networking with the industry people and to give recognition.\r\n\r\n\r\nThe Indian Restaurant Congress brought together key representatives from the food service industry, trade bodies and associations, design professionals, product development companies, manufacturers, policy makers, investment groups and other stakeholders from the restaurant supplies and food industry.', 'Restaurant, business, congress, food, awards, eat out, entrepreneur, cuisine, 2012,', '4.52', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 5384, 'A', '2012-11-23 11:37:21', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(715, '6ixThYFyGsg', NULL, 'Vikash Arora at Indian Restaurant Congress 2012', 31, '', NULL, '', 0, 'India`s Biggest National Restaurant forum in its 2nd edition focusing all the Restaurant professionals, Owners, Operators and stake holders from Restaurant industry to have a deliberate discussion on the growth of Restaurant Business in India. To discuss on the real time challenges ( in terms of Operation and financials ), imbibing best industry practices, Restaurant Franchising Know how, Networking with the industry people and to give recognition.\r\n\r\n\r\nThe Indian Restaurant Congress brought together key representatives from the food service industry, trade bodies and associations, design professionals, product development companies, manufacturers, policy makers, investment groups and other stakeholders from the restaurant supplies and food industry.', 'Restaurant, business, congress, food, awards, eat out, entrepreneur, cuisine, 2012,', '4.36', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 6025, 'A', '2012-11-23 11:39:11', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(716, 'JBDLFiF5FCg', NULL, 'Venkatraman Girish at Indian Restaurant Congress 2012', 31, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Indian Restaurant Congress 2012\r\n\r\nIndia`s Biggest National Restaurant forum in its 2nd edition focusing all the Restaurant professionals, Owners , Operators and stake holders from Restaurant industry to have a deliberate discussion on the growth of Restaurant Business in India. To discuss on the real time challenges ( in terms of Operation and financials ), imbibing best industry practices, Restaurant Franchising Know how, Networking with the industry people and to give recognition.\r\n\r\n\r\nThe Indian Restaurant Congress brought together key representatives from the food service industry, trade bodies and associations, design professionals, product development companies, manufacturers, policy makers, investment groups and other stakeholders from the restaurant supplies and food industry.', 'Restaurant, business, congress, food, awards, eat out, entrepreneur, cuisine, 2012,', '4.28', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 6000, 'A', '2012-11-23 11:40:52', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(30, 'hrEeG0wH6XQ', NULL, 'Efficiency in retail', 2, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Mr. Hemachnadra Jaweri, MD, Forum Synergy talks at FI2009 about how everyone in retail industry went on an expansion aggressively in last few years, and then fell flat on their faces. Unnecessary expansion made them loose all of their money; the only thing that matters is efficiency in retail industry is being spoken of. The only thing that matters in retail efficiency is \\\'single store profitability\\\'. ', 'Franchise Retail Business', '10:07', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2520, 'A', '2010-03-18 06:06:41', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(31, 'vLlxdfIQKJ4', NULL, 'Getting your brand ready', 2, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Nicholas Bloom, AVP, Beenstalk discussed about his company\\\'s profile not only in India but globally at FI2009, a popular business conference. He talked about the presence, development and key achievements of his company. Later he shifted his discussion totally towards licensing which is the new and growing business format in India that now interests a lot of people.', 'brand building, branding strategy, branding your company, Nicholas Bloom, Beanstalk brand licensing services, how to franchise, business startup, franchise India 2009, business conference, business seminar, FI2009', '8:22', 'V', NULL, 'en', 2, 2, 6, 3079, 'A', '2010-03-18 06:08:55', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(717, 'CaE9doQQ9cQ', NULL, 'Sunil Kapur at Indian Restaurant Congress 2012', 31, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Indian Restaurant Congress 2012\r\n\r\nIndia`s Biggest National Restaurant forum in its 2nd edition focusing all the Restaurant professionals, Owners , Operators and stake holders from Restaurant industry to have a deliberate discussion on the growth of Restaurant Business in India. To discuss on the real time challenges ( in terms of Operation and financials ), imbibing best industry practices, Restaurant Franchising Know how, Networking with the industry people and to give recognition.\r\n\r\n\r\nThe Indian Restaurant Congress brought together key representatives from the food service industry, trade bodies and associations, design professionals, product development companies, manufacturers, policy makers, investment groups and other stakeholders from the restaurant supplies and food industry.', 'Restaurant, business, congress, food, awards, eat out, entrepreneur, cuisine, 2012,', '5.29', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 5523, 'A', '2012-11-23 11:42:09', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(33, 'vjxtCx5rRTc', NULL, 'The location strategy', 2, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Mr. Kush Medhore, CEO, EWDPL disagrees with the normal notion that people have about India that its population is a bane, according to him it’s a boon and allows us a good consumer base. While talking about location strategy at FI2009 business event, he gave an example that how 15 yrs back South Ex wasn\\\'t a good place to have a store but now it’s the best, so you need to know where will your consumer be in the coming years than where is it now. At FI2009 Mr. Kush Medhore also shared with the attendees about many of his retail career experiences. ', 'location strategy, location strategy for business, location strategy in retail, Kush Medhore, ewdpl retail offer, how to franchise, business startup, franchise India 2009, business entrepreneurship, business conference, business seminar, FI2009', '6:31', 'V', NULL, 'en', 4, 4, 11, 4077, 'A', '2010-03-18 06:12:39', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(35, 'zS-BBVSdcI0', NULL, 'Franchising business an option for the young ', 1, '', NULL, '', 0, 'McDonalds Franchising is the best business option for those who don\\\'t want to start a business from scratch. As per Gaurav Marya, President of Franchise India Holdings Ltd., \\\"Franchising is possible for McDonalds as its business model could be efficiently duplicated in other geographical locations and even an 18 year old can manage an outlet.', 'McDonalds franchising,  Gaurav Marya, Franchise India, franchising, business model', '4:40', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 2, 451, 'D', '2010-10-23 05:27:27', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(36, 'UtzsZ55guuw', NULL, 'Franchise India Awards 2008 ', 1, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Franchise Awards’08 where franchisors from different business sector, are facilitated for their excellent business concepts and quality work.  ', 'Franchise Business Retail Awards', '7:57', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 4, 149, 'D', '2010-10-23 05:28:43', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(37, 'rusNV0JrcAs', NULL, 'Star cricketer sells his name', 1, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Harbhajan Singh – the star cricketer of Indian team, has joined hands with License India who will use his name to sell products. Gaurav Marya, License India, says, \\\"He is the first sports person who has taken licensing very seriously\\\".', 'Harbhajan Singh, brand licensing, License India, Gaurav Marya, Franchise India', '1:14', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 2, 246, 'D', '2010-10-23 05:30:15', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(38, 'v-_3_LANWI0', NULL, 'Licensing by Harbhajan Singh', 1, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Indian cricketer Harbhajan Singh sold licensing rights to his name as a brand to Delhi-based License India for an undisclosed sum. Now his name will be used in various types of merchandise and even in chain of restaurants as ‘Bhajji Da Dhaba’.', 'Harbhajan Singh, brand licensing, License India, Gaurav Marya, Franchise India', '2:45', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 80, 'D', '2010-10-23 05:37:24', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(39, 'uXeza_sI8wY', NULL, 'Harbhajan Singh becomes brand Harbhajan ', 1, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Gaurav Marya’s company License India would explore avenues to design and develop the brand ‘Harbhajan’ with established firms in the field of merchandise, manufacturing and retail, besides franchise operators. Harbhajan Singh is the first cricketer to have signed a licensing agreement with License India.', 'Franchise Business Entrepreneur Retail Business Opportunity', '1:17', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 77, 'D', '2010-10-23 05:38:21', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(40, 'IMS66s_wAE8', NULL, 'Bhajji and licensing', 1, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Harbhajan Singh has found a unique way to market his brand with License India. The firm will be using the “Harbhajan” brand name for merchandise, retail marketing and various accessories. ', 'Harbhajan Singh, brand licensing, License India, Gaurav Marya, Franchise India', '1:17', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 3, 66, 'D', '2010-10-23 05:39:08', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(41, 'Zv5Z1rAwbBI', NULL, 'FRO 2009 ', 1, '', NULL, '', 0, 'FRO2009- 17th India\\\'s Biggest Multi-city Franchise & Retail Show is a place where both investors and Franchise owners can get benefited in many ways.  Today, franchising is looked upon as the best way to expand a popular business format by business owners and investors find it a better way to enter the business world. ', 'Franchise Business Entrepreneur Retail Business Opportunity FRO', '2:04', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 3, 77, 'D', '2010-10-23 05:39:47', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(42, 'rjLt2BK5tGk', NULL, 'A report on Franchise Business ', 1, '', NULL, '', 0, 'In India, the concept of franchising in different business sectors is getting popular day by day. According to Gaurav Marya, President, Franchise India Holdings Ltd., believes that franchising is a better option for unemployed people.', 'Franchise Business Entrepreneur Retail Business Opportunity', '4:00', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 2, 345, 'D', '2010-10-23 05:40:33', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
