(48, '8T7pXAkK7jM', NULL, 'Franchise India 2010 – International Franchise & Retail Show', 1, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Franchise India 2010 Show was held on Dec 11-12, 2010 at Hotel Ashok, New Delhi, It was a business opportunity show for someone looking to start the business and looking for business expansions. Here delegates meet experts and have talked with business owners face to face in one place and explored business concepts and ideas. For more please visit: www.franchiseindia.com', 'franchise india, business opportunity, business expansions, business concepts, business ideas, start business, franchising, retailing, licensing', '0:45', 'V', NULL, 'en', 4, 4, 11, 4146, 'A', '2011-01-13 05:45:03', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
