(667, 'kS3BagAXVMs', NULL, 'Craig A Rogerson : Chemtura Corporation\r\n', 30, '', NULL, '', 0, 'US company Chemtura Corporation to strengthen its presence in Asia through acquisition. Deal struck with Solaris ChemTech in India. Speciality chemicals provider Chemtura Corp is to create a new subsidiary headquartered in New Delhi, by acquiring the bromine assets of India\'s Solaris ChemTech Industries Ltd. They have entered into a business transfer agreement with Solaris ChemTech Industries Ltd and its parent company, Gautam Thapar-led Avantha Holdings Ltd, for the deal. The acquisition would further strengthen Chemtura\'s position in bromine, provide customers with increased security of supply through further diversification of its bromine supply and would also give access to substantial bromine reserves to fuel Chemtura\'s future global growth through increased access to a scarce natural resource. Chemtura Corporation, with a turnover of $3 billion, is a global manufacturer and marketer of specialty chemicals, agrochemicals and pool, spa and home care products.', 'franchise business', '14.06', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 108, 'D', '2012-11-19 13:38:15', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(740, 'GzLkAHRdKGE', NULL, 'Anil Sinha at Indian Education Congress 2011', 28, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Anil Sinha speaking on the Indian Education Congress 2011 stated that the mandate  of the IFC is to promote  inclusive growth in developing countries through the private sector. He stated in the year 2010, 18 billion US dollar was invested in the private sector by IFC. India being one of the largest portfolios for IFC, 1 billion dollar is invested in the private sector of India every year. In the education sector there is an increasing trend of different models coming through and these models could be captured in the education industry acclaimed Anil. The benefits of India trying to capture the education sector with the private dominance is very fruitful with the technological base and entrepreneurial ship ability ootimised Anil.', 'franchise education congress entrepreneur', '2.37', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3841, 'A', '2012-11-26 10:57:34', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
