(191, 'O9oLNjObLwc', NULL, 'Consumers should not be kept in dark : Ananta Singh Rahuvanshi of DLF ', 33, '', NULL, '', 0, 'While dealing with delay residential or retail projects, consumers should be shared information about the project. Lots of initiatives are to be taken, anything little thing which comes up there, every development that happens, anything new that happens, each and every one of these activities ...', 'Anantha Raghuvanshi DLF India Ltd retail initiatives retail industry retail consumers', '3:37', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 2, 4461, 'A', '2011-10-04 12:08:37', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
