(198, 'foiO4hcu9MM', NULL, 'Estate Awards 2011', 34, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Estate World Award gives the esteem, the due recognition and reward that beckons them. This is an initiative from the Franchise India bandwagon, which is here to ensure that the estate industry has the right attributes to grow further.', 'estate world industry Franchise India reward initiative', '12:28', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 3, 2262, 'A', '2011-10-18 15:42:08', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
