(327, 'N9ckDrjOF3I', NULL, 'A journey from a salesman to an entrepreneur', 30, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Speaking on the occasion of Entrepreneur India 2011, D.K.Jain stated the entrepreneur conclave is a platform which gives a very good opportunity to the younger generation. He said the connection and being a part of the entrepreneurial fraternity is needed today especially to the younger generation. He spoke about the product of India which is available in terms of renewable and non-renewable resources and how it could be used in the future and from a business perspective. He further encouraged the aspiring entrepreneur by giving an example how life was different in the 1950-1960, then opportunities was very difficult, the good news today for aspiring entrepreneurs is that with technology life has become easy and so also starting a business. With the experience D.K.Jain has he said that he wanted to act more as an advisor and said that he was born as a sales man and ended as an entrepreneur.', 'Franchise India,D.K. Jain, Entrepreneur India 2011, Business, Exhibition, Luxor Group', '04:58', 'V', NULL, 'en', 2, 2, 7, 3834, 'A', '2012-01-23 11:11:44', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(328, 'iBTA3XeYstY', NULL, 'Padmaja Ruparel at Entrepreneur India 2011', 30, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Padmaja Ruparel after attending the Entrepreneur India 2011 on being asked her experience about the opinion states the event was a good one and she met a lot of interesting entrepreneur wherein exchange of ideas was possible. The entrepreneurs who were present though at the early state of start up phase a lot of synergy stated Padamaja. She lauds this was a perfect meeting ground for Angel Network invests in early start up business and she is hopeful to takes things forward and connect the dots with the entrepreneur she met here. Further the networking bit with investors and venture capitals who were also present in the event made Entrepreneur India 2011 a thriving and a complete event asserted Padmaja.rnPadmaja Ruparel has a wide range of experience in starting and growing organizations related to IT, entrepreneurship & investing.Padmaja was part of the key team of Xansa India Ltd. Through the years, she moved across various roles in the company before exiting as Vice President – Corporate Communications. While in Xansa, she built the communications, media and advertising strategy of the company in India.She is the President of Indian Angel Network (IAN), India\\\'s first and now the largest group of business angels, comprising the who\\\'s who of successful entrepreneurs and dynamic CEOs from India and overseas. ', 'Franchise India, Padmaja Ruparel, Entrepreneur India 2011,Business, Exhibition ', '1.25', 'V', NULL, 'en', 2, 2, 7, 4771, 'A', '2012-01-23 11:23:13', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(329, 'lAHB8Ks5pUo', NULL, 'Pavan Vaish at Entrepreneur India 2011', 30, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Pavan Vaish speaking on Entrepreneur India 2011 stated he found many budding entrepreneurs in the event and the gathering was a very practical one.rnThe event had involvement of the audience to a great extend with the people charging there own life experiences and question-answer session making it an involved session. rn\\\" Today a lot more people are entrepreneurial , today people have a risk appetite, going back 10-15 years where there were only a hand full of career options today with internet, social media the options have opened up and awareness is tremendous. Today the youngsters are taking so much risk and that is the key , if one cannot take risk one cannot be an entrepreneur\\\", said PavanrnrnHe also about entrepreneur and quasi-entrepreneur , thought out exit strategy, continuity of the company. Entrepreneurs\\\' succeed more if they try to create something fantastic rather than focusing on creating money.rnPavan Vaish is currently the Global Chief Operating Officer & Board Member at UnitedLex Corporation, he earlier was the CEO at IBM Daksh Business Process Services and before that Director at Quadrant Infotech. A born entrepreneur with his past experience and education that of Harvard Business School, Stanford University and Carnegie Mellon University, he is one an independent business think tank of the country.rn', 'Franchise India, Pavan Vaish, Entrepreneur India 2011, Business, Exhibition ', '2.24', 'V', NULL, 'en', 5, 5, 18, 5640, 'A', '2012-01-23 11:30:16', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(330, 'Tp7l1VTOaV0', NULL, 'Rajiv Bajaj at Entrepreneur India 2011', 30, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Rajiv Bajaj speaking on Entrepreneur India 2011 stated : My role in the Board is particularly to spread out the message of Entrepreneurs Organisation ( EO is company run by Bajaj Group) through seminars such Entrepreneur India 2011. EO looks for good ideas and validation of those ideas and the scalability of the idea As a financer I manage the the budge of the organisation and work with various sponsors . Being a part of Bajaj Capital and second generation entrepreneur , I am very comfortable in such environment of a seminar . Each generation of entrepreneurs have different characteristics, in every talk , every interaction you pick up ideas, community of like minded people . When I joined the organisation it was from a company try and build an institution, from a 100 odd people to a a 500 people company. Today we are a 3500 company, I wanted to build an institution which further realises the scale of vision to achieve.', 'Franchise India Rajiv Bajaj Entrepreneur India 2011 Business Exhibition ', '2.43', 'V', NULL, 'en', 3, 3, 7, 4958, 'A', '2012-01-23 11:44:46', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(331, 'jyX0paC_6d4', NULL, 'Vandana Gandhi speaking on pre-school education in India', 28, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Vandana Gandhi speaking on Entrepreneur India 2011 stated : We are looking into expanding into India because so far we have expanded in the UAE and we have successful there so we are looking at the Indian market because everybody is coming to India now, so India is the new West of the world. The UAE school has been running for the last six years and we have got four branches in UAE. We follow the British curriculum, there is a strict pre-school guideline which the UK government provides to the pre-schools and they are inspected regularly . We have imbibed the guidelines , although we do not have the off-stead inspecting pre-schools, we wanted to set the bench mark very high from the beginning.', 'Franchise India Vandana Gandhi Entrepreneur 2011 Business British Orchard', '4.01', 'V', NULL, 'en', 2, 2, 6, 4674, 'A', '2012-01-23 11:54:05', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(332, 'WL7v9TFkGsc', NULL, 'Vikram Bakshi at Indian Restaurant Congress 2011', 31, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Franchise India Vikram Bakshi at Indian Restaurant Congress 2011 ', 'Franchise India Vikram Bakshi  Restaurant India 2011 Business Exhibition ', '3.29', 'V', NULL, 'en', 3, 3, 8, 2081, 'A', '2012-01-23 12:01:23', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(801, 'lR-Z4f8gb_w', NULL, '\\\'Beauty Salon Industry a 30,000 Cr. Industry\\\' : C.K. Kumaravel at Franchise India 2012', 27, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Franchise India 2012, the 10th edition of Asia\\\'s biggest Franchise & Retail exhibition held its Franchise Awards 2012 & Star Retailer Awards 2012 on 4th November, 2012 at Shangri La\\\'s Eros Hotel, New Delhi. The splendid show was attended by the biggest and the most reputed names in the franchise and retail industry. The highlight of the evening was Franchise India\\\'s unique CSR initiative for enabling \\\'Mompreneurship\\\' in India launched by Shilpa Shetty. Story telling by Neelesh Misra, famous for his Yaadon Ka Idiot Box made for an entertaining session at the event.rnrnFranchise Awards 2012 are India\\\'s Topmost Honour in Franchising. Benchmarking excellence, the Awards celebrated and acknowledged contribution to one of India\\\'s most dynamic industries. The winners were those organisations that have shown outstanding business acumen, passion and achievement of franchise businesses and thus achieved sustainable growth across India. They were judged by an independent panel of experts and supported by the Indian Franchise Association (IFA) & Entrepreneur India Advisors. Franchisors, Franchisees, Master Franchisees and Entrepreneurs all over India had applied for the Awards considered to be the industry\\\'s top accolade.rnrnStar Retailer Awards is the only Awards of its kind which celebrates the best in Indian retailing. It is a singular platform for everyone from independent entrepreneurial retailers to the largest supermarket groups. These Awards celebrated the outstanding achievements across the retail fraternity. rnrnThe corporate social responsibility initiative of Franchise India 2012 this year was to launch the \\\'Mompreneur\\\'. The objective was to create an enabling ecosystem that will empower women and get them to draw on their inherent strengths and also overlay business opportunities most suited for mothers. Actor cum business entrepreneur Shilpa Shetty who has recently become a mother herself was roped in to raise awareness for the need for moms to be in business. The event showcased over 300 mom-friendly business opportunities and was attended by more than 25,000 people.rnrnFranchise India Awards 2012 and Star Retailer Awards are the most credible and prestigious received. Taking the commitments forward, the awards this year acknowledged the best performances in the industry in various categories.', ' franchise, business, entrepreneur, congress, awards, 2012, www.franchiseindia.com, www.entreprenuerindia.com, Gaurav Marya, Sachin Marya,', '3.56', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 3, 6904, 'A', '2012-11-27 15:45:11', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(755, 'L8Um2MsW5gA', NULL, 'Public-Private Partnership in action', 28, '', NULL, '', 0, 'According to public sources the financial need, required to implement in Indian education system, is almost 1 lac 50 thousand corers. India\'s 11th 5 year plan had allocated of 12thousand 5 hundred corers for model schools initiatives. We are still left out by 50 to 60 thousand corers. A lot of the burden will have to be taken by the vocational training segment. To change a mindset, drop out student should be called up for vocational training.', 'franchise business education entrepreneur ', '2.31', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 1, 4961, 'A', '2012-11-26 11:29:53', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(756, 'o2f8RXz3Ucs', NULL, 'The Transforming Scenario of Vocational Education', 28, '', NULL, '', 0, 'We should be aware of the initiatives that the government t and the private sector are taking in to meet the aim of expansion of higher education.', 'franchise entrepreneur education business ', '2.29', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3302, 'A', '2012-11-26 11:31:07', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(335, 'zisyILIZ1hY', NULL, 'Prakash Kumar at Entrepreneur India 2011', 30, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Speaking at Entrepreneur India 2011, Prakash Kumar stated he found the event very interesting wherein the audience was very inquisitive. He was thrilled to see such an audience which wanted to learn so much. Despite his presentation being over for more than an hour the audiences were still asking questions to Prakash about various topics and concerns. Prakash further spoke on the functioning of SIDBI and the various schemes offered by it. He said that the business models are definitely important and track record is important wherein the banks would look for the balance sheet and IT returns and CIBEL score for the last three years, these details are of prime importance to secure a loan stated Prakash. The project which the bank would fund would be one which is highly viable; it need not be one with high growth and high risk however it should be one which is scalable. Overall the credit worthiness and the quantum of credit which the bank can trust the borrower should be one which has been handled with care.', 'Franchise India Prakash Kumar Entrepreneur India Business Exhibition ', '4.08', 'V', NULL, 'en', 2, 2, 6, 4869, 'A', '2012-01-23 12:25:23', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(336, 'SxhRu18Z6cY', NULL, 'Enterprise Auto Expo 2012 : Biennial International Event ', 1, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Over 50 global brands , one lakh visitors a day, around 1500 participants from 23 countries, more than 50 new cars launched and unveiled .Hatchbacks, Sedans, SUVs, ATVs, Electric Vehicles, hybrid cars and concept cars. This isn’t all about the largest Indian Automobile Fair. The 11th Auto Expo 2012 which was held in the city recently was a week-long affair organized by Automotive Component Manufacturers Association of India, Confederation of Indian Industry   and     Society of Indian Automobile Manufacturers. Global Giants such as Hyundai, Honda, Volkswagen, Fait, Renault, Audi, Tata, Chevrolet, Maruti Suzuki, Toyota, Mahindra, Skoda and BMW had their dominant presence. Franchise India brings to you the images from the 1st and 2nd day of this biennial International Event.', 'Franchise India, Auto Expo 2012, Biennial Event, International Event, Cars', '4.00', 'V', NULL, 'en', 2, 2, 6, 6497, 'A', '2012-01-23 12:44:29', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(337, '3QouWQ6yS6Y', NULL, 'Pioneer India leads car entertainment at Auto Expo 2012', 1, '', NULL, '', 0, 'When it comes to car audio, Pioneer is one of the leading names in the world. Pioneer’s car entertainment has it all be it car units, speakers, subwoofers, amplifiers and accessories and all latest technology accessories and several concept devices. \\r\\n\\r\\nFranchise India caught up with Pioneer India which is one of the biggest names in the car entertainment section. Pioneer India is the Indian Subsidiary of Pioneer Corporation, Japan. Its core business covers the car audio and video segments with a diversified range of products focusing on DVD players, home entertainment systems, speakers and car audio-visual solutions.\\r\\n\\r\\nSpeaking on the occasion, Gaurav stated that they are showcasing best of Pioneer’s technology in the Auto Expo 2012, with two of the latest car entertainment, one being Mixtrax. Mixtrax comprises of 53 products installed and works with 1700 volts, making it a DJ in itself. The second car uses SPL technology, which has two sub-buffers installed. Both these products exhibit Pioneer’s prominence in the market of the head unit in the car entertainment arena. \\r\\n\\r\\n', 'Tags: Franchise India, Gaurav Kulshrestha  , Pioneer India, Auto Expo 2012, Mixtrax ', '03:15', 'V', NULL, 'en', 4, 4, 10, 5693, 'A', '2012-01-24 11:49:32', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(338, 'IxJwiOlXkow', NULL, 'Bahamian - India business tie-up', 30, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Bertha M. Cooper-Rousseau a successful entrepreneur of Bahamans is here in India to see the likelihood of her business expansion. A keen learner, she states at present she is more interested learning as to how business happens in India and thereafter once done with the learning process she is eager to explore the Indian market. On being asked about the challenges faced by women, she asserts the challenges are the same, be it here or in the Bahamans. She also states that the presence of SME is very dominant in her country as well. Her visit to India at present is absolutely business oriented wherein she intends to meet legal partners and collaborative associates.', 'Bertha Cooper-Rousseau, Franchise India, Women Entrepreneur, Business', '03:10', 'V', NULL, 'en', 2, 2, 5, 3189, 'A', '2012-01-24 12:24:02', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(339, 'umpSM8L1QxM', NULL, 'Maruti Suzuki @ Auto Expo 2012', 1, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Maruti Suzuki @ Auto Expo 2012', 'Franchise India, Maruti Suzuki, Cars, Bikes, Auto Expo 2012', '02:07', 'V', NULL, 'en', 7, 7, 24, 4575, 'A', '2012-01-24 15:46:15', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(340, 'Q_2Ag6bhch4', NULL, 'Polaris @ Auto Expo 2012', 1, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Polaris Industries is a manufacturer of snowmobiles, ATV, and neighborhood electric vehicles. Polaris is based in Medina, Minnesota, USA. The company also manufactures motorcycles through its Victory Motorcycles subsidiary and through the Indian Motorcycle subsidiary which it purchased in April 2011. Polaris had a dominant presence at the Auto Expo 2012. Gul Panag, an Indian actor and model was thrilled driving the Polaris ATV.', 'Franchise India, Polaris, ATVs, Gul Panag, Polaris India', '1:51', 'V', NULL, 'en', 2, 2, 6, 2717, 'D', '2012-01-25 11:30:42', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(342, '0tGx3oZ_HhM', NULL, 'SME : India International Trade Fair 2011', 1, '', NULL, '', 0, 'The 31st edition of the popular annual mega trade fair, the India International Trade Fair (IITF), was held at Pragati Maidan, New Delhi from November 14 to 27, 2011. IITF is the largest incorporated Trade Fair with both B2B and B2C components. This event was thronged with a large presence of the SME sector of India. India\'s global presence had its initiation long time back with the prominent contribution of the Micro, Small and Medium Entrepreneurs\' of India. It has proved that was, it is and it shall remain the \'Backbone of India\'.', 'Franchise India, Sapna Bhardwaj, SME IITF Franchise India Small Business \"Small And Medium Enterprises\" Franchising Success', '4.00', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 134, 'D', '2012-02-14 11:41:44', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(343, '2AeunBqi4gw', NULL, 'SME:India International Trade Fair 2011', 30, '', NULL, '', 0, 'The 31st edition of the popular annual mega trade fair, the India International Trade Fair (IITF), was held at Pragati Maidan, New Delhi from November 14 to 27, 2011. IITF is the largest incorporated Trade Fair with both B2B and B2C components. This event was thronged with a large presence of the SME sector of India. India\\\'s global presence had its initiation long time back with the prominent contribution of the Micro, Small and Medium Entrepreneurs\\\' of India. It has proved that was, it is and it shall remain the \\\'Backbone of India\\\'.', 'Franchise India SME, India International Trade Fair, Pragati Maidan', '5.59', 'V', NULL, 'en', 2, 2, 3, 1950, 'D', '2012-02-14 11:50:45', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(344, 'F8pOkx54FFc', NULL, 'When sports becomes religion', 2, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Established in 1977, Kelme was the equipment sponsor of the Spanish Olympic team in 1992 Barcelona Olympic Games. The brand is present in 45 countries worldwide and truly represents sports.', 'Kelme Luca Gios sports spanish Barcelona', '3:57', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 2, 3250, 'A', '2012-02-29 12:31:33', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(345, 'o08T5ny9bFQ', NULL, 'Craving the delicacies', 31, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Chicking Fried Chicken was established in the United Arab Emirates in 2000.Chicking Fried Chicken has over 85 outlets in 14 Countries across the world. With more than 25 outlets in the southern region, the brand has made its foray into the North.', 'Chicking UAE chicken north India', '3:43', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 4, 1989, 'A', '2012-02-29 12:32:25', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
