(356, '_rBpwP94jF8', NULL, 'Indian eRetail Congress 2012', 29, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Franchise India in association with Gitanjali presented eRetail Congress 2012. The two day conference saw industry veterans from across the country discussing the power of retail through mobile commerce, e-marketing and web merchandising. The event provided e-retailers with a platform to showcase their products and services and also help them connect with key policy-makers of the industry. The event had key speakers, retailers, vendors and supplierssh are their experiences and promote innovation to capture consumer interest in the segment. Special awards was presented to those who have created path breaking trends and have led unprecedented innovations towards uplifting the morale of the entire eRetail Industry.', 'Franchise India, eRetail, online market,consumption, trends online, Peyush Bansal, Valyoo Technologies', '16.54', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 3, 5857, 'A', '2012-03-07 10:49:54', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
