(967, 'aFYT3utz69Y', NULL, 'Jagdeep Kapoor speaking at Estate Awards 2012 ', 3, '', NULL, '', 20, '4th Annual Biggest Real Estate Awards for Developers and Brokers.rnEstate Summit & Awards 2012 presented by Franchise India & Orbit. The 4th edition of the Estate Summit & Awards 2012 reunites the thought leaders of yesterday, and brings to the dais visionaries who have been front runners of this changing era of real estate dynamics together. The summit and awards will bring together a great lineage of developers, property brands, real estate professionals, urban planners, architects, designers, policy makers, government officials and brokers to explore best practices and strategies to best utilise the investment strength of the Indian buyer.', 'franchise, business, entrepreneur, retail', '8.31', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3637, 'A', '2013-01-10 16:19:24', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
