(370, 'Vp-x6e-yVKk', NULL, 'Consciousness to Education ', 3, '', NULL, '', 0, 'S. Chand is India\'s leading publishing company with unmatched market leadership over 7 decades. “Bringing people and knowledge together\" is core to the mission of S. Chand Group and this has translated into \'Empowering Minds\'. S. Chand Books have touched three generations of Indian educated community. Today S. Chand needs no introduction. Its continuous commitment and endeavor of publishing quality books and meeting the needs right from primary level books to higher academic books in Engineering, Management, Commerce, Basic Sciences and others has built unmatched equity.', 'Franchise India, Education Congress 2011, Amit Gupta, S. Chand Books, Publishing, Books, Schools, Education Sector ', '1.15', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 255, 'D', '2012-03-23 15:14:54', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(799, 'CY9vxG1QxDE', NULL, 'Vikram Bakshi of McDonalds India at Franchise India 2012', 35, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Franchise India 2012, the 10th edition of Asia\\\'s biggest Franchise & Retail exhibition held its Franchise Awards 2012 & Star Retailer Awards 2012 on 4th November, 2012 at Shangri La\\\'s Eros Hotel, New Delhi. The splendid show was attended by the biggest and the most reputed names in the franchise and retail industry. The highlight of the evening was Franchise India\\\'s unique CSR initiative for enabling \\\'Mompreneurship\\\' in India launched by Shilpa Shetty. Story telling by Neelesh Misra, famous for his Yaadon Ka Idiot Box made for an entertaining session at the event.rnrnFranchise Awards 2012 are India\\\'s Topmost Honour in Franchising. Benchmarking excellence, the Awards celebrated and acknowledged contribution to one of India\\\'s most dynamic industries. The winners were those organisations that have shown outstanding business acumen, passion and achievement of franchise businesses and thus achieved sustainable growth across India. They were judged by an independent panel of experts and supported by the Indian Franchise Association (IFA) & Entrepreneur India Advisors. Franchisors, Franchisees, Master Franchisees and Entrepreneurs all over India had applied for the Awards considered to be the industry\\\'s top accolade.rnrnStar Retailer Awards is the only Awards of its kind which celebrates the best in Indian retailing. It is a singular platform for everyone from independent entrepreneurial retailers to the largest supermarket groups. These Awards celebrated the outstanding achievements across the retail fraternity. rnrnThe corporate social responsibility initiative of Franchise India 2012 this year was to launch the \\\'Mompreneur\\\'. The objective was to create an enabling ecosystem that will empower women and get them to draw on their inherent strengths and also overlay business opportunities most suited for mothers. Actor cum business entrepreneur Shilpa Shetty who has recently become a mother herself was roped in to raise awareness for the need for moms to be in business. The event showcased over 300 mom-friendly business opportunities and was attended by more than 25,000 people.rnrnFranchise India Awards 2012 and Star Retailer Awards are the most credible and prestigious received. Taking the commitments forward, the awards this year acknowledged the best performances in the industry in various categories.', 'franchise business entrepreneur ', '1.11', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 4, 6474, 'A', '2012-11-27 12:22:18', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(794, 'VM2_cZMrA6M', NULL, 'Momir Popovic of Rexair LLC, USA at Franchise India 2012', 35, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Franchise India 2012, the 10th edition of Asia\\\'s biggest Franchise & Retail exhibition held its Franchise Awards 2012 & Star Retailer Awards 2012 on 4th November, 2012 at Shangri La\\\'s Eros Hotel, New Delhi. The splendid show was attended by the biggest and the most reputed names in the franchise and retail industry. The highlight of the evening was Franchise India\\\'s unique CSR initiative for enabling \\\'Mompreneurship\\\' in India launched by Shilpa Shetty. Story telling by Neelesh Misra, famous for his Yaadon Ka Idiot Box made for an entertaining session at the event.rn', 'Franchise, education, congress, business, entrepreneur, 2012, awards, congress, Franchise India 2012, Sachin Marya, Business,', '1.39', 'V', NULL, 'en', 2, 2, 8, 4734, 'A', '2012-11-26 17:57:34', NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, 0),
(376, 'K_-BKPe26HE', NULL, 'Indian Salon Congress 2012: The Beauty Forecast 2012', 27, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Indian Salon Congress 2012 organised by Franchise India and Naturals was a successful conclave with a complete networking aide and business solutions and awareness to the new trends in the Salon and Spa Industry of India.Prominent players in the industry as well as the aspiring entrepreneurs venturing out proved their learning edge by their presence in this two day national event. This industry is reported to have a growth of 30% year on year and is one which will boom very well, stated Samarendra Sahu, official of the esteemed MSME Ministry.  The conference was thronged with the imminent figures in the Salon and Spa industry of India.', 'Franchise India, CK Kumaravel, Naturals, Sandeep Ahuja, VLCC, Samarendra Sahu, MSME', '11.15', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 3, 4825, 'A', '2012-03-29 13:12:43', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
