(859, 'LoWJgRrEkS4', NULL, 'Economics of Retailing for Salons : Building Products with Services', 27, '', NULL, '', 0, 'The Salon Congress 2012 is presented by Franchise India and UTV Bloomberg with Entrepreneur India Advisors as the knowledge partners and Indian Franchise Association (IFA) as supporting partners. It is a first time projection by Franchise India to conduct Salon Congress that will take note of the robust growth in the salon industry and in lieu of matching up with the international counterparts to come together and deliberate on the pertinent points of getting finances, retaining skilled personnel, bringing in standardisation in processes, creating quality consistency and more through the course of this two day comprehensive conference. The show brought forward a great networking opportunity that aims to strengthen industry connections.\r\nIndian Salon Congress 2012, a two day conference brought together industry veterans to interact and draw attention to best practices and promote innovation to capture consumer interest that will help grow the beauty services sector. The Expo 2012 will be a showcase and branding opportunity for your product or services operating in the beauty services segment, connecting with suppliers and other allied industries. Indian Salon Awards 2012 acknowledged contribution of market leaders and innovators from the beauty services industry.', 'Franchise, Business, Entrepreneur, Salon, Congress, 2012, spa, Indian Salon Congress 2012, Beauty, Salon, Grooming, Personal Grooming, Hair, Skin, www.franchiseindia.com, video.franchiseindia.com,', '21.33', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 4, 8379, 'A', '2012-11-30 11:52:08', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
