mothers. Actor cum business entrepreneur Shilpa Shetty who has recently become a mother herself was roped in to raise awareness for the need for moms to be in business. The event showcased over 300 mom-friendly business opportunities and was attended by more than 25,000 people.rnrnFranchise India Awards 2012 and Star Retailer Awards are the most credible and prestigious received. Taking the commitments forward, the awards this year acknowledged the best performances in the industry in various categories.', 'India Gets Business, A business for every Indian, Franchise, business, entrepreneur, awards, congress, 2012, Franchise India 2012, India, MSME, MNC, ', '6.54', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 6484, 'A', '2012-12-01 17:18:34', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
