(1002, 'wWMFO21gTdQ', NULL, 'Increase Business Profitability by 100% : Rahul Jain, CEO, Business Coaching India ', 30, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Rahul Jain is a professional with over 17 years’ hands-on experience with blue chip companies such as Tata Motors and then as a serial entrepreneur. rnHe conceptualised Business Coaching India in 2004 - Over the last 8 years, he has coached more than 100 business owners, across all verticals.rnMr. Jain has a wide range of experience in diverse industries and products ranging from training, manufacturing, insurance, direct sales, designing, to setting up distribution and retail channels.rn', 'franchise, business, entrepreneur ', '7.55', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 699, 'D', '2013-01-28 13:20:59', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
