(845, 'RxW5naTjUfU', NULL, 'Tiago Marques of Kider : In-Store Asia 2012', 1, '', NULL, '', 0, 'In store Asia 2012, is an annual Retail Design event which was held at FRDC sweeping major design awards at Pragati Maidan, New Delhi on 17th Feb 2012rn rnIn-Store Asia Expo has grown by 60%, and with Indian retail experiencing unprecedented growth, it is expected to grow tremendously further on. As with every passing day there are a million needs that crop up in the retail solutions and services space. The Expo at In-Store Asia is the platform where all the needs of brands and retailers, find an answer and an opportunity where exhibitors bag businesses that help them take the huge leap.rn rnThe Expo at In-Store Asia is of world-class, state-of-the-art retail solutions, services, technologies and ideas come together. It promises a holistic experience with its five distinct pavilions -- Absolute POP, Retail Signs, VM & Store Fix, Dynamic Environments and Designers Den. Each of these pavilions offers a comprehensive range of solutions and expertise. Alongside the five pavilions is the material lounge that showcases the latest and the best in the field of materials.rn rnThis year 2012, the expo witnessed 3500 visitors, 1800 sq. mt. of Expo space and more than 80 exhibitors of which 40% were new participants.', 'Franchise, business, entrepreneur, In-Store Asia 2012, 2012, Pragati Maidan,', '2.01', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 4454, 'A', '2012-11-28 16:11:14', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
