(1097, 'I2v14aBY-Ic', NULL, 'Do\'s and Don\'ts in the Salon Business', 9, '', NULL, '', 42, 'Franchise India - Asia\\\\\\\'s largest integrated franchise solution company held the annual Indian Salon Congress 2013 at the Claridges, Surajkund on 24th & 25th March, 2013. This event provided a direct B2B engagement to many Indian leading beauty retailers combining inspiration, education and wisdom from some of the most innovative thinkers. The Conference brought forward a great networking opportunity that aims to strengthen and organize the industry connections. Over 50 of the industry\\\\\\\'s most dynamic, thoughtful and inspirational speakers not only shared their valuable insights but also presented working visionary strategies to help the beauty and salon industry merge with the business.', 'franchise, business, entrepreneur, salon, beauty, ', '6.20', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 4219, 'A', '2013-04-04 12:43:39', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
