(1102, 'OZEzWpa6pJs', NULL, 'What it takes for your own Brand to win at the Beauty Game ', 9, '', NULL, '', 42, 'Indian Salon Congress 2013 organised by Franchise India\\r\\nFranchise India - Asia\\\\\\\'s largest integrated franchise solution company held the annual Indian Salon Congress 2013 at the Claridges, Surajkund on 24th & 25th March, 2013. This event provided a direct B2B engagement to many Indian leading beauty retailers combining inspiration, education and wisdom from some of the most innovative thinkers. The Conference brought forward a great networking opportunity that aims to strengthen and organize the industry connections. Over 50 of the industry\\\\\\\'s most dynamic, thoughtful and inspirational speakers not only shared their valuable insights but also presented working visionary strategies to help the beauty and salon industry merge with the business.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe first day\\\\\\\'s sessions focused on the current state of the Beauty Industry including key speakers on the panel like Jawed Habib, Chairman, Jawed Habib Hair Hair & Beauty Ltd. and C. K. Kumaravel, Managing Director, Naturals Beauty Salon India Pvt. Ltd.  Pushkaraj Shenai,CEO,Lakme Lever, Sachin Kamat, Director, Enrich Salons & Academy, Murali Sundar, Country Manager, Schwarzkopf Professional and Dr. Arvind Poswal, Founder, Dr. A\\\\\\\'s Clinic shed light on the Men\\\\\\\'s grooming market and its Trends, Opportunities and Strategies. Samantha Kochhar, Managing Director, Blossom Kochhar Group of Companies, Sandeep Ahuja, Managing Director, VLCC Health Care Ltd identified the key formulas for a brand to win from a business perspective.', 'franchise, business, entrepreneur', '15.01', 'V', NULL, 'en', 2, 2, 6, 5812, 'A', '2013-04-09 12:27:21', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
