(1125, 'P9tf4M-5X40', NULL, 'Indian Salon Awards 2013 - Part I ', 9, '', NULL, '', 44, 'Franchise India - Asia\\\\\\\'s largest integrated franchise solution company held the annual Indian Salon Congress2013 at the Claridges, Surajkund on 24th & 25th March, 2013. This event provided a direct B2B engagement to many Indian leading beauty retailers combining inspiration, education and wisdom from some of the most innovative thinkers. The Conference brought forward a great networking opportunity that aims to strengthen and organize the industry connections. Over 50 of the industry\\\\\\\'s most dynamic, thoughtful and inspirational speakers not only shared their valuable insights but also presented working visionary strategies to help the beauty and salon industry merge with the business.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe Indian Salon Awards 2013 acknowledged the contribution of market leaders & innovators from the beauty services industry. Awardees received national recognition and extensive media coverage with the partners. Such recognition helped create awareness, and built cross industry association across various sectors covering finance, design and aesthetics, service aspects, merchandising, sourcing and marketing through brand building.\\r\\nSome of the key the awardees were: Jawed Habib who was honoured \\\\\\\'Salon of the Year Award\\\\\\\', Mr. C.K Kumaravel received the Entrepreneurial Excellence for Salon Leadership award and \\\\\\\"The Lifetime Achievement Award\\\\\\\" was given to Ahmed Habib.', 'Franchise, business, entrepreneur, retailer,salon, beauty', '7.18', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 3, 6308, 'A', '2013-04-15 12:09:00', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
