(1140, 'Ftaai4H4C8E', NULL, 'Success story : Sanjeev Gupta - The Man behind \\\\\\\'Albion Info Tel\\\\\\\'', 2, '1140.png', NULL, '', 14, 'Sanjeev started his career in IT industry and went on to become an entrepreneur in IT business. Today in his 17 years entrepreneurial carrier, he took up his current business from small scale unit to medium scale unit in IT industry.rnSanjeev is a seasoned entrepreneur in IT infrastructure and services space. He has spent more than two decades in venturing businesses in this industry. He started Albion in the year of 2000 and transformed it to a professional IT consulting, development and services company during past years. The company is considered leader in cloud services and managed support services space.rnSanjeev\\\\\\\'s incredible powers of leadership, integrity, ethics, honesty and professionalism have made his businesses high achievers in all respects. Albion strives for excellence, be it in product development, service delivery or corporate governance and it never lands up with the second best. This is the culture of superiority that has made this company outstanding. Under his leadership the Company has been awarded as \\\\\\\"Best Cloud Service Provider Nationally - 2012\\\\\\\" by CRN Magazine in second consecutive year. Recently, he has been entitled with chairmanship of IT Committee, PHD Chamber of Commerce & Industries.', 'IT, cloud computting,business, entrepreneur, retailer, business, venture, Albion, ', '8.53', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 5725, 'A', '2013-04-22 15:11:44', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1141, 'odEgUgkcrlA', NULL, 'Suman Jyoti Khaitan, President, PHD Chamber at IT investor\\\'s meet -Focus: Gwalior IT Park ', 2, '', NULL, '', 0, 'IT investor\\\'s meet -- Madhya Pradesh -- Focus: Gwalior IT Park. The state government has geared up to explore new possibilities of investments, availability of manpower and IT infrastructure required for the upcoming IT investments in Madhya Pradesh. Low cost of operations, cheaper land, availability of quality manpower, low cost of living and good social and physical infrastructure are few examples that will attract IT industries to invest in Madhya Pradesh said Mr. J. Satyanarayana, Secretary, Department of Electronics & Information Technology, Government of India in IT Investors Meet -- Experience Madhya Pradesh Focus: Gwalior Park organized by PHD Chamber of Commerce and Industry in Delhi.', 'franchise, business, entrepreneur', '4.15', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 5021, 'A', '2013-04-22 16:21:15', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1142, 'gJAl2nRTWU8', NULL, 'Sanjeev Gupta, Chairman IT Committee, PHD Chamber at IT investor\\\\\\\'s meet : Focus: Gwalior IT Park ', 2, '', NULL, '', 0, 'IT investor\\\\\\\'s meet -- Madhya Pradesh -- Focus: Gwalior IT Park \\r\\nThe state government has geared up to explore new possibilities of investments, availability of manpower and IT infrastructure required for the upcoming IT investments in Madhya Pradesh. \\r\\nLow cost of operations, cheaper land, availability of quality manpower, low cost of living and good social and physical infrastructure are few examples that will attract IT industries to invest in Madhya Pradesh said Mr. J. Satyanarayana, Secretary, Department of Electronics & Information Technology, Government of India in IT Investors Meet -- Experience Madhya Pradesh Focus: Gwalior Park organized by PHD Chamber of Commerce and Industry in Delhi.', 'franchise, business, entrepreneur', '05.03', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 5321, 'A', '2013-04-22 16:22:17', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
