(1240, 'lGb-XfA0TkA', NULL, 'Jitendra Tripathi Mani, DCP, Delhi Police at Entrepreneur India Awards 2013 ', 2, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Entrepreneur India Awards 2013: The 3rd Edition of Biggest Entrepreneurship awards in India. Entrepreneur India Awards 2013 recognized and felicitated Achievers, Innovators and Suppliers, who contributed significantly towards the development of Entrepreneurship in India.\\r\\nAward winners list : a\\r\\nEntrepreneur of the Year in Service Business - SCM & logistics Services: Mr. G. Sambasiva Rao - Sarvan Shipping Services private limited\\r\\nEntrepreneur of the Year in Service Business- Food & Beverage: Mr. Vikram Bakshi - McDonald\\\\\\\'s\\r\\nEntrepreneur of the Year in Service Business- Financial Services: Mr. Pankaj Dinodia - Dinodia Capital Advisors\\r\\nEntrepreneur of the Year in Service Business - Education & Traning: Mr. Satya Narayanana R. - Career Launcher\\r\\nEntrepreneur of the Year in Service Business - Travel Services: Mr. Rajiv Kumar Vij - Carzonrent\\r\\nEntrepreneur of the Year in Service Business - BPO Services: Mr. Akbar A. Lalani - Corelead Interactive Private Limited\\r\\nEntrepreneur of the Year - Healthcare Services: Mr. Ankit Agarwal - Perfect Wellness Private Limited\\r\\nEntrepreneur of the Year in Service Business - SAS & IT Services: Ms. Sonali Chowdhry - Netcomm Labs Private Limited\\r\\nTrading Business\\r\\nEntrepreneur of the Year in Trading Business - Retail Business: Mr. Punit Agarwal - Promart Retail India Private Limited\\r\\nEntrepreneur of the Year in Trading Business - Franchise & Distribution Business: Mr. Madan Dodeja - Vashi Electricals Private Limited\\r\\nManufacturing Business\\r\\nEntrepreneur of the Year in Manufacturing Business - Textile Business: Mr. Nilesh Doshi - MNR Exports Private Limited\\r\\nEntrepreneur of the Year in Manufacturing Business - Technology: Mr. Indrajit Sabharwal - Simmtronics Semi Conductors Limited\\r\\nInnovative Start-up of the Year: Mr. Siddharth Verma - Maritime Energy Heli Air Services Private Limited - (MEHAIR)\\r\\nEntrepreneur of the Year- Consumer Business: Mr. Ravi Bansal - B.P. FOOD PRODUCTS Private Limited\\r\\nDynamic Entrepreneur of the Year - Business Transformation :Mr. Manoj Kumar Agarwal - Adhunik Group\\r\\nEntrepreneur of the Year - Innovation in Technology: Mr. Sundeep Malhotra - HomeShop18\\r\\nProfessional Entrepreneur of the Year: Mr. Amit Gupta - S. Chand Group\\r\\nEntrepreneur of the Year - Innovation in Financial Services: Mr. Rohit Gadia - CapitalVia Global Research Limited\\r\\nSocial Entrepreneur of the Year: Ms. Rashi Anand - Lakshyam\\r\\nCreative Entrepreneur of the Year: Mr. Sandeep Maheshwari - Images Bazaar\\r\\nAcharya of the Year / Business Mentor of the Year: Mr. Bijaei Jayraj - Loyalty Rewardz Management Private Limited\\r\\nSerial Entrepreneur of the Year: Mr. R.Narayan - Power2SME (Legal Name - BEBB India Private Limited)\\r\\nLifetime Achievement: Mr. Subhasish Chakraborty - DTDC\\r\\nWoman Entrepreneur of the Year: Ms. Devita Saraf - Vu Technologies\\r\\nYoung Entrepreneur of the Year: Mr. Nayan Raheja - Raheja Developers\\r\\nEntrepreneur of the Year: Mr. Akshay Bector - Mrs Bector Cremica', 'franchise, entrepreneur, business, ', '5.28', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 599, 'D', '2013-07-16 10:48:06', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1241, 'tepD8UrLMTM', NULL, 'Arvind Kejriwal of Aam Admi Party at Entrepreneur India Congress 2013 ', 2, '', NULL, '', 0, 'Franchise India, Asia’s largest integrated franchise solution company, presented its third annual ‘Entrepreneur Summit 2013’. This national-level conference was an exclusive platform for highlighting the major aspects of entrepreneurship in India and an opportunity for bringing together the entrepreneurial passion of the countryrnEntrepreneur India 2013 has been designed to help the entrepreneur community to come out and stand strong not just for their enterprise but also for the cause of building this nation and making it one of the best nations across the globe.', 'Arvind Kejriwal, AAP, Aam Admi Party, Franchise, business, entrepreneur, retailer, education, awards, conference, ', '3.52', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3597, 'A', '2013-07-16 10:56:37', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1242, 'FewU_cAUkY0', NULL, 'Indian Restaurant Congress & Awards 2012 ', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'India`s Biggest National Restaurant forum in its 2nd edition focusing all the Restaurant professionals, Owners , Operators and stake holders from Restaurant industry to have a deliberate discussion on the growth of Restaurant Business in India. To discuss on the real time challenges ( in terms of Operation and financials ), imbibing best industry practices, Restaurant Franchising Know how, Networking with the industry people and to give recognition.rn', 'Franchise, business, entrepreneur, retailer, education, awards, conference, ', '3.56', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3405, 'A', '2013-07-16 10:59:50', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
