(1310, 'IV3tIoTIueE', NULL, 'Roadmap for Multichannel Retailing - Putting 4i Model in Practice ', 5, '', NULL, '', 26, 'FICCI\\\\\\\'s annual flagship event Massmerize - 2013 brought together the stalwarts from the Retail and FMCG fraternity.rnMassmerize 2013 was a great success having the presence of the top most Retailers & FMCG Industry players and a footfall of 400 stakeholders. This year the theme was \\\\\\\"Consumerism in Digital Era\\\\\\\" and how to make brands more responsible.rnMassmerize 2013 is one of its kind initiatives of FICCI, which brought together the best minds from the Retail & FMCG Industry and the Government and offers a cerebral platform to:rnNothing succeeds as success! But what are the elements that are the success pillars for the Retail & FMCG sector today and what are the strategies company employs to survive the competition and excel?rn Are market leaders will be those who adopt a multichannel approach?rn For a country like India with millions below the poverty line, and nearly 12 million people entering the job market every year, is it time the sector looks upon an inclusive business model as a core objectivern How will technological advances change the future of Retail sector?rn How do you retain customer loyalty?', 'Franchise, business, entrepreneur, retailer, education, awards, conference, roadmap, multichanel, ', '2.56', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 5243, 'A', '2013-08-13 11:28:33', NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, 0),
