(1324, 'Ye53V7d0NF8', NULL, 'Curtain Raiser : Franchise India 2013 : Flagship Event ', 1, '', NULL, '', 10, 'Franchise India Holdings Limited is Asia\\\\\\\'s largest integrated franchise solution company since 1999. It is an absolute authority on franchising and licensing. FIHL has helped hundreds of investors in selecting the right franchise and have assisted numerous organisations in international and domestic franchise expansion. Knowledge, Opportunity, Network and Success are FIHL\\\\\\\'s key ingredients.rnGaurav Marya : Group ChairmanrnSachin Marya : Group President', 'franchise, business, entrepreneur,retailer, Flagship, Event, curtain, ', '3.22', 'V', NULL, 'en', 2, 2, 10, 5787, 'A', '2013-08-19 12:33:57', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
