(1384, 'PGRcArWUm0Y', NULL, 'Dr. Anil Jindal, Chairman & MD, SRS Group : Success story : The Executive Summary ', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'Success story of  SRS Group rnThe SRS Group certainly can claim to be a league apart, given the amazing business story it has, the sectors it operates in and the legacy it enjoys. And more so, for what the future holds for it.rnrnA diversified enterprise, the SRS Group enjoys a rare, synergistic presence across sectors such as jewellery, cinemas, retail, hospitality as well as real estate, healthcare and financial services. The ability to run so many ships efficiently has meant the creation of multiple growth engines, which in turn will power the future growth waves. rnrnWhat makes it an interesting entity is the fact that it has managed to synthesise multi-domain operations on one hand and business success on the other. The SRS Group today has combined turnover of approx USD 650 million, and SRS Ltd. ranks 337 in the latest compilation of ET Top 500 companies (Dec 2012). It has 5 jewellery showrooms apart from wholesaling and manufacturing operations, 33 cinema screens, 21 retail stores, 14 f&b outlets and a 4 start hotel. Add to this a corporate tower, an IT park, a mall, group housing, independent floors, a five star hotel, motels and more, some of which are completed and others are fast moving towards completion. All this is in addition to its manufacturing operations that include a medical equipment plant as well as jewellery manufacturing facilities. rnrnA group with such far reaching scale has to have a visionary leader charting out new horizons. For SRS, it is Dr Anil Jindal, its founder Chairman, who has built this enterprise right from scratch. An accomplished professional with a quintessential positive attitude, he is a highly learned man who also holds the venerable D Litt, and is deeply committed towards CSR initiatives at the corporate and personal level.rnrnToday, the SRS Group stands firm on a solid foundation. Two of its group companies, SRS Ltd and SRS Real Infrastructure Ltd are listed on the BSE and the NSE. Its geographical spread touches diverse cities such as Delhi, Mumbai (Karjat), Faridabad, Gurgaon, Ludhiana, Patiala, Moradabad, Gorakhpur, Kurukshetra, Panchkula, Palwal and more.rnrnWith its sterling leadership, a competent team and an unshakeable belief in an honest, transparent and value-based management, it is a business house that eagerly looks forward to a glorious future.', 'entrepreneur, SRS Group, business, Dr. Anil Jindal, SRS Cinema, SRS, Success, Story, Entrepreneurial journey, ', '13.03', 'V', NULL, 'en', 32, 32, 160, 12624, 'A', '2013-10-03 14:15:22', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
