(1533, 'TAzm_viiJSE', NULL, '&quot;Licensing 189 billion USD Business&quot; - Franchise India 2013', 1, '', NULL, '', 13, 'Franchise India 2013, the 11th edition of Asia\\\'s biggest Franchise show attended by the biggest and the most reputed names from the world in franchise and retail industry. ', 'LIMA Brand Licensing 2013, Franchise India 2013, Brand Licensing India 2013, Franchise India Pragati Maidan', '18:56', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2587, 'A', '2014-09-15 12:11:59', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1534, 'cnkPXmQPHls', NULL, 'Mr. Chackochen Mathai - Importance of Training in Franchising ', 1, '', NULL, '', 13, 'Franchise India 2013, the 11th edition of Asia\\\'s biggest Franchise show held on 18th & 19th November, 2013 at Pragati Maidan, New Delhi. The grand show was attended by the leading and the most reputed names from the world in franchise and retail industry. In this video Mr. Chackochen Mathai is discussing the importance of training in franchising in Franchise Knowledge Series 2013.', 'Franchise India 2013, Franchise Knowledge Series 2013, Importance of training in Franchising', '19:01', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3650, 'A', '2014-09-15 12:15:08', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1535, '6OUoYlq59gQ', NULL, 'Panel Discussion Questionnaire - Entrepreneurship summit 2013', 1, '', NULL, '', 10, 'Franchise India 2013, the 11th edition of Asia\\\'s biggest Franchise show held on 18th & 19th November, 2013 at Pragati Maidan, New Delhi. In this video, discussion is on for the operation in franchising in various industries.', 'Franchise India 2013, Entrepreneurship summit 2013, Challenges in Franchise Operations ', '07:16', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 4, 4149, 'A', '2014-09-15 12:22:16', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1536, 'JztVH4OIsPM', NULL, 'Mobile app necessity for a Brand by Mr. Nikhil Sama at FKS 2013', 1, '', NULL, '', 13, 'Franchise India 2013, the 11th edition of Asia\\\'s biggest Franchise show held on 18th & 19th November, 2013 at Pragati Maidan, New Delhi. In this video Mr. Nikhil Sama (Founder & CEO, SnapLion) is putting the light on the importance of a mobile app for any particular brand. \r\nThe grand show was attended by the leading and the most reputed names from the world in franchise and retail industry. Technology definitely play a superb role in catching the strenuous traffic for a particular page or brand and by the time has proved to be the key investment to be made of best ROI. More than half of the population is using their mobile phones to stay updated about trending brands and offers.', 'Franchise India 2013, Franchise Knowledge Series 2013, Necessity of a brand mobile app, Mr. Nikhil Sama', '10:28', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 5113, 'A', '2014-09-15 12:26:11', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1537, 'e0SQOIebmX4', NULL, 'Understanding business potential by Ms. Aparna Mittal  ', 1, '', NULL, '', 13, 'Franchise India 2013, the 11th edition of Asia\\\'s biggest Franchise show held on 18th & 19th November, 2013 at Pragati Maidan, New Delhi. Ms. Aparna Mittal (Partner, Luthra & Luthra Law Offices) in this video is putting the light on how one can leverage the business and take it to the next level.\r\nThe splendid show was attended by the leading and the most reputed names from the world in franchise and retail industry. \r\nThe Indian market is considered among the top five retail market in the world. The business can grow to new heights by understanding true potential of business, bottom necks, regulatory schemes and long term strategies. Check out the video for detailed knowledge.', 'Franchise India 2013, Franchise Knowledge Series 2013, Understanding business potential, Ms. Aparna Mittal  ', '19:08', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 4651, 'A', '2014-09-15 12:27:44', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1538, 'pzaNey2HaQw', NULL, 'Economics of Indian Restaurant Industry in 2014 and beyond by Amit Burman at IRC 2014', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Amit Burman - A fourth generation entrepreneur with an eye on identifying emerging business opportunities, is the brain behind the introduction of packaged fruit juices in India way back in 1997 with Dabur India Ltd, a leading consumer products maker in the country. He also manages F&B retail venture by the name of Lite Bite Foods which has forged a strategic alliance to manage Food Courts on behalf of PVR Cinemas. Talking at 4th Indian Restaurant Congress, held on 28th and 29th of August at Taj Vivanta, SurajKund Road, Burman talks about the economics of Indian Restaurant Industry in 2014 and beyond drafting a clear picture on how technology is shaping the future of food service markets and their suppliers in India. ', 'Indian Restaurant Congress 2014, Franchise India, Amit Burman, Indian F&B  Industry, Food Retail, Dabur India, Lite Bite Foods', '16:27', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 5623, 'A', '2014-10-28 11:50:30', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1539, 'QlhBGOElNYo', NULL, 'Economics of Indian Restaurant Industry in 2014 and beyond by Amit Burman at IRC 2014 - Part 2', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Amit Burman - A fourth generation entrepreneur with an eye on identifying emerging business opportunities, is the brain behind the introduction of packaged fruit juices in India way back in 1997 with Dabur India Ltd, a leading consumer products maker in the country. He also manages F&B retail venture by the name of Lite Bite Foods which has forged a strategic alliance to manage Food Courts on behalf of PVR Cinemas. ', 'Indian Restaurant Congress 2014, Franchise India, Amit Burman, Indian F&B  Industry, Food Retail, Dabur India, Lite Bite Foods', '15:09', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 1, 4757, 'A', '2014-10-28 11:55:10', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1540, '7KXNJfm9sIE', NULL, 'Evolution of Indian cuisine in India and abroad', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Chef Hemant Oberoi is the face of Taj cuisine. A multiple award winner, including the Executive Chef of the year award by H & F S Hosts, Chef Oberoi brings over 30 years of culinary expertise to the Taj name. Credited with having introduced various niche cuisines to the Indian palate, Chef Oberoi single-handedly brought Indian cuisine to world-class gourmet standards. Talking at 4th Indian Restaurant Congress, held on 28th and 29th of August at Taj Vivanta, SurajKund Road, Chef Oberoi shares his experience on evolution of Indian cuisine in India and abroad.', 'Indian Restaurant Congress, Taj Mahal Palace, Indian Cuisine, Chef Hemant Oberoi, Gourmet Standards', '13:15', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 1, 3193, 'A', '2014-10-28 12:09:21', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1541, '9Tjg3oskj4U', NULL, 'Food law and policies by Shri Siraj Hussain at Indian Restaurant Congress 2014', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Shri Siraj Hussain is an IAS officer of 1979 batch. He has specialized in Higher Education and Food Management. He has served the Government of India in various capacities but he has been mostly involved with the Food Management in various capacity and was instrumental in putting up the scheme Private Entrepreneurs Guarantee Scheme 2010. Talking at Indian Restaurant Congress 2014, held on 28th and 29th of August at Taj Vivanta, Surajkund Road, he shares his thought on the Food law and policies also briefing the audience about the Food management in Indian F&B industry.', 'Siraj Hussain, Food law and Policies, F&B Industry, Food Management, Indian Restaurant Congress ', '8:22', 'V', NULL, 'en', 2, 2, 3, 3624, 'A', '2014-10-28 12:14:22', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1542, '6vgD6kQsZmE', NULL, 'The changing face of beverages in India by Rahul Singh at Indian Restaurant Congress 2014', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Rahul Singh is the proud CEO and founder of THE BEER CAFE - India largest & favorite Beer Chain, with 10 outlets pouring and 15 more locations in making. Taking the unconventional route, Rahul kick started this venture in 2011, and it is already poised to become the largest, fastest, and most profitable alco-beverage service brand in India. Talking at Indian Restaurant Congress, Rahul shares his view on the growing beverages trend in India and how is it evolving from sharbat to cocktails and mocktails.', 'Beverages trend, Beer, The Beer cafe, Indian Restaurant Congress, Rahul Singh', '6:09', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 4438, 'A', '2014-10-28 12:19:21', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1543, 'Dw7iuEl7zPE', NULL, 'How to motivate your employee at workplace by Niren Chaudhary at Indian Restaurant Awards 2014', 7, '', NULL, '', 36, 'Niren Chaudhary is the President at Yum! Restaurants, India, a subsidiary of Yum! Restaurants which owns the brands &ndash; Pizza Hut, KFC, A&W, Long John Silver and Taco Bell worldwide. Speaking at Indian Restaurant Awards, Niren shares his view on How to maintain Happiness at Workplace.', 'Niren Chaudhary, Indian Restaurant Awards, Motivation, Indian Restaurants', '24:12', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2955, 'A', '2014-10-28 12:27:08', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1544, 'NWxea8zWddU', NULL, 'Innovation in Restaurant Business by Chirag Gupta at Indian Restaurant Congress 2014', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Chirag is a Business Consultant with MS Degree from Case Western Reserve University, Cleveland, Ohio. He, together with his friend, Ankur Gupta has nailed down the Gourmet Popcorn concepts in India. Speaking at Indian Restaurant Congress, he shares his view on How in restaurant business will save pricing when it comes to eating out.', 'Chirag Gupta, Indian Restaurant Congress, Innovation in Restaurant Business, Popcorn, 4700 BC Popcorn', '14:20', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 4, 3958, 'A', '2014-10-28 12:30:31', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1545, 'xeVCCuStQm4', NULL, 'Food Trends in Indian F&B Industry by Chef Jolly at Indian Restaurant Congress 2014', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'The two decades of long career span of Surjan Singh Jolly, fondly known as Chef Jolly, includes being the Guest Chef on the world renowned reality television show on Star Plus, Junior Master Chef India. He also has his own show on Zee Khana Khazana titled Ab Har Koi Chef and was chosen as the Head Chef for Paris Hilton during her visit to India.  Speaking at Indian Restaurant Congress, Chef Jolly opines about the ongoing food trends in India and how the shift is going from beverages to food which was earlier food to beverages.', 'Indian Restaurant Congress, Food Trends, Indian F&B Industry, Chef Surjan Singh Jolly', '17:03', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 4812, 'A', '2014-10-28 12:34:47', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1546, 'rVo82THUsdU', NULL, 'Dum pukht Style Cooking by MasterChef Imtiaz Qureshi at Indian Restaurant Congress 2014', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Hailing from the famed Qureshi clan of cooks, Master Chef Imtiaz Qureshi is the man behind the underrated Dumpukht. Born in the year 1939 in Lucknow, he learnt on the job and jumped into catering for a gathering of 1000 people as well as cooking for political big-wigs including Pt. Jawaharlal Nehru and Indira Gandhi. Talking at Indian Restaurant Congress 2014, he shares his experience of learning the skills of cooking Dum Pukht style Biryani in the kitchen at an early age of Nine.', 'Indian Restaurant Congress, Restaurant Fraternity, Chef Imtiaz Qureshi, Dum Pukht Style Cooking', '21:51', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 4, 4547, 'A', '2014-10-28 12:36:29', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1547, 'w1CuX4VH8mQ', NULL, 'The current demand of PEs when investing in restaurant Business', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Ashish is currently leading investments of TVS Capital in the F&B space. He is the CEO for TexMex Cuisine which own and operated Chili\\\'s Grill & Bar in West and South India. He is also actively supporting TVS Capital for opportunities to invest further in this sector. Sharing his opinion about the investment scenario in India at Indian Restaurant Congress, Ashish says Casual dining is the new love of PEs when investing in restaurant business.', 'Ashish Saxena, Investment, Restaurant Business, PEs', '6:38', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 4, 3973, 'A', '2014-10-28 12:41:06', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1548, '6NGTPGYgrIM', NULL, 'Food trend in India by Kunal Kapoor', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'A degree holder from the Institute of Hotel Management Chandigarh, Kunal Kapoor started his career with the Taj Group of Hotels. He has an in depth understanding of North-West Frontier, Punjabi, Awadhi, Dakshin, Italian, European and Goan cuisines and has earned specialisation in Indian curries and kebabs. Chef Kunal has recently launched his cookbook by the name of A Chef in Every Home. Talking at Indian Restaurant Congress 2014, Kunal shares his view on the growing food trend in Indian and globally.', 'Kunal Kapoor, Chef, Celebrity Chef, Indian Restaurant Congress, Food Trend', '12:57', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 7410, 'A', '2014-10-28 12:44:24', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1549, 'ZKie7Rp3YLA', NULL, 'Growing from Local to a Chain', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Narendra Malhotra has over 25 years of rich, cross cultural experience in F&B retail and has worked with some of the leading brands of India. He holds a Diploma in Hotel Management from the Institute of Hotel Management, Catering & Nutrition, Pusa, New Delhi. Talking at Indian Restaurant Congress 2014, he shares his view on Growing from Local to a Chain.', 'Narendra Malhota, Restaurants, Indian Restaurant Congress, Local to a Chain', '6:40', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 4, 3932, 'A', '2014-10-28 12:47:16', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1550, 'XdltNKj1uSg', NULL, 'Future of restaurant operations and technology convergence by Kapil Malhotra', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Kapil Malhotra is the Founder & Managing Director of the Total Solutions Group. Being a Chartered Accountant, by qualification had the distinction of being the youngest CA\\\'s in India at 21 years of age. Addressing the audience at Indian Restaurant Congress 2014, he shares his view on Future of restaurant operations and technology convergence.', 'Kapil Malhotra, Technology, Technology in Restaurants, Restaurant Operations', '14:58', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3912, 'A', '2014-10-28 12:51:06', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1551, '44nr8SKTByM', NULL, 'Keeping the menu local according to the taste and palate of the customer by Nita Mehta at Indian Restaurant Congress 2014', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Nita Mehta is the Cookery Book Writer and Owner - SNAB Publishers Pvt Ltd. Nita Mehta has entered the hearts and homes of millions of people across the globe through her cookbooks. In the discussion of a recipe, Nita becomes the readers teacher and friend. She is an MSc graduate and gold medalist in Food and Nutrition subject. Speaking at the Indian Restaurant Congress 2014, she shares her view on Keeping the menu local according to the taste and palate of the customer.', 'Nita Mehta, Local tastes, Indian Restaurant Congress, Restaurant Industry, Menu', '8:42', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 4442, 'A', '2014-10-28 12:54:27', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1552, 'PhWGULqnf4w', NULL, 'How brand image and design can make the restaurant concept more successful by Ashish Kapur at Indian Restaurant Congress 2014', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Ashish Kapur is the Co-Founder & Managing Director of Yo! China. He has successfully developed India\\\'s first and largest chain of Chinese restaurants. Presently, Yo! China has 51 outlets across 14 cities in India and aims to open over 200 outlets by 2015. Talking at Indian Restaurant Congress, Ashish shares his view on How brand image and design can make the restaurant concept more successful.', 'Ashish Kapur, Indian Restaurant Congress, Restaurant Brand Image, Restaurant Concept', '9:01', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3373, 'A', '2014-10-28 12:59:17', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1553, 'wDhFUVcbXjQ', NULL, 'Reality of Retail from Past to Present by Rajesh Jain', 5, '', NULL, '', 26, 'Mr. Rajesh Jain (CEO & Director), LaCoste India Sports & Leisure Apparel Ltd. telling about his experience & views on the retail industry growth from early 90s to present.\r\nHe believes that retail & brand actually coexists and cannot survive without each other with the growing competition in today\\\'s time. He focuses on the challenges faced so far and the need of the change in the true manner to become a successful brand with powerful retail network.\r\n', 'Franchise India, Retail vs Brand, Rajesh Jain, E Retail', '4:43', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 6009, 'A', '2014-10-28 14:13:18', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1554, '4xX4eKHmypE', NULL, 'The Global Entrepreneur Going Places by Vishwanath, MD, Nath Bros Exim International Ltd', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'Vishwanath is the founder member of Export Promotion Council of EOU and SEZ and of National Institute of Fashion Technology. He is also the elected member of ASSOCHAM. Besides, He is the Joint Managing Director of Messrs Nath Bros Exim International Ltd &ndash; weavers of silk fabrics and blends and exporters of ladies designer apparels to Europe and the US. Speaking at the Entrepreneur India Show 2014, he narrated his entire entrepreneurial journey and how he attained success. ', 'Nath Bros Exim International, Vishwanath, Export Promotion Council, National Institute of Fashion Technology', '12:17', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 5217, 'A', '2014-11-15 10:32:40', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1555, 'm4VxAQEdM8k', NULL, 'Social Entrepreneurship by Akshay Saxena, Co-founder & President, Avanti ', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'Akshay currently serves as the President of Avanti. For his work at Avanti, he was awarded the Draper Richards Kaplan Fellowship and Echoing Green Fellowship in 2012. Before Avanti, Akshay served on the founding team of HeartFlow, a venture-backed medical diagnostics company. Speaking at the Entrepreneur India 2014, he threw on some of the challenges which entrepreneurs face in the social business.', 'Avanti, Akshay Saxena, Save the Children Alliance', '4:27', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 4580, 'A', '2014-11-15 10:35:18', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1556, 'ujEJj-Dkg3s', NULL, 'How to Workshop: Developing A Business Plan by Prajakt Raut at Entrepreneur India 2014 - Part1', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'Personal goal of Prajakt in life is to encourage and assist a 100,000 people to become entrepreneurs. Prajakt was previously a part of the founding team of The Hatch for start-ups, where he established the brand as a leading player in the early-stage entrepreneurial eco-system in India. At the Entrepreneur India 2014, he shared his view on what is the time right time for an entrepreneur to raise capital.', 'Prajakt Raut, business plan, entrepreneurship, eco-system ', '19:54', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 1, 4079, 'A', '2014-11-15 10:41:18', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1557, 'fgTV252Kj7k', NULL, 'The Ecosystem for Entrepreneurship: A New Vision by Mahendra Swarup at Entrepreneur India 2014 ', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'Mahendra Swarup is the Managing Director and Partner at Avigo Capital Partners. He has more than 30 years of operating experience in blue-chip companies including PepsiCo, Nestle, ACC, Times Group and Sun Group (Moscow). Speaking at the Entrepreneur India 2014, he discussed about the future of entrepreneurship.', 'Mahendra Swarup, ecosystem, entrepreneurship, Avigo Capital Partners', '18:08', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2588, 'A', '2014-11-15 10:44:07', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1558, 'yWiutvUUk9Y', NULL, 'The Ecosystem for Entrepreneurship by Sudarshan Bhagat, MOS - Social Justice & Empowerment, GOI', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'Sudarshan Bhagat is 45 years old Loksabha MP, elected from Lohardaga of Jharkhand state as a member of Bharatiya Janata Party. He is a former Jharkhand Mukti Morcha member & a non-RSS MP of the BJP. He was a State (Bihar) General Secretary with the Akhil Bhartiya Vidyarthi Parishad as a student. Speaking at the inaugural session of Entrepreneur India Show 2014, he discussed about the crucial initiatives taken by government for education sector in India.', 'Entrepreneurship, ecosystem, Govt of India, Minister of State for Social Justice & Empowerment', '14:16', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3522, 'A', '2014-11-15 10:47:43', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1559, 'tQI4qPhmJqc', NULL, 'How to Workshop: Developing A Business Plan by Prajakt Raut at Entrepreneur India 2014 - Part2', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'Prajakt\\\\\\\'s personal goal in life is to encourage and assist a 100,000 people to become entrepreneurs. Prajakt was previously a part of the founding team of The Hatch for start-ups, where he established the brand as a leading player in the early-stage entrepreneurial Eco-system in India. At the Entrepreneur India 2014, he shared his view on what is the time right time for an entrepreneur to raise capital.', 'Prajakt Raut, business plan, entrepreneurship, eco-system ', '20:24', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3996, 'A', '2014-11-15 10:51:57', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1560, '6OP3qnrE9hE', NULL, 'Lean growth for MSMEs', 2, '', NULL, '', 17, 'Shyam Poddar is the Chairman of Foreign Exchange Committee at PHD Chamber of Commerce and Industry and also the MD at Forex Capital Services based in New Delhi. Sharing his insights with Entrepreneur, Poddar talks about the on the current state of affairs of Indian MSMEs and enhancing their exports.', 'shyam poddar, phd, msme, export, entrepreneur india', '04:44', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3182, 'A', '2014-12-05 14:26:41', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1561, 'IZSK22kJwKg', NULL, 'Understanding what Ache Din means for India Inc.', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'Dr Pronab Sen is the Chairman at National Statistical Commission. He was the first Chief Statistician of India (CSI) from 2007-2010 and also the Secretary at Ministry of Statistics & Programme Implementation during the same period. Underlining the growth of MSMEs so far, Dr Sen tells Entrepreneur the need for increased public investments in rural connectivity to boost MSMEs performance and whether industries are reflecting true story of Indians growth.', 'pronab sen, msme, ache din, rural india, entrepreneur, national statistical commission', '02:52', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 2, 3893, 'A', '2014-12-05 14:30:03', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1562, 'FgIGce9nE9g', NULL, 'Definitive way of implementing GST and usage of technology for MSMEs ', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'Dr Nilotpal Goswami is the Principal Director at Comptroller and Auditor (CAG) of India, country supreme audit institution. Talking to Entrepreneur, Dr Goswami highlights recent developments in trade and finance having direct bearing on MSMEs, including the highly anticipated Good and Services Tax and its rightful implementation along with effective technology implementation without passing on its cost to the end consumer.', 'nilotpal goswami, gst, technology, cag, msme, entrepreneur india', '02:08', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 5, 4593, 'A', '2014-12-05 14:31:53', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1563, 'stpcVGNJeK4', NULL, 'How local bodies like NDMC can contribute to restaurant and hospitality growth in India', 7, '', NULL, '', 35, 'O.P. Mishra is the Director at NDMC. Talking to Restaurant India, he shares how can these food fest help in growth of the countries hospitality sector and also the tourism in Delhi as approximately 35 percent foreign tourists choose Delhi when on India Trip.', 'NDMC, Palate Fest, O.P. Mishra, Indian Hospitality, Restaurant ', '02:48', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3865, 'A', '2014-12-08 11:11:34', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1564, 'GZN3TVZE9gU', NULL, 'How will food fests help Indian restaurant and hospitality industry grow', 7, '', NULL, '', 35, 'Ruchi Sibal together with Aditi Kapoor founded Palate Fest to initiate the trend of food fest in India. Talking to Restaurant India, they share, what prompted them to arrange a international level food fest partnering with around 40 restaurants and suppliers in the city.', 'Palate Fest, Food Fest, Indian F&B Industry, NDMC, Emerging Taste', '02:20', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3863, 'A', '2014-12-08 11:13:03', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `fihl_podcstvideo` (`sno`, `videoID`, `podcast_id`, `title`, `category`, `image`, `image_path`, `maxresimage`, `subcategory`, `description`, `keyword`, `duration`, `podcast_type`, `podcast_link`, `pod_lang`, `total_comment`, `total_votes`, `total_value`, `views`, `status`, `create_date`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `fbshare`, `twittershare`, `linkedinshare`, `whasupshare`) VALUES
(1565, 'iKiTvCZ62xA', NULL, 'Mr. Gaurav Marya, Chairman, Franchise India, Inaugural speech at Delhi Franchise Summit &ndash; Leadership and Growth by CII and Franchise India', 1, '', NULL, '', 10, 'Confederation of Indian Industry and Franchise India co-organized the Delhi Franchise Summit with the theme Leadership & Growth in New Delhi on 21st November 2014.\r\n\r\nThis exclusive convention was designed for CEOs, Presidents, CXO and Business Development & Franchise Leaders to have Strategic high &ndash; level growth dialogues for their business and Brand growth. The content raised the bar on Ideas for Development, Building a Distribution set-up or franchising the business. Through engaging discussions and facilitated roundtables, executive leaders discussed challenges and shared best practices that drilled deep on culture, franchise growth, unit economics for franchisees and franchisor, new areas of growth and risk management.\r\n', 'Delhi Franchise Summit, franchising, Franchise India, MSME, CII & Franchise India\r\n\r\n', '20:16', 'V', NULL, 'en', 2, 2, 10, 6090, 'A', '2014-12-08 11:27:52', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1566, 'GlodJz8roac', NULL, 'Before-time delivery is USP of Gaurs - Jitendra Singh', 3, '', NULL, '', 19, 'Jitendra Singh is President - Sales & Marketing with Gaursons India Ltd, one of the most seasoned realty players in India today. ', 'Jitendra Singh, Gaursons India, Real Estate, developer, Realty market, FDI, FAR, REIT', '0:56', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2346, 'A', '2014-12-08 17:41:26', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1567, 'Otu3tlQYwEA', NULL, 'Housing for All campaign by Government will revive Realty sector by Manoj Gaur', 3, '', NULL, '', 19, 'Manoj Gaur is the President of Confederation of Real Estate Developers Associations of India (CREDAI) Western U.P. and has been involved in various social causes. Also, he is the Managing Director of Gaursons India Ltd, one of the most seasoned realty players in India today, with a rich experience of close to 16 years. \r\nHis expertise lies in the field of construction. He has to his credit the development of 25,000 flats and Rs. 10,000 Crore worth of projects in holding group companies.', 'Manoj Gaur, Gaursons India Ltd, Real Estate, developer, Realty market, FDI, FAR, REIT', '02:04', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3941, 'A', '2014-12-08 17:42:31', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1568, 'WHukwW3EGPU', NULL, 'The new retail revolution by Devendra Chawla', 5, '', NULL, '', 26, 'Devendra Chawla, Chief Executive Officer of  Food Bazar - Future Group shares his industry \r\nexperience. Besides, he throws light on the evolution of new retail  and how the segment has evolved over the years.\r\n', 'Indian Retail Congress 2014, Franchise India, Retail, Online Retail, Devendra Chawla', '06:36', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3264, 'A', '2014-12-09 09:23:19', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
