(1572, 'nnZl8jrbT0U', NULL, 'How franchising can help grow your restaurant business by Dheeraj Gupta at Indian Restaurant Congress 2014', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Recognized as one of the youngest thought-leaders in the franchising industry, Dheeraj has won several awards in this field including titles like Award for New Concept Franchising and Award for Innovative Franchisee model in 2007. Talking at Indian Restaurant Congress he speaks on How franchising is helping the restaurant sector in India grow.', 'Dheeraj Gupta, Indian Restaurant Congress, Vada Pav, JumboKing', '07:36', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2703, 'A', '2014-12-12 15:08:29', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1573, 'z0_qZ9NhJGg', NULL, 'How consumers have changed with time by M A Tejani at Indian Restaurant Congress 2014', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Ashish Kapur is the Co-Founder & Managing Director of Yo! China. He has successfully developed Indias first and largest chain of Chinese restaurants. Presently, Yo! China has 51 outlets across 14 cities in India and aims to open over 200 outlets by 2015. Talking at Indian Restaurant Congress, Tejani shares his view on How Indian consumers have evolved their tastes over the years.', 'M A Tejani, Indian Restaurant Congress, Consumers, RTC, Gits Foods', '03:44', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 2, 2866, 'A', '2014-12-12 15:09:59', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1574, 'y7uWuhac7GE', NULL, 'How can a restaurateur use the right combination of high street, malls and food court at its venture by Murali Krishna Parna at Indian Restaurant Congress 2014', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'An IIM-Ahmedabad alumnus, Murali Krishna Parna, currently the CEO of Sagar Ratna, has a career that expands within sectors ranging from sales, advertising communication, brand management to category management, merchandising etc. Speaking at Indian Restaurant Congress, Parna Shares his view on How can a restaurateur use the right combination of high street, malls and food court at its venture.', 'Murali Krishna Parna, Indian Restaurant Congress, Restaurateur, Sagar Ratna, South Indian Restaurant', '05:53', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 4719, 'A', '2014-12-12 15:11:30', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1575, 'pfmeh5i4LUs', NULL, 'How the modern day franchise owners model is changing by Sam Chopra at Indian Restaurant Congress 2014', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Sam Chopra is Chairman of CybizCorp which is an India entry and expansion expert specializing in Franchising, Licensing and Channel Distribution in verticals like Business Services, Real Estate, Retail, Hospitality and Food & Beverage. Talking at Indian Restaurant Congress, he tells How the modern day franchise owners model is changing.', 'Sam Chopra, CybizCorp, Franchisor, Restaurant, Franchising', '10:59', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 4898, 'A', '2014-12-12 15:13:54', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1576, 'o0CmPQg6_5k', NULL, 'How to keep the stores consistent and the location similar by Sharad Sachdeva at Indian Restaurant Congress 2014', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Today after completing 20 years in the corporate world Mr. Sachdeva heads one of the largest food & Beverages Company of the country, Lite Bite Foods. Speaking at Indian Restaurant Congress, he shares his view on How to keep the stores consistent and the location similar.', 'Sharad Sachdeva, Lite Bite Foods, Indian Restaurant Congress, Restaurant Location', '06:10', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3671, 'A', '2014-12-12 15:15:09', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1577, 'R9yNTcfDoso', NULL, 'How a restaurateur can use real estate as an inflation hedge over the years by Zorawar Kalra at Indian Restaurant Congress 2014', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Counted amongst one of the youngest, successful restaurateurs of India, Zorawar has amalgamated a penchant for Indian cuisine with his natural business acumen and a rich heritage spanning over four decades in the Indian culinary space and hospitality industry. Talking at Indian Restaurant Congress, he shares, his view on How a restaurateur can use real estate as an inflation hedge over the years.', 'Zorawar Kalra, Massive Restaurant, Real Estate, Restaurant, Best Location', '12:31', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 5, 3982, 'A', '2014-12-12 15:17:18', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1578, 'elxROBO9w1o', NULL, 'Driving innovation in loyalty by Anjan Choudhary at Indian Restaurant Congress 2014', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Anjan has unique experience of starting a cutting edge software product startup, running a small scale traditional economy business and successfully transitioning in between to establish himself in a rapidly growing career in technology and consulting. Speaking at Indian Restaurant Congress, he tells how one can find the sweet spot for the business by creating loyalty.', 'Anjan Choudhary, Marketing, Loyalty Programs, Innovation in Restaurant Business', '09:44', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 4, 3854, 'A', '2014-12-15 10:54:55', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1579, 'gOgEJgf4QSM', NULL, 'How to advertise, socialise and monetise when word-of-mouth has moved online by Samir Khadepaun at Indian Restaurant Congress 2014', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Samir, a Bachelor from PCIT and Monash University, is as passionate about Mobile Technologies as he is passionate about being a foodie. Talking at Indian Restaurant Congress, he shares his experience about placing your product right in the market.', 'Samir Khadepaun, Indian Restaurant Congress, Marketing Approach, Mobikon Asia ', '04:07', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 1, 4137, 'A', '2014-12-15 10:56:04', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
