(1581, '5XCrlQ6Pb6Q', NULL, 'What made Carls Jr to enter India by Ned Lyerly', 7, '', NULL, '', 35, 'Ned Lyerly, is President at CKE Restaurants Holding, which owns Californian burger chain, Carls Jr.  Talking to Restaurant India, he shares his experience about placing his brand right into the Indian market by partnering with the right local partner.', 'Ned Lyerly, Carls Jr, Burger Chain, India Entry', '01:15', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 5, 2423, 'A', '2015-01-12 16:14:46', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
