(1583, '2vznI224VQE', NULL, 'Harman Baweja talks about Fitness industry and diet food at The Entrepreneurship Summit 2014', 2, '', NULL, '', 17, 'Known to be one of the most handsome celebrities of Bollywood, Harman Baweja is the Co-founder of LYS and a renowned Celebrity Fitness Enthusiast. The actor has played a pivotal role in setting up each and every aspect of LYS Fitness and supported Bollywood Diva Bipasha Basu in her drive to keep daughters, mothers, wives and sisters fit. During the session, the actor talked about his journey from Fat to Fit and gave views on binging on fast food, importance to include healthy food in the diet and much more.', 'Entrepreneur Summit, Franchise India, Harman Baweja, Bipasha Basu, fitness, healthcare', '04:40', 'V', NULL, 'en', 2, 2, 6, 5230, 'A', '2015-01-14 12:33:08', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1584, '7XDZIVm8U-Y', NULL, 'Six factors contributing growth of B&W industry: Chackochen Mathai', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'Speaking at The Entrepreneurship Summit 2014, organised by Franchise India Holdings Ltd recently in New Delhi, Chackochen Mathai, GM- Business Development, Trends in Vogue Pvt Ltd, a Cavinkare Group Company has shared some points which would indeed help the small and big players in the industry to embrace new ways to improve their business growth. Mathai had given an overview on the lines of - importance of location, purchasing power of the consumer, democratic age, role of franchising, funding, maintenance of quality & hygiene and more.', 'Chackochen Mathai, Entreprenuer Summit, Franchise India, salon, business', '13:19', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3406, 'A', '2015-01-14 12:34:49', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1585, '_MQTXQTAwh4', NULL, 'Bausch & Lomb MD unveils 2015 expansion plans in aesthetics market', 1, '', NULL, '', 11, 'In conversation with Wellness India, Sanjay Bhutani, Managing Director- India & SAARC, Bausch & Lomb Eyecare spreads light over expansion plans of the brand in 2015 with big targets to capture the largest share of aesthetics market. \\r\\nFurthermore, Bhutani speaks about invasive and non-invasive products offered by the brand in aesthetics market. He explains how these products will cover different surgical and non-surgical requirements and what would be the price range. He also lists skin clinics, cosmetologists and other market leaders who are service providers of the company.', 'LOreal Professional, Aseem Kaushik, Wellness India, Indian Hairdressing Awards', '06:24', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 5658, 'A', '2015-01-14 12:39:43', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1586, 'V0SfndLWue4', NULL, 'L\\\'Oreal Professional on expansion spree: Aseem Kaushik', 1, '', NULL, '', 11, 'In a rendezvous with Aseem Kaushik, Director, L\\\'Oreal Professional Product Division, on the sidelines of Indian Hairdressing Awards, Wellness India found that brand is all set to launch aggressive horizontal expansion plans. \r\nAs of now, Paris based global cosmetic brand has presence in 350 towns in India.\r\nDuring the event, Kaushik disclosed targets 2015 and the brands\\\' strategy to laud young talent by organizing big events and much more.', 'Baush & Lomb, aesthetics market, Wellness India, Sanjay Bhutani', '01:49', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 4867, 'A', '2015-01-14 12:41:15', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1587, 'GsA3MyLoMAQ', NULL, 'Learning the Art of Delegation', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'Sharmeen Khalid is Info Edge India Chief Human Resources Officer. Prior to joining Info Edge in 2006, Indias premier on-line classifieds portal that runs portals like naukri.com and 99acres.com, Khalid was working with Polaris, a leader in financial technology sector. In an interactive discussion, she shares her learning over the key aspect of delegation in a small business set up, such as what to be delegated, what not to be delegated, things to look at while hiring people and few examples of good delegation and bad delegation.', 'delegation, sharmeen Khalid, info edge, entrepreneur India, MSME, HR', '06:29', 'V', NULL, 'en', 2, 2, 9, 3967, 'A', '2015-01-15 14:13:25', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1588, 'tZGOvpHx4mU', NULL, 'Measuring Employee Productivity', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'Gagan Bhargava is current heading the HR division of prime news channel NDTV as its Group Head since 2007. A seasoned HR professional, Bhargava talks about the aspects of compensation and incentives for employees to work extra hours in a growing environment and touches upon areas viz., do long hours means more productivity? Setting productivity targets for people and abiding with the labour laws.', 'gagan bhargava, ndtv, entrepreneur India, hr, employee productivity, incentives', '03:00', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2502, 'A', '2015-01-15 14:14:06', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1589, 'RI-NQDCI8sQ', NULL, 'Taking the Road Less Travelled', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'Dhruv Shringi is among the few new and young poster boys of rising Indian ecommerce space. His online travel portal Yatra.com started in 2006 today sits prettily at the top of online travel business segment with 2,000 people on-board and competes with Nasdaq-listed MakeMyTrip. Shringi shares his thoughts on different growth areas of Yatra.com starting from its start-up days, how did Kingfisher crisis affected them, issues they face when they hire new people, the time when they had to lay off 600 people, how tough is it to retain the start-up culture while growing up, his current job profile and much more in a high-powered interaction.', 'Dhruv shringi, online travel, yatra.com, entrepreneur India, make my trip, ecommerce', '14:16', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 4465, 'A', '2015-01-15 14:14:53', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1590, 'SKUqnL8RAzA', NULL, 'Estate Summit and Awards 2014, organized by Franchise India', 3, '', NULL, '', 20, 'Biggest B2B show in the real estate sector for property developers, brokers and suppliers organized by Franchise India.', 'real estate, property, builder, construction, broker, developer, realty, estate show, real estate show ', '0:54', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 5, 3768, 'A', '2015-01-15 17:35:45', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
