(1599, 'YW8nJxbHNSc', NULL, 'India is our prime focus for expansion at present says John Kersh', 2, '', NULL, '', 15, 'In an exclusive conversation with Wellness India, John Kersh, Vice President of International Development, Anytime Fitness LLC, talked about long term opportunity for fitness in Indian market, his big plans to spread the brand in every nook & corner of the country, strategy of Anytime Fitness to constantly re-invigorate the brand, its brand loyal members who have etched the brands tattoo on their body and much more.', 'John Kersh, India, Anytime Fitness, gym, expansion', '06:01', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 4210, 'A', '2015-01-17 16:39:07', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1600, '3yQDXvD9Vw0', NULL, 'Spain Custo Dalmau Enters the Country of Colours with a Bang', 5, '', NULL, '', 27, 'Much like the American subregion latinamericano, India for Spain\\\'s fashion designer Custo Dalmau is a sunshine place. He looked for inspiration on colour in Asia and picked up India (Delhi, precisely) to launch his premium brand, Custo Barcelona. Amid fanfare and a veritable rainbow of hues, Retailer caught up with the man and talked about Custo foray into Indian market.', 'Custo Barcelona, Custo Dalmau, International design house, Spanish designer, Foray into India, Delhi launch, Colours, designs, retailer, Latin America         ', '07:29', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 4963, 'A', '2015-01-20 09:37:15', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1601, 'aGXealyU7gI', NULL, '109th annual session of PHD Chamber', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'Sharad Jaipuria currently serves as the President of PHD Chamber of Commerce and Industry. He is the Chairman and MD of Ginni International Ltd. and the chairman of the Jaipuria Institute of Management. He is also the President of Integral Education Society. Jaipuria has been associated with textile industry for over 30 years. While speaking at the 109th annual session of PHD Chamber, Jaipuria highlighted the importance of Make in India initiative, which is likely to boost the manufacturing sector of India.', 'PHD Chamber, Ginni International Ltd, Make in India, Sharad Jaipuria, Integral Education Society', '18:45', 'V', NULL, 'en', 4, 4, 20, 4235, 'A', '2015-01-20 09:39:01', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1602, 'rVclzCh0BwA', NULL, 'Eyeing big pie in hygiene market and plans to improve sanitation in India: SCA Head ', 2, '', NULL, '', 15, 'In an exclusive interaction with Wellness India, Cecilia Edebo, Managing Director, SCA Hygiene Products India, unveiled her big plans to uplift the hygiene quotient of India, joining the Make in India campaign of PM Narendra Modi, about the unique products being introduced by the company which include bio-degradable diapers and tissues, company factory in Pune and plans to open more manufacturing units in years to come.', 'Sanitation, Narendra Modi, Make In India, campaign, SCA ', '13:32', 'V', NULL, 'en', 2, 2, 10, 3239, 'A', '2015-01-20 09:41:21', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(1603, 'pZ-h9wh6Xtc', NULL, 'Aim to be a global learning hub: Holistic Training Solution', 2, '', NULL, '', 15, 'Ian Stern is the MD of Holistic Training Solutions (HTS), a leading Talent Development Consultancy in India. Stern has consulted and trained in all continents and over 15 countries across the globe and travelled over 50 countries. In the last 12 months, he has trained and coached leaders from over 30 countries. He has personally worked as a business consultant with over top 170 global clients and trained over 35,000 people in the last 18 years. rnrnLynda Ongel Lepcha is the MD of Holistic Training Solutions. She is also the author of Winning Hearts and Touching Minds - Training in India. Before venturing into the world of entrepreneurship, she used to work in Citi bank in the training and development department where she developed and delivered programs in behavioural skills and leadership programs.', 'Holistic Training Solutions, Consultancy, Training, entrepreneurship, Citi bank ', '04:54', 'V', NULL, 'en', 2, 2, 10, 5743, 'A', '2015-01-21 17:09:19', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
