(2005, 'YXu4QRN_lnU', NULL, 'The encounter of retail with eRetail - Part 1', 5, '', NULL, '', 26, 'In a panel discussion held at the Indian Retail and eRetail Congress 2015 organised by Franchise India, representatives from some of the emerging retailer brands in the country shared their views on the online war between retail and eRetail and how franchising and real estate can act as a catalyst for brick-and &ndash;mortar as eRetail has exploded big time. ', 'Indian Retail Congress, Retail, eRetail, Real Estate, Franchising', '16:25', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3089, 'A', '2015-10-30 08:56:53', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
