(2010, 'anbYbYBNJLc', NULL, 'The relationship between consumers and brands - Part 1', 5, '', NULL, '', 26, 'In a panel discussion held at the Indian Retail and eRetail Congress 2015 organised by Franchise India, some well known faces of Retail and eRetail landscape participated to share their views on the changing dynamics of the retail business in the country. They also spoke about how todays consumers wants to stay ahead with the times and how they want brands to come to them rather than they going to the brands.', 'Indian Retail Congress, Retail, eRetail, Fashion, Consumer Behaviour', '20:31', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3033, 'A', '2015-10-30 09:04:53', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
