(2013, 'wgr2cTxzYNw', NULL, 'No more mass markets in Retail', 5, '', NULL, '', 26, 'During a panel discussion held at the Indian Retail and eRetail Congress 2015 organised by Franchise India, Abhishek Sharma, CMO, GOQii spoke on the emerging segmentation trends in millennials. He said how a brand interacts with its consumers is very important today and the best endorser for a brand can be its existing users. ', 'Abhishek Sharma, GOQii, Indian Retail Congress, Technology, Wearable', '06:41', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2699, 'A', '2015-10-30 09:09:49', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2014, 'r8box6b6a1k', NULL, 'Ecommerce particularly important for licensed Sports merchandise, says Martin Brochstein from LIMA ', 4, '', NULL, '', 23, 'While eCommerce has done wonders to the entire licensing industry, it has been of paramount importance especially for licensed sports merchandise by connecting the world, asserted  Martin Brochstein, SVP-Industry Relations and Information, LIMA Worldwide while speaking to License India at the 8th Brand Licensing conference in India. ', 'Martin Brochstein, LIMA, Brand Licensing Conference 2015, Sports Licensing, Brand Licensing and eCommerce, Licensing in India, Character Licensing', '03:05', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 4050, 'A', '2015-10-31 08:51:08', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2015, 'k2SFQ1pwqN4', NULL, 'Happy to be with Bradford, says Gaurav Gera', 4, '', NULL, '', 23, 'Actor Gaurav Gera, now a hit sensation with the Shopkeepa and Chutki series on BIG MAGIC and 92.7 Big fm, Gera has initiated licensing program for Shopkeeper by Gaurav Gera together with Bradford License India. Speaking at Brand Licensing Conference 2015, Gera shares about choosing Bradford as an agent to extend the brand in the market. ', 'Gaurav Gera, Shopkeeper by Gaurav Gera, Brand Licensing Conference 2015, Bradford Licesne India, Brand Licensing, Licensing in India, Character Licensing', '01:55', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2688, 'A', '2015-10-31 08:53:31', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2016, 'AvvcFEOI1Xg', NULL, 'eCommerce has boost licensing PAN India', 5, '', NULL, '', 26, 'During a session at the Indian Retail and eRetail Congress 2015 organised by Franchise India, Anand Singh, Director, Cartoon Network Enterprise, South Asia shared his thoughts on how eRetail has revolutionized the whole licensing model in the country. As per Anand, all format of retail in India will co-exist and will complement each other in one way or the other.', 'Anand Singh, Cartoon Newtwork Enterprise, Licensing, Indian Retail Congress', '04:50', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3857, 'A', '2015-10-31 08:56:32', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2017, 'kQCdZKfQ_5U', NULL, 'Understanding data and acquiring customers ', 4, '', NULL, '', 22, 'During a session at the Indian Retail and eRetail Congress 2015 organised by Franchise India, Bijaei Jayaraj, Founder & CEO, Loyalty Rewardz Mngt. Ltd., talked about how the entire retail industry is suffering due to lack of consumer data and he also shared his thoughts on particular perspective of consumer acquisition.', 'Bijaei Jayaraj, Loyalty Rewardz, Big Data, Retail, Indian Retail Congress', '19:03', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3391, 'A', '2015-10-31 08:58:12', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2018, 'jtU3Yxrx6Js', NULL, 'Changing dynamics of Indian retail (online vs offline)', 4, '', NULL, '', 22, 'During a panel discussion held at the Indian Retail and eRetail Congress 2015 organised by Franchise India, Manish Sharma, MD, Panasonic India & South Asia & President, CEAMA, took the dialogue forward by sharing his thoughts on the change from manufacturers can sell to era of creating a sell-through channel to how quality technology came into play.', 'Manish Sharma, Panasonic, CEAMA, CDIT, Indian Retail Congress ', '10:41', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3825, 'A', '2015-10-31 08:59:23', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2019, 'ANpiuQBtT_k', NULL, 'Why retail runs in India ', 4, '', NULL, '', 22, 'During a panel discussion held at the Indian Retail and eRetail Congress 2015 organised by Franchise India, Damodar Mall, CEO Grocery Retail, Reliance Retail Limited addressed the audience with some basics of retail and how quickly consumer behaviour changes. He also said that it is never an emerging customer but an assertive customer.', 'Damodar Mall, Reliance Retail, Grocery, Indian Retail Congress', '20:14', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3526, 'A', '2015-10-31 09:00:35', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2020, 'tmbEFT_ALDY', NULL, 'Gaps in modern retail  ', 4, '', NULL, '', 22, 'During a panel discussion held at the Indian Retail and eRetail Congress 2015 organised by Franchise India, Dipak Agarwal, CEO- Operations & Strategy, DLF Brands Limited shared his thoughts on the nature of todays retailers and how the world describes them as a creator, an innovator or a destructor. He also spoke about the modern retail and the innovations happening to acquire more and more customers.', 'Dipak Agarwal, DLF Brands, Retail, Indian Retail Congress', '15:17', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2597, 'A', '2015-10-31 09:02:40', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2021, 'JyCgcdKTr-U', NULL, 'Overload of choices in Retail ', 4, '', NULL, '', 22, 'During a panel discussion held at the Indian Retail and eRetail Congress 2015 organised by Franchise India, Prof. Piyush Kumar Sinha, Professor- Retailing & Marketing, IIM-A shared his thoughts on reason behind customer visiting your store or website and not purchasing. He said consumer retention is a big challenge in all formats of retail in India. ', 'Piyush Kumar, Retail, Indian Retail Congress', '06:25', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3201, 'A', '2015-10-31 09:05:28', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2022, 'JGUtn4_JMnA', NULL, 'Rovios Anurag Sachdeva on 100 million downloads in India ', 1, '', NULL, '', 10, 'Rovio &ndash; a digital oriented brand has carved a niche for itself in Indian market with more than 100 million plus downloads. Anurag Sachdeva from Rovio talks about the immense recall value of the brand and its future plans for Indian market while speaking to License India at the 8th Brand Licensing conference in India. ', 'Anurag Sachdeva, LIMA, Rovio, Angry Birds, Angry Birds Star Wars, Brand Licensing Conference 2015, Licensing in India', '03:00', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2697, 'A', '2015-11-02 09:21:40', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2023, 'aH7FL25vPhc', NULL, 'NBAs Yannick Colaco on sports licensing & value proposition by retailers', 1, '', NULL, '', 11, 'Digital content has already revolutionized the licensing industry, particularly sports licensing, which has seen a shift in consumption pattern due to advent of live sports, asserted Yannick Colaco, Managing Director, NBA while speaking to License India at the 8th Brand Licensing conference in India. ', 'Yannick Colaco, NBA, NBA Jam, Satnam Singh Bhamara, NBA draft, Brand Licensing Conference 2015, Licensing in India', '02:24', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 4651, 'A', '2015-11-02 09:24:00', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2024, '0ljZcaw0cr4', NULL, 'Rohit Bal offers Balance for the upper middle class                                  ', 46, '', NULL, '', 48, 'Rohit Bal Designs has come up with sub brand Balance to tap the upper mid segment, which is to be licensed out. speaking to License India at the 8th Brand Licensing conference in India, Akhilesh Sharma, General Manager, Rohit Bal Designs Pvt. Ltd. talks about Balance and the criteria for choosing the licensee for the sub brand. ', 'Akhilesh Sharma, Rohit Bal Designs, Rohit Bal, Balance by Rohit Bal, Brand Licensing Conference 2015, Licensing in India, fashion licensing ', '03:26', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1978, 'A', '2015-11-03 08:59:31', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2025, 'R6Z1OspkMX8', NULL, 'Being Human to launch actiwear, says mandhana', 46, '', NULL, '', 48, 'Mandhana Industries &ndash; the official licensee of Being Human - The Salman Khan Foundation, is soon launching actiwear and apparel range for boys, revealed Manish Mandhana, Managing Director, Mandhana Industries, while speaking to License India. ', 'Manish Mandhana, Being Human, Salman Khan, The Salman Khan Foundation, Brand Licensing Conference 2015, Licensing in India, celebrity licensing ', '03:50', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2739, 'A', '2015-11-03 09:01:23', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2026, '-CD04Bnr9dA', NULL, 'Owning a Loyalty Business', 7, '', NULL, '', 35, 'Arpit Agarwal is the Co-Founder, OneLoyalCard & Director at Globe Capital Market Limited. Talking at Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, he shares How has he come up with the idea of building a loyalty business for customers.', 'Food Business, Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, One Loyal Card, Loyalty Program', '02:30', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2294, 'A', '2015-11-04 09:03:02', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2027, 'Ua-f8Oql4FM', NULL, 'Boozing the Beer business', 7, '', NULL, '', 35, 'Rahul Singh is the Founder & CEO of The Beer Cafe. With 25 locations operational within a short span of three years, it has already become the largest, fastest and most profitable Alco-beverage service brand in India. Speaking at Indian Restaurant Congress, 2015, Singh shares about the expansion plan of brand focusing on his boozing business. ', 'Rahul Singh, Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, Franchise India, The Beer Cafe, Restaurant Business', '02:20', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3056, 'A', '2015-11-04 09:04:37', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2028, '1Hxqq8QLJlk', NULL, 'Maintaining a cordial relation with franchisee', 7, '', NULL, '', 35, 'Sharad Sachdeva is the CEO of Lite Bite Foods, one of the fastest growing restaurant chain in India which owns amazing brands like Zambar, Punjab Grill and the newly launched Artful Baker. Addressing at Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, Sachdeva shares about the franchisee- franchisor relation. ', 'Sharad Sachdeva, Lite Bite Foods, Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, Franchise India, Restaurant Business', '03:19', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3129, 'A', '2015-11-04 09:05:38', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2029, 'brKpCyNG71w', NULL, 'GIONEE to manufacture phones in India ', 5, '', NULL, '', 27, 'Arvind R Vohra, CEO and Managing Director of Gionee India speaks to Retailer Media about Gionee powerhouse smart-phone ELIFE E8, the company plans to start manufacturing in India before the next fiscal and photography becoming the main reason to buy smart-phones today.', 'ELIFE E8, Arvind Vohra, Gionee India, Smart-phones, camera, photography, India. Launch', '03:24', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 4004, 'A', '2015-11-06 08:52:33', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2030, 'CE5EOGKDKtA', NULL, 'Omni-channel experience for end users ', 5, '', NULL, '', 26, 'During a session at the Indian Retail and eRetail Congress 2015 organised by Franchise India, Ronak Samantray, Co-Founder, Now Floats, spoke about the changing consumer behavior and how they prefer location-based searches to buy their products. He also talked about how the market is moving towards omni-channel strategies to aid their end users in all hemisphere of retailing.', 'Ronak Samantray, Now Floats, Omni-Channel, Retail, Indian Retail Congress', '11:38', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2687, 'A', '2015-11-06 08:59:43', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2031, '3vh9aoRoZQs', NULL, 'Gen Y, a potential target group in retail', 5, '', NULL, '', 26, 'During a panel discussion held at the Indian Retail and eRetail Congress 2015 organised by Franchise India, Ruchira Jaitly, Sr. Director &ndash;Social Beverages, PepsiCo India, shed light on the impact of retail revolution in the market and how Gen Y have fueled this change. She also spoke about how to connect with the new generation and make them stick your brand/services.', 'Ruchira Jaitly, PepsiCo India, Retail, Indian Retail Congress', '09:43', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2852, 'A', '2015-11-06 09:02:12', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2032, 'iAISHEm3QYs', NULL, 'Westernising businesses in India, a must', 5, '', NULL, '', 26, 'During a panel discussion held at the Indian Retail and eRetail Congress 2015 organised by Franchise India, Samir Modi, Managing Director, Modi Enterprises, spoke about his ideas and thoughts of westernising brand in Indian diaspora. He also said that consumers today are in a dichotomy of being an Indian but I am no less than other people across the world.', 'Samir Modi, Modi Enterprises, Reail, Indian Retail Congress', '20:16', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3269, 'A', '2015-11-06 09:03:16', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2033, '0mW0Y81J10Q', NULL, 'Home and Furniture: An Experiential Buy!', 5, '', NULL, '', 27, 'Nimit Kumar, CTO, FabFurnish talks to Retailer media about his role and responsibility, the expanding portfolio of the company and future plans. He also spoke on the importance of choosing the right sellers and how the integration of offline and online will help the customer have a seamless experience.', 'FabFurnish, CTO, Nimit Kumar, offline channel, sellers, home solutions', '11:01', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 4561, 'A', '2015-11-06 09:06:23', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2034, 'EiKbo12vIYk', NULL, 'How technology is helping restaurant business grow by Vivek Kapoor', 7, '', NULL, '', 35, 'As part of the founding team, Vivek Kapoor heads the Pan India Sales and Operations team at Dineout.co.in. Vivek is a peoples person, which makes him proficient in handling all office operations, including hiring and managing team members at Dineout. For him, employees are the backbone of the company and have contributed to his success overall, pillaring his progress professionally. Speaking at Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, he shares How Technology is shaping the future of Indian food industry.', 'Vivek Kapoor, Dineout, Times Internet, Online Food Space, Food-Tech, Franchise India, Restaurant Congress 2015', '02:52', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 4050, 'A', '2015-11-06 09:09:25', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2035, '1v0-__tM9ic', NULL, 'LENOVO IS No.1 4G BRAND IN INDIA', 5, '', NULL, '', 27, 'Sudhin Mathur, Director for Smartphones, Lenovo India spoke to Retailer Media at the India launch of Lenovo Vibe P1 and P1m. He spoke about the two new phone launched by the group, the festive-ready retail industry and how Lenovo has sold 3 million devices and become the number one 4G brand in the country.', 'Sudhin Mathur, Smartphones, India, Launch, Lenovo, P1, P1m, festive discounts, flash sales, Flipkart', '03:07', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3530, 'A', '2015-11-07 09:00:54', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2036, '3352OotB3u0', NULL, 'MOTO X STYLE LAUNCHES IN STYLE', 5, '', NULL, '', 27, 'Amit Boni, Motorola India Head spoke to Retailer Media at the launch of their flagship phone Moto X Style in New Delhi. He also runs us through its features, talks on the Groups future plans and role of eCommerce in the retail industry.', 'Amit Boni, Motorola, India, Moto X Style, India launch', '01:53', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2803, 'A', '2015-11-07 09:03:10', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2037, 'MvF0VEfGuQY', NULL, 'ONLINE SLOWERED THE GROWTH OF MALLS', 5, '', NULL, '', 27, 'Rajneesh Mahajan, MD of Inorbit Malls Pvt Ltd spoke to Retailer Media on the convergence of online and offline spaces, the dip in growth of malls, rentals and future plans. He also spoke on the rising footfall during the festive season and how Inrobit is going to celebrate with its customers.', 'Inorbit Malls, Rajneesh Mahajan, Inorbit Malls, customer evolution, online sales, touch and feel, festive season, Mumbai', '13:00', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3167, 'A', '2015-11-07 09:04:36', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2038, '1VURfgfEDRQ', NULL, 'Changing dynamics and digitization of Retail ', 5, '', NULL, '', 26, 'In a panel discussion held at the Indian Retail and eRetail Congress 2015 organised by Franchise India, some of Indias modern eRetailer shared their views about the need of digitization in the typical retail models. They were of the firm opinion that today the consumers are changing and prefer various channels to shop (online & offline) and the best retailer is the one who is there on all of these channels. ', 'Retail, eRetail, Digitisation, Technology, India Retail Congress', '21:33', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 4614, 'A', '2015-11-07 09:18:04', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0);
