(2039, 'Y9PRR-KdFTw', NULL, 'Grabbing lion share of unorganized market: Flipkart', 4, '', NULL, '', 22, 'During the Indian Retail and eRetail Congress 2015, Retailer Media caught up with Anil Goteti, Senior Director- Business (Home & Furniture), Flipkart, to know more about Flipkarts foray into online home and furniture market and the response so far. Here he talked about how tier II and III cities have picked up the pace and a lot of sales are coming through mobile.', 'Indian Retail, eRetail Congress, Flipkart, Anil Goteti, online home and furniture', '20:23', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 5842, 'A', '2015-11-18 17:24:24', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2040, 'gF-upJTUVAg', NULL, 'DBC, a one-stop-shop for all Building Care needs', 5, '', NULL, '', 27, 'During the Franchise India Show 2015, Retailer Media caught up with Itisha Chauhan, Director - Business Head, Diamond Building Care Ltd., to know more about the emerging utility services in the country. Here she also explained about the requirement of such services and how DBC has catered in meeting all service and maintenance needs. ', 'Itisha Chauhan, DBC Care, Utility services', '05:57', 'V', NULL, 'en', 13, 13, 63, 5595, 'A', '2015-11-19 11:11:09', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2041, 'Y5xvzVvWjZM', NULL, 'Fashion as a category is lucrative & exciting', 5, '', NULL, '', 27, 'During the Franchise India Show 2015, Siddhant Rana, Head Business Development, Exclusively.com caught up with Retailer Media and shared his thoughts on transforming Exclusively.com from the largest to the ultimate fashion destination of the country. He also spoke about the changing dynamics of online fashion industry and how eCommerce can leverage different channels for a better consumer experience.    ', 'Siddhant Rana, Exclusively.com, Retailer Media, online fashion ', '03:44', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 5240, 'A', '2015-11-19 12:22:09', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2042, 'JWDjzQywY3M', NULL, 'Franchise India 2015 - A Grand Celebration of Ideas, thoughts and Enterprise', 1, '', NULL, '', 13, 'A teaser of Franchise India Show 2015, that was captured live in action at the show this year on October 18-19.', 'Franchise India 2015, start a business', '0:30', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 4, 2127, 'A', '2015-11-19 12:37:28', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2043, 'dPvDz8-KtoQ', NULL, 'Smiley World more versatile than Smiley Original', 46, '', NULL, '', 48, 'Mandy Kaur, Brand Manager APAC, SmileyWorld Ltd. / Smiley APAC Ltd speaks about the product lines of Smiley and the variations between Smiley Originals and Smiley World. ', 'Brandspoke, Mandy Kaur, Smiley APAC, Smiley Originals, Smiley Classic, Brand Licensing Conference 2015, Licensing in India', '03:01', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2032, 'A', '2015-11-21 09:12:53', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2044, 'VCfd72dp-50', NULL, '97% brand recognition for Smiley', 46, '', NULL, '', 48, 'Brandspoke is helping Smiley group venture across categories in India through licensing. Speaking with license India, Pritti Ravindra, Director, Brandspoke shares about the phenomenal recognition for Smiley and the parameters for an ideal licensee.  ', 'Brandspoke, Pritti Ravindra, Smiley APAC, Smiley Originals, Smiley Classic, Brand Licensing Conference 2015, Licensing in India', '04:33', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 2, 2622, 'A', '2015-11-21 09:16:01', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2045, 'ufesPckpBFE', NULL, 'Brand Sanjeev Kapoor not focused on instant money', 46, '', NULL, '', 48, 'Translating the love-for-food, Brand Sanjeev Kapoor has introduced a range of house-ware products under licensing agreement. Stating the Brand as not a mere deal-maker, but a home-grown brand, Vishal Y. Sinha, Business Head, Brand Sanjeev Kapoor says that the brand aims at long term relations through licensing instead of instant money. ', 'Vishal Y. Sinha, Brand Sanjeev Kapoor, Chef Sanjeev Kapoor, Brand Licensing Conference 2015, Brand Licensing and eCommerce, Licensing in India', '05:35', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3440, 'A', '2015-11-21 09:18:08', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2046, 'BEX-9F6RPH4', NULL, 'eRetail models seeking investors attention - Part1', 4, '', NULL, '', 22, 'In a motivating panel discussion held at the Indian Retail and eRetail Congress 2015 organised by Franchise India, some of the leading investors of retail industry shared their views on how the industry is evolving and what would be the runway like, in terms of investments. They also spoke about the USPs investors look before inject money into a retail/e-retail business and how entrepreneurs can leverage the internet and do commerce or a business.', 'Investment, Retail, eCommerce, Indian Retail Congress', '16:44', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2657, 'A', '2015-11-21 14:19:11', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2047, 'n3X7sTeNSDE', NULL, 'eRetail models seeking investors attention - Part2', 4, '', NULL, '', 22, 'In a motivating panel discussion held at the Indian Retail and eRetail Congress 2015 organised by Franchise India, some of the leading investors of retail industry shared their views on how the industry is evolving and what would be the runway like, in terms of investments. They also spoke about the USPs investors look before inject money into a retail/e-retail business and how entrepreneurs can leverage the internet and do commerce or a business.', 'Investment, Retail, eCommerce, Indian Retail Congress', '24:41', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 4480, 'A', '2015-11-21 14:20:39', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2048, 'Nh87biw469U', NULL, 'Putting in Perspective Investment Strategies - Part 1', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Investing in restaurant business has become part of the big money play. With gross margins going up to 60 per cent upwards, investors are today hungry for the brands that sell well. During the Capital Connection session at 5th Indian Restaurant Congress, experts shared their view on the growth of investment taking place in the food business giving a good surge to the food-start-ups and quirky concepts. The panelist also expressed that Eating out has become a fashion, and investment in this segment is the part of the scene of big domestic consumption. Today, 50 per cent of Indians are eating at least 8 times every month which is leveraging great growth for restaurants luring investors to own that brand which has grown three folds in last few months.', 'Investment, Food Business, Restaurant Business, Restaurant Congress, Everstone Capital, Franchise India', '24:45', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 5170, 'A', '2015-11-23 16:55:51', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2049, 'I4l1_bF9agw', NULL, 'Putting in Perspective Investment Strategies - Part 2', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Investing in restaurant business has become part of the big money play. With gross margins going up to 60 per cent upwards, investors are today hungry for the brands that sell well. During the Capital Connection session at 5th Indian Restaurant Congress, experts shared their view on the growth of investment taking place in the food business giving a good surge to the food-start-ups and quirky concepts. The panelist also expressed that Eating out has become a fashion, and investment in this segment is the part of the scene of big domestic consumption. Today, 50 per cent of Indians are eating at least 8 times every month which is leveraging great growth for restaurants luring investors to own that brand which has grown three folds in last few months.', 'Investment, Food Business, Restaurant Business, Restaurant Congress, Everstone Capital, Franchise India', '22:21', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 5558, 'A', '2015-11-23 16:56:52', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2050, 'BwtVCytIR4c', NULL, 'mCommerce is the way forward in Indian retail spectrum - Part1', 4, '', NULL, '', 22, 'In an appealing panel discussion held at the Indian Retail and eRetail Congress 2015 organised by Franchise India, some of countrys well known eRetailers shared their views on how the retail industry is drifting towards a new spectrum called mobile commerce (mCommerce). They also spoke about how mobile penetration across the country has help this format of retail to reach the inflation point and what they think is the runway like.   ', 'mCommerce, Retail, Technology, Indian Retail Congress', '20:49', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 5385, 'A', '2015-11-26 15:35:21', NULL, NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0),
(2051, 'dLwr7WVSETs', NULL, 'mCommerce, Retail, Technology, Indian Retail Congress - Part2', 4, '', NULL, '', 22, 'In an appealing panel discussion held at the Indian Retail and eRetail Congress 2015 organised by Franchise India, some of countrys well known eRetailers shared their views on how the retail industry is drifting towards a new spectrum called mobile commerce (mCommerce). They also spoke about how mobile penetration across the country has help this format of retail to reach the inflation point and what they think is the runway like.   ', 'mCommerce, Retail, Technology, Indian Retail Congress', '11:56', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 5311, 'A', '2015-11-26 15:36:42', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2052, 'AhRgGmbZRvQ', NULL, 'Feeding the Future - Part2', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'In the last two years, the industry witnessed so much discussion about innovation, tapping the regular customers, because they are the one who is bringing the money back. But, beyond all these will push the restaurant into growth mode is that emotional connect which one need to introduce into the brand. To get more insight on the same this session on How people are feeding in India would give a detail about the industry insight.', 'Eating Out, Food Trend, Emotional Connect, Restaurant Congress 2015, Franchise India', '19:40', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1940, 'A', '2015-11-28 08:43:59', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2053, 'LtE5KL066D8', NULL, 'Feeding the Future - Part1', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'In the last two years, the industry witnessed so much discussion about innovation, tapping the regular customers, because they are the one who is bringing the money back. But, beyond all these will push the restaurant into growth mode is that emotional connect which one need to introduce into the brand. To get more insight on the same this session on How people are feeding in India would give a detail about the industry insight.', 'Eating Out, Food Trend, Emotional Connect, Restaurant Congress 2015, Franchise India', '24:00', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1659, 'A', '2015-11-28 08:45:19', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2054, 'x20iqZ-d7P0', NULL, 'Eyeing big business with new products offerings: Astaberry Director', 9, '', NULL, '', 43, 'Astaberry, a leading manufacturer and exporter of herbal cosmetics and personal care solutions from the house of BHIMSAINI, pioneer in the Kajal Industry & a leading manufacturer and marketer of Ayurvedic skincare, healthcare and eye care products since 1950. Known for its wine and fruit base skincare products, Astaberry has big plans to elaborate its product offering. In an exclusive conversation with WI Bureau, Achal Arya, Director, Astaberry disclosed his business plans with the brand.', 'AstaBerry, herbal cosmetic, Ayurveda, skincare products, wellness', '07:35', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 5825, 'A', '2015-11-28 08:47:40', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2055, 'g1M7_vTIQyQ', NULL, 'Western brand unfolding success in India - Part 1', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'With food being one of the main markets of elaborate opportunities, the international brands are giving much attention to the regulations and legalities in a bid to deliver high class, globally acclaimed products to their fussy Indian counterparts. Reason is Indians are known for being selective and choosy in picking food and the food regulation and safety is something which indeed demands acute care and attention to make a niche in the market here. Speaking at Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, panellists shares the opportunity for the global chains in India.', 'Western Brands, Food Business, Global QSR, Burger King, Chilis, Food Service, Restaurant Congress 2015', '18:55', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 4094, 'A', '2015-11-30 16:59:39', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2056, 'ERbR14uLihE', NULL, 'Western brand unfolding success in India - Part 3', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'With food being one of the main markets of elaborate opportunities, the international brands are giving much attention to the regulations and legalities in a bid to deliver high class, globally acclaimed products to their fussy Indian counterparts. Reason is Indians are known for being selective and choosy in picking food and the food regulation and safety is something which indeed demands acute care and attention to make a niche in the market here. Speaking at Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, panellists shares the opportunity for the global chains in India.', 'Western Brands, Food Business, Global QSR, Burger King, Chili’s, Food Service, Restaurant Congress 2015', '13:14', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 4136, 'A', '2015-12-01 14:14:43', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2057, 'HRfOvgx872I', NULL, 'Western brand unfolding success in India - Part 2', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'With food being one of the main markets of elaborate opportunities, the international brands are giving much attention to the regulations and legalities in a bid to deliver high class, globally acclaimed products to their fussy Indian counterparts. Reason is Indians are known for being selective and choosy in picking food and the food regulation and safety is something which indeed demands acute care and attention to make a niche in the market here. Speaking at Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, panellists shares the opportunity for the global chains in India.', 'Western Brands, Food Business, Global QSR, Burger King, Chili’s, Food Service, Restaurant Congress 2015', '20:10', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 4325, 'A', '2015-12-01 14:18:17', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2058, 'm314SVmDQSM', NULL, 'Innovating into New Markets - Part 1', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Whenever new brands enter into an unknown place or demography, they take franchising as a route to expand the service as the franchisee being a local partner is well aware about the best location in the particular area where the brand is going to open its outlet. Meanwhile, each store needs to be profitable, because many a times, franchisees do not average out the profits across stores, for him, his store has to make money. Listen, what panellists have to share on expansion of their brands.', 'Franchise Brands, Restaurant Chains, Franchise India, Food Franchising, Expansion, Restaurant Congress 2015', '16:19', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2545, 'A', '2015-12-02 09:08:04', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2059, 'jnOLdw2kYD4', NULL, 'Innovating into new markets - Part 2', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Whenever new brands enter into an unknown place or demography, they take franchising as a route to expand the service as the franchisee being a local partner is well aware about the best location in the particular area where the brand is going to open its outlet. Meanwhile, each store needs to be profitable, because many a times, franchisees do not average out the profits across stores, for him, his store has to make money. Listen, what panellists have to share on expansion of their brands.', 'Franchise Brands, Restaurant Chains, Franchise India, Food Franchising, Expansion, Restaurant Congress 2015', '20:35', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2333, 'A', '2015-12-03 08:59:52', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2060, 'FexsNK8A_Dg', NULL, 'Disrupting traditional payment mechanism through Digital Currency', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'In an appealing panel discussion held at the Indian Retail and eRetail Congress 2015 organised by Franchise India, some of industrys major players from mobile payment segment participated and shared their views on how consumers are moving towards a digital revolution in payments. They also spoke about the challenges these eWallet providers are facing in term of acceptability, access points and technological hindrances.', 'mWallets, Payment, Digitisation, eRetail, Indian Retail Congress', '19:38', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 4292, 'A', '2015-12-03 09:03:25', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2061, 'ZwHkimT85dI', NULL, 'World Franchise Congress on ET Now', 1, '2061.jpg', NULL, '', 10, 'The annual World Franchise conference laid a foundation for building a big vision in Indian Franchising. Jointly brought to you by Franchise India and PepsiCo was held on 24th November 2015 at Hotel Pullman, Aerocity, New Delhi. It was India\\\'s foremost opportunity to network with corporate peers and gain insight into the opportunities and answers to the challenges associated with developing and maintaining an effective franchise program. \\r\\n\\r\\nAlong with the congress, World Franchise Congress presented the country\\\'s most prestigious awards in the arena of Franchise Leadership. The awards aim to recognize and felicitate Achievers, Innovators, smartest futurists and franchise leaders from all over the world and who have contributed significantly towards the development of current and franchise future trends in business, government and technology and society.\\r\\n', 'World Franchise Congress, Awards, Franchise Conference, Franchise Awards, Pepsico, Franchise India, ET Now, Rajiv Pratap Rudy, National Franchise Convention, World Franchise Congress Promo, Industry Conference, Franchise Summit, Andy Williams, Shiva shivakumar, Samudra Bhattacharya, Franchisor, Franchisee, Channel development, B2B conference ', '1:08', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 4778, 'A', '2015-12-04 13:09:56', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2062, '9O5iEzblikI', NULL, 'Understanding customers buying behaviour', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'During a panel discussion held at the India Retail and eRetail Congress organised by Franchise India, Anubhav Sonthalia, COO & Co-Founder, Sokrati shared an interesting presentation on customer behaviour and how that can help SMBs to sell better. He also spoke about how to target the right customers with the right products or services using big data and analytics to help them make a decision faster.  ', 'Retail, Marketing, Sokrati, SMBs, Indian Retail Congress', '16:33', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2772, 'A', '2015-12-09 11:10:32', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2063, 'QkVDkqsh230', NULL, 'Leveraging big data and IoT for better retailing', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'During a panel discussion held at the India Retail and eRetail Congress organised by Franchise India, Dr. Anthony Kilili, Capability Director, Communication & Media, dunnhumby India, shared an interesting presentation on the how important is big data for a retail business. He also shared his thoughts on the emerging IoT (Internet of Things) and other analysis measures that have evolved and have given retail a cutting edge advantage. ', 'Technology, IoT, Big Data, Retail, Indian Retail Congress', '17:41', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3673, 'A', '2015-12-09 11:12:16', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2064, 'SR80vHUZMaQ', NULL, 'Upcoming trends in payment space ', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'During a panel discussion held at the India Retail and eRetail Congress organised by Franchise India, Nilesh Patel, CEO, EasyPay Ovt. Ltd. spoke about the sprouting payment industry and consumers behavbiour towards the same. He also spoke about the ease that the industry is providing to the consumers such as buying online and paying offline. He believes that the Indian consumers are evolving and so are their habits and with this evolution, payment service providers of the country have huge opportunities to infuse new modes of payment in retail.', 'Payments, Mobile Wallet, eCommerce, Indian Retail Congress', '10:17', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 3, 3490, 'A', '2015-12-09 11:14:19', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2065, 'gRqmqK4TEak', NULL, 'The new-age retail ecosystem', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Starting the Indian Retail and eRetail Congress 2015, Ritu Marya, Editor-in-Chief, Franchise India, extended her gratitude to all the speakers and delegates present at the show. She also opened the discussion pointing out the revolution happening in the retail and eRetail space of the country. She explained her thoughts and experience of talking to the industry players and understanding their prospective in terms of growth, innovations and opportunity and the competition within', 'Retail, eRetail, Omni-Channel Retailing, Technology, Indian Retail Congress', '16:04', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2578, 'A', '2015-12-09 11:19:59', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2066, 'L3Bzu5nWLow', NULL, 'Rural customers with urban like buying patter', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'L Oreal, Personal Care, Retail, Indian Retail Congress', 'In a panel discussion held at the Indian Retail and eRetail Congress 2015, Satyaki Ghosh, Director- Consumer Products Division, L Oreal India shared a brilliant presentation on the consumer trends in personal care space. He also spoke about how the brands are adapting global phenomenon and make in Indian and the vice-versa to woo the customers. He also believes that digital has changed the face of retail and it holds a strong potential in the coming future.', '18:51', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2323, 'A', '2015-12-09 11:24:07', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2067, 'WsjE_VzTBSY', NULL, 'One stop business solutions leveraging technology', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'During a panel discussion held at the India Retail and eRetail Congress organised by Franchise India, Jitender Sharma, Business Head- Strategic Business Vertical, Ricoh India Ltd., shared an interesting presentation on Ricoh profile and model that help retailers in making business strategies. He also spoke about how Ricoh help retailers in testing their products/services and increasing workplace efficiency through IT integration and process automation.', 'Business Solution, Strategy Making, Technology, Retail, eRetail, Indian Retail Congress', '10:11', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 4093, 'A', '2015-12-09 11:25:26', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2068, 'IEG3S6OiFxc', NULL, 'How convenient meals are catching up the ground by Chef Sabyasachi Gorai', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'After receiving the most coveted National Tourism Award, 2011 for Best Chef of India, Awarded by the President, Chef Saby quit his job as Culinary Director of Olive bar and kitchen, and started his culinary academy to nurture and mentor young Chefs. Addressing the audience at Indian Restaurant Congress, Saby shares, how convenient meals are catching up the ground these days, with people becoming global and more nuclear families coming in. ', 'Chef Saby, Chef Award, Indian Restaurant Congress, Culinary Director, Convenient Meals, Healthy Eating ', '19:53', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2671, 'A', '2015-12-09 11:29:33', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2069, 'NS6_VIh45Qo', NULL, 'Growing Trends of Casual Dining Chain', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Over the years casual dining trend as fast picked up the ongoing restaurant war in India. Speaking at Indian Restaurant Congress, Griffith David shares about How the casual dining chains are helping in the advance growth of the restaurant business.', 'Bread Basket, Subway, Casual Ding Chain, Restaurant Trend', '14:55', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2124, 'A', '2015-12-10 14:58:26', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2070, 'NqjwVZSo4hA', NULL, 'Flash talks with Start-ups', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Alok is the founder & CEO at Yumist. Prior to this he has built multiple tech startups across India, US and Singapore in the fields of e-commerce, consumer internet, mobile gaming and digital strategy consulting. He has also served as CMO at Zomato and DealsAndYou. Talking at Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, he speaks about innovation in restaurant business.', 'Start-ups, Food Business, Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, Yumist ', '12:55', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3133, 'A', '2015-12-14 09:22:47', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2071, '9Lut8yA7geU', NULL, 'Latest food trends ', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Masterchef Sanjeev Kapoor has been conferred the Best Chef of India award by the Government of India and has represented India in the World Association of Chefs Societies (WACS) in South Korea introducing ancient Indian way of Ayurvedic cooking. He is also known as the Rachel Ray of India, his website www.sanjeevkapoor.com has more than 10,000 recipes, attracts more than eight million page views per month. Talking at Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, he shares food trends of today and tomorrow.', 'Chef, Food Business, Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, Sanjeev Kapoor, Masterchef', '19:09', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3590, 'A', '2015-12-14 09:24:23', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2072, 'LOvY1WOfWjg', NULL, 'Reinventing the tradition', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Chef Michael Swamy has more than 20 years of experience. He is known for Food styling & photography, Chef Michael has creatively contributed to a number of cookery books. His cookbook, The East Indian Kitchen (2010) has also won The Gourmand Award in Paris (2012) for Best Indian Cookbook. The Indian Chefs Association has listed him as one of the Top 50 Chefs in India in 2012 and again in 2013. Talking at Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, he shares how people consume.', 'Chef, Food stylish, Food Business, Indian Restaurant Congress 2015 ', '08:58', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3619, 'A', '2015-12-14 09:25:30', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2073, 'M5FxfBuC7us', NULL, 'Manish Agarwal, Chief Executive Officer, Gati Kausar', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Manish Agarwal is the CEO of Gati Kausar, Gatis cold chain subsidiary. Manish has been instrumental in giving the business a new direction, creating integrated supply chain capability and enhancing synergy with the rest of Gatis capabilities and products.', 'Supply Chain, Food Business, Gati Kausar, Cold Chain, Food Processing ', '05:23', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 4135, 'A', '2015-12-16 09:07:41', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2074, '6rdFvCCljyo', NULL, 'Pushpinder Singh, Founder, Travelkhana.com', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Pushpinder founded Travelkhana.com which is the worlds first on demand marketplace for travelers on the move. In its first avatar 10 million passengers who travel every day in Long distance Indian trains can order the food of their choice from over 150 stations across the country in more than 5000 trains.  Speaking at 5th Indian Restaurant Congress, Singh shares about his growth plans.', 'Travelkhana, Food on Wheel, Train, IRCTC, Food Business', '07:18', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 4578, 'A', '2015-12-16 09:09:01', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2075, 'kbqQZXnjAOM', NULL, 'Chef Manish Mehrotra, Celebrity Chef & Corporate Chef-Luxury Dining, Old World Hospitality Pvt. Ltd. (Indian Accent)', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Chef Manish Mehrotra is the most Promising Young Chef of India. By launching the path-breaking contemporary Indian menu of Indian Accent, at the Manor, New Delhi in 2009, Chef Mehrotra reinvented Delhis fine dining scene. Talking at 5th Indian Restaurant Congress, Mehrotra shares about Building one of the most celebrated and acclaimed restaurant globally.', 'Chef, Food, Menu Trend, Indian Accent, Executive Chef, Old World Hospitality ', '08:43', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 5041, 'A', '2015-12-16 09:10:28', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2076, 'WfkHz65gjQc', NULL, 'Chef J P Singh, Executive Chef, Bukhara- ITC Maurya', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Chef Singh is 7-time winner of the Restaurant Magazine Award for being amongst the Best 50 Restaurants in the World & Best in Asia, Best Hotel Chef (India) in recognition of his excellence as the Executive Chef of Bukhara at the ITC Maurya and the list goes on. Chef Singhs Biography has been featured in IWWC-International who is who of the Chefs from USA. Speaking at Indian Restaurant Congress, Chef Singh talks about the Food trends and techniques that are bringing revolutionary changes in Indian food business scenario.', 'Chef, Food, Menu Trend, ITC Maurya, Executive Chef, Bukhara', '04:57', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 5921, 'A', '2015-12-16 09:12:41', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2077, 'XpyVqKV-Qlg', NULL, 'Chef Vicky Ratnani, Culinary Director, F&B Asia Ventures & Celebrity Chef', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'People are becoming conscious about what they eat, how they eat. How others eat and are following those trends. Health and wellness is the top priority these days. And what the guest want we like to give that in our menu believes, Chef Vicky Ratnani. ', 'Culinary Director, F&B Asia Ventures, Celebrity Chef, Food Menu', '06:12', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3518, 'A', '2015-12-16 09:15:10', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2078, 'fieBerXiVrE', NULL, 'Leveraging technology to aid merchants ', 5, '', NULL, '', 26, 'During a panel discussion held at the Indian Retail and eRetail Congress 2015, Shaleen Verma, Retail Solution Architect, Microsoft Dynamics, shared a brilliant presentation on the opportunity, potential and challenges in the omni-channel space. He also shared his experience of putting in place an omni-channel for customers. He also spoke about the needs of merchants and how a service provider like Microsoft helps them to achieve their goals leveraging technology and data analytics. ', 'Omni-channel retailing, Technology, Cloud Computing, Microsoft, Indian Retail Congress', '11:29', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3948, 'A', '2015-12-16 09:18:10', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 1, 0),
(2079, 'YT8phlxRRMw', NULL, 'Online creates reassurance for consumers', 4, '', NULL, '', 22, 'During a panel discussion held at the Indian Retail and eRetail Congress 2015, Siddharth Vinchurkar, Managing Director India, Mirum shared his thoughts on the opportunities and potential the online space has and how it works as a medium of reassurance for todays consumers. He also spoke about how online brands engage with their consumers to build trust and satisfy them real time.', 'Digital Retail, eCommerce, Siddharth Vinchurkar, Indian Retail Congress', '06:00', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 5996, 'A', '2015-12-16 09:19:34', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2080, 'm-0pLTLxSpk', NULL, 'Offline Retail is huge because of trust', 5, '', NULL, '', 26, 'During a panel discussion held at the Indian Retail and eRetail Congress 2015, Vijay Menon, VP- Enterprise Solutions, Zopper shared a luminous presentation on making an omni-channel strategy for a retail business. Here he also shared some numbers and analysis on the online vs offline product preferences for various retail business models. He also believes that offline retail is here to stay and how it can leverage from the digital space.', 'Vijay Menon, Omni-Channel Retail, IT, Technology, Indian Retail Congress', '13:22', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3185, 'A', '2015-12-16 09:21:38', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2081, '0sZAekaLkJI', NULL, 'World Franchise Congress on ET Now', 1, '', NULL, '', 12, 'The annual World Franchise conference laid a foundation for building a big vision in Indian Franchising. Jointly brought to you by Franchise India and PepsiCo was held on 24th November 2015 at Hotel Pullman, Aerocity, New Delhi. It was Indias foremost opportunity to network with corporate peers and gain insight into the opportunities and answers to the challenges associated with developing and maintaining an effective franchise program. \r\n\r\nAlong with the congress, World Franchise Congress presented the countrys most prestigious awards in the arena of Franchise Leadership. The awards aim to recognize and felicitate Achievers, Innovators, smartest futurists and franchise leaders from all over the world and who have contributed significantly towards the development of current and franchise future trends in business, government and technology and society.', 'World Franchise Congress, Awards, Franchise Conference, Franchise Awards, Pepsico, Franchise India, ET Now, Rajiv Pratap Rudy, National Franchise Convention, World Franchise Congress Promo, Industry Conference, Franchise Summit, Andy Williams, Shiva shivakumar, Samudra Bhattacharya, Franchisor, Franchisee, Channel development, B2B conference, World Franchise Congress Episode', '25:30', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 5, 5332, 'A', '2015-12-16 09:26:21', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2082, 'FxmcEk59ffU', NULL, 'If you do your business the way you do yesterday, you are for sure going to perish from the market', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'At Entrepreneur Dialogue 2015, Mr. R K Panigrahi, Director, MSME-Development Institute, shares his thoughts about the business opportunity of being both a producing and consuming nation. ', 'Entrepreneur show 2015, R K Panigrahi, MSME-Development Institute, Make in India, Make for India, Small business', '14:08', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 2, 2666, 'A', '2015-12-17 09:20:15', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2083, '4yW-aMGgMJk', NULL, 'Bringing the best of Restaurants together - Part 1', 7, '', NULL, '', 36, 'Get the insight of biggest Restaurant Awards at JW Marriott, New Delhi. A night of awards, accolades and recognition that was well represented by the industry leaders.', 'Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, Restaurant Awards, Food Night, Franchise India, Food Business', '19:08', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2512, 'A', '2015-12-19 13:04:54', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2084, 'mVxpUtuf5og', NULL, 'Bringing the best of Restaurants together - Part 2', 7, '', NULL, '', 36, 'Get the insight of biggest Restaurant Awards at JW Marriott, New Delhi. A night of awards, accolades and recognition that was well represented by the industry leaders. ', 'Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, Restaurant Awards, Food Night, Franchise India, Food Business', '18:16', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2650, 'A', '2015-12-19 13:08:21', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2086, 'nzQ6R0dA8eI', NULL, 'New Game New Rules', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Sunil Kapur, has been a pioneer in the Indian F&B Industry. Under his leadership K Hospitality Corp has expanded into a national, privately held, Hospitality and Food Services Corporation, with operations across specialty restaurants, cafes, bars, large F&B concession management, banqueting & outdoor catering, sports & industrial catering and travel retail. Talking at Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, he shares Economics of Indian Restaurant Industry in 2015 and beyond.', 'Indian Restaurant Congress 2015,  Sunil Kapur, K Hospitality Corp, Franchise India, Food Business', '18:07', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 5859, 'A', '2015-12-19 13:12:50', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2087, 'BBDQjI60HIQ', NULL, 'New Game New Rules', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Sunil Kapur, has been a pioneer in the Indian F&B Industry. Under his leadership K Hospitality Corp has expanded into a national, privately held, Hospitality and Food Services Corporation, with operations across specialty restaurants, cafes, bars, large F&B concession management, banqueting & outdoor catering, sports & industrial catering and travel retail. Talking at Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, he shares Economics of Indian Restaurant Industry in 2015 and beyond.', 'Indian Restaurant Congress 2015,  Sunil Kapur, K Hospitality Corp, Franchise India, Food Business', '10:40', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 6442, 'A', '2015-12-19 13:14:04', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2088, 'qNgKNFP_56s', NULL, 'New Game New Rules', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Mr. Burman, Vice-Chairman of Dabur India Ltd and has been involved with giving strategic direction to this FMCG biz. He was the driving force behind Dabur entering the Food business with the launch of India first packaged juice brand Real. He is India largest restaurateur having set up a food venture Lite Bite Foods, which today has a network of over 100 restaurants across the globe. Talking at Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, he shares Economics of Indian Restaurant Industry in 2015 and beyond.', 'Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, Amit Burman, Dabur India Ltd, Franchise India, Food Business', '22:44', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3871, 'A', '2015-12-19 13:16:57', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2089, 'K9C-LXM08H0', NULL, 'How technology is shaping the future', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Mohit Kumar is an independent and customer focused strategist. He started at HolidayIQ as a developer specialized at SEO but slowly he assumed leadership role in product meetings and took a lead in technical aspects of the company. Talking at Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, he shares how technology is shaping the future.', 'Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, Franchise India, Mohit Kumar, Roadrunner', '13:39', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1885, 'A', '2016-01-04 13:07:53', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2090, 'c0sJJVMLfJo', NULL, 'How technology is helping restaurant business grow by Vivek Kapoor', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'As part of the founding team, Vivek Kapoor heads the Pan India Sales and Operations team at Dineout.co.in. Vivek is a peoples person, which makes him proficient in handling all office operations, including hiring and managing team members at Dineout. For him, employees are the backbone of the company and have contributed to his success overall, pillaring his progress professionally. Speaking at Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, he shares How Technology is shaping the future of Indian food industry.', 'Vivek Kapoor, Dineout, Times Internet, Online Food Space, Food-Tech, Franchise India, Restaurant Congress 2015', '10:13', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3820, 'A', '2016-01-04 13:10:54', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2091, 'SeNszxyDpEM', NULL, 'Bringing the best of Restaurants together - Part 3', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Get the insight of biggest Restaurant Awards at JW Marriott, New Delhi. A night of awards, accolades and recognition that was well represented by the industry leaders. ', 'Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, Restaurant Awards, Food Night, Franchise India, Food Business', '21:21', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2100, 'A', '2016-01-05 09:33:14', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2092, 'agFTnfmBkFA', NULL, 'The Digital Restaurant', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Mohit sharma has great interest in mobile solutions, analytics and big data, business intelligence, decision support system. He is heading R&D of Romio, which has recently developed Android POS on cloud technology. His vision is to provide customised solutions to restaurant chains which can solve their day to day problem and increases their revenue. Talking at Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, he talks about how technology is changing the dining experience.  ', 'Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, Franchise India, Mohit Sharma, Romio Technologies ', '17:15', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3167, 'A', '2016-01-05 09:34:17', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2093, '0SnmktIkPfc', NULL, 'Trio Of Trust- Consumers, Shoppers and Brands', 7, '', NULL, '', 35, 'Hemant Rupani leads the multi category Sales function for Britannia Industries Limited spanning over Biscuits, Cakes, Rusk and Dairy. While Britannia has been well known for its brands, under Hemants leadership, the company has done some cutting edge work on distribution models, sales information systems and performance management. In his time spent with Britannia the company has delivered growths ahead of industry, gained market leadership, scaled up direct distribution by over 60 per cent, reduced spends by over a third and done all this with lesser manning.  Talking to Restaurant India, he shares the Growth Rate of Britannia.', 'FoodWorld India 2015, Britannia, Hemant Rupani', '02:38', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3711, 'A', '2016-01-06 09:12:28', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2094, 'LLlWb82Johw', NULL, 'Innovation - A Key growth driver for food industry ', 7, '', NULL, '', 35, 'Siraj A Chaudhry tenure at Cargill spans 20 years, under his leadership since 2007 Cargill India has successfully built both institutional and consumer businesses backed by world class manufacturing facilities, a robust distribution network and an enviable brand portfolio. He pioneered the concept of fortifying all its edible oils with vitamins A, D and E in India to deliver much needed micronutrients and fight malnutrition in India. Talking to Restaurant India, he talks about Measures to keep food healthy.', 'FoodWorld India 2015, Siraj A Chaudhry, Cargill India', '03:52', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 4728, 'A', '2016-01-06 09:13:56', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2095, '7n0QOCufjYo', NULL, 'Innovation - A Key growth driver for food industry ', 7, '', NULL, '', 35, 'V L Rajesh has been with ITC ever since25 years. He spent the first 10 years in sales and brand management in the ITC tobacco division. During this time; he handled some of the largest tobacco brands in the country including Gold Flake. Talking to Restaurant India, he shares Changes in consumer behaviour.', 'FoodWorld India 2015, ITC, Food, V L Rajesh ', '02:07', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3879, 'A', '2016-01-06 09:15:44', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2096, 'LLSBuOJdiZQ', NULL, 'Economics of Indian Restaurant Industry ', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Riyaaz Amlani, a thorough homebred restaurateur with 18 unique brand identities to his credit. He also took over as President, National Restaurant Association of India in 2014 for which he was unanimously selected by his peers. Talking at Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, he shares the insight of the restaurants and  new trends coming in 2016.', 'Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, Franchise India, Food Business, NRAI', '17:03', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3395, 'A', '2016-01-06 16:32:00', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2097, 'TEyh8QlyPJE', NULL, 'Maximising Revenue and Profitability', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Mr. Kapil Malhotra, Founder & Chairman of the Total Solutions Group.  He has travelled to many countries with Prime Minister Modi delegation and has spoken at many prestigious business strategy and investment conferences in Phuket, Athens, Sydney, Mauritius and Tokyo. Talking at Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, he talks about how the restaurateurs through proper audits and customized trainings can maximise revenue. ', 'Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, Franchise India, Total Solution Group', '19:17', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3419, 'A', '2016-01-06 16:33:04', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2098, '3NXVnqMwHWE', NULL, 'Welcome Note', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Ritu Marya, Editor-in-Chief, Franchise India Holdings Pvt Ltd addresses the restaurateurs. She speaks about the upcoming growth with changing technology, evolving market and new ideas in the industry. ', 'Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, Franchise India', '10:59', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2751, 'A', '2016-01-07 16:03:54', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2099, 'XNS6cnFGsZU', NULL, 'Building Customer Loyalty', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Arpit Agarwal is the Co-Founder, OneLoyalCard & Director at Globe Capital Market Limited. Talking at Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, he shares how to build customer loyalty.', 'Indian Restaurant Congress 2015, Franchise India, OneLoyalCard', '04:03', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2823, 'A', '2016-01-07 16:04:54', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2100, 'HopI37RyHJI', NULL, 'Entrepreneur Awards 2015 recognizes achievers, innovators and young entreprenurs - Part 1', 2, '', NULL, '', 16, 'Entrepreneur Media India in association with leading Industry bodies, including FICCI, NEN and NASSCOM 10,000 Startups organised the 5th Annual Entrepreneur India Awards 2015 on 22nd July at JW Marriott Hotel, Aerocity, New Delhi. Being the most prestigious awards in the Entrepreneur arena, they recognize and felicitate achievers, innovators and suppliers, who have contributed significantly towards the development of Entrepreneurship in India. The chief Guest for the gala night was Shri Rajiv Pratap Rudy, Minister of State Skill Development & Entrepreneurship and the International Guest of Honour was Mr. Ryan Shea, President & COO of Entrepreneur Media Inc., USA.', 'Entrepreneur India Award 2015, Rajiv Pratap Rudy, Entrepreneurship, Startups, Innovators', '15:12', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3871, 'A', '2016-01-12 12:51:58', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2101, 'x8Fw47c3gFY', NULL, 'Entrepreneur Awards 2015 recognizes achievers, innovators and young entreprenurs - Part 2', 2, '', NULL, '', 16, 'Entrepreneur Media India in association with leading Industry bodies, including FICCI, NEN and NASSCOM 10,000 Startups organised the 5th Annual Entrepreneur India Awards 2015 on 22nd July at JW Marriott Hotel, Aerocity, New Delhi. Being the most prestigious awards in the Entrepreneur arena, they recognize and felicitate achievers, innovators and suppliers, who have contributed significantly towards the development of Entrepreneurship in India. The chief Guest for the gala night was Shri Rajiv Pratap Rudy, Minister of State Skill Development & Entrepreneurship and the International Guest of Honour was Mr. Ryan Shea, President & COO of Entrepreneur Media Inc., USA.', 'Entrepreneur India Award 2015, Rajiv Pratap Rudy, Entrepreneurship, Startups, Innovators', '14:48', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3928, 'A', '2016-01-12 12:52:58', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2102, 'rCu9erFQZxw', NULL, 'Entrepreneur Awards 2015 recognizes achievers, innovators and young entreprenurs - Part 3', 2, '', NULL, '', 16, 'Entrepreneur Media India in association with leading Industry bodies, including FICCI, NEN and NASSCOM 10,000 Startups organised the 5th Annual Entrepreneur India Awards 2015 on 22nd July at JW Marriott Hotel, Aerocity, New Delhi. Being the most prestigious awards in the Entrepreneur arena, they recognize and felicitate achievers, innovators and suppliers, who have contributed significantly towards the development of Entrepreneurship in India. The chief Guest for the gala night was Shri Rajiv Pratap Rudy, Minister of State Skill Development & Entrepreneurship and the International Guest of Honour was Mr. Ryan Shea, President & COO of Entrepreneur Media Inc., USA.', 'Entrepreneur India Award 2015, Rajiv Pratap Rudy, Entrepreneurship, Startups, Innovators', '10:06', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3515, 'A', '2016-01-12 12:54:02', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2103, 'sL986w-1gAk', NULL, 'Entrepreneur Awards 2015 recognizes achievers, innovators and young entreprenurs - Part 4', 2, '', NULL, '', 16, 'Entrepreneur Media India in association with leading Industry bodies, including FICCI, NEN and NASSCOM 10,000 Startups organised the 5th Annual Entrepreneur India Awards 2015 on 22nd July at JW Marriott Hotel, Aerocity, New Delhi. Being the most prestigious awards in the Entrepreneur arena, they recognize and felicitate achievers, innovators and suppliers, who have contributed significantly towards the development of Entrepreneurship in India. The chief Guest for the gala night was Shri Rajiv Pratap Rudy, Minister of State Skill Development & Entrepreneurship and the International Guest of Honour was Mr. Ryan Shea, President & COO of Entrepreneur Media Inc., USA.', 'Entrepreneur India Award 2015, Rajiv Pratap Rudy, Entrepreneurship, Startups, Innovators', '19:43', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3616, 'A', '2016-01-12 12:54:52', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2104, 'HUhBaR1_x_0', NULL, 'Angel investment: Creating diverse social impact on small biz ', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'Discussing on making business your business, the panelists talk about the risk capital, business experience and skills which are needed to grow your startup or small business. They further talk about the angels and what they look into the startup portfolios before investing in them.', 'Entrepreneur, Investor, Entrepreneur India show 2015, Angel Investment, Startups, Mentoring, Small Business', '19:14', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2235, 'A', '2016-01-15 09:17:15', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2105, 'YtFOdVuKtQU', NULL, 'Angels supporting and mentoring startup for their growth', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'Discussing on making business your business, the panelists talk about the risk capital, business experience and skills which are needed to grow your startup or small business. They further talk about the angels and what they look into the startup portfolios before investing in them.', 'Entrepreneur, Investor, Entrepreneur India show 2015, Angel Investment, Startups, Mentoring, Small Business', '11:31', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1974, 'A', '2016-01-15 09:18:23', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2106, 'mQg3V8-e63I', NULL, 'Estate Summit & Awards 2015 &ndash; ET Now Promo', 3, '', NULL, '', 20, 'The 8th edition of the Estate Summit & Awards 2015 is an initiative by Franchise India and Propertyindia.tv to deliberate on how to leverage the change that surrounds the Real Estate Industry to make the sector the best investment segment. The conference was a conglomeration of 250+ leading developers, C- level real estate professionals, policy makers and government office holders . \r\nThe Estate Summit was concluded by Estate Awards 2015 that rewarded excellence, innovation and creativity in the real estate industry. The Estate Awards recognize the finest real estate projects, developers, brokers, architects and suppliers during a prestigious gala dinner attended by the most influential Real estate leaders and C-level property professionals.', 'Estate Summit 2015, Estate Awards 2015, Estate Conference, Business Conference, Estate Convention, ET Now, Promo', '0:44', 'V', NULL, 'en', 2, 2, 6, 4142, 'A', '2016-01-15 16:03:44', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2107, 'M3eZo7GHnNY', NULL, 'Knowing what kind of capital is right for your business ', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'Discussing on the topic such as when is the  right time for the founders to raise fund, the panelist talks about the targeting right investors, know your business and the your consumer well, research properly etc. during their discussion they throw lights on what can someone else money and mind do to your business, understanding the science of the business etc. ', 'Entrepreneur, Investor, Entrepreneur India show 2015, Startup Investment, Funding, Startup, Growth Strategies ', '22:27', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2466, 'A', '2016-01-16 12:11:10', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0);
