(2446, 'Sl6NwZdE_PA', NULL, 'Franchising has become a Global business, says Mr.Troy ', 1, '', NULL, '', 10, 'Enlighting the panel at Delhi show 2016 along with the moderator Ms. RituMarya(Editor in chief, Franchising India) we had the speakers DR. OP Manchanda (CEO of Dr. Lal Path Labs Pvt. Ltd.), Mr. Troy Franklin (COO of World Franchising Association in South-east Asia), Mr. N. Mathivanan (Principle partner and country head of LakshmiKumaran&Sridharan) talking about what is trending in Franchising and how the businesses are transforming further addressing the questions from the audiences.', 'Franchising India, Franchising, Delhi show 2016, Ms. RituMarya, Dr. OP Sharma, Mr. Troy Franklin, Mr. N. Mathivanan, Panel Discussion, Franchising in India, Business models, Stages of business, Dr. Lal Path Labs, LakshmiKumaran&Sridharan, World Franchising Association, IPO, Technology', '1:09:09', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2712, 'A', '2017-04-19 10:35:59', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2447, 'BosnqsDkkok', NULL, 'Venturing Into Healthcare, Beauty & Wellness ', 9, '', NULL, '', 42, 'Dr. Pradeep Jeothi, Chairman & Managing Director, Vasudeva Vilasam Group of Companies, Mr. DarpanSanghvi, Managing Director, Sanghvi Brands & CEO, My Glamm and Mr. Sarvesh Shashi, Founder & CEO, ZORBA: A Renaissance Studio discusses Health care, Beauty and Wellness respectively talking about venturing into the industries.', 'Franchise India, Franchising, Delhi Show 2016, Venturing, Panel Discussion, Dr. Pradeep Jeothi, Vasudeva Vilasam Group of Companies. Mr. DarpanSanghvi, My Glamm, ZORBA, Mr. Sarvesh Shashi, Health care, Beauty, Wellness', '49:02', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3983, 'A', '2017-04-19 10:37:47', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2448, 'oQxHICyyhao', NULL, 'The story of Food Industry', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Mr. Sanjay Coutinho, CEO, Baskin Robbins, Mr. Anurag Katriar, Executive Director & CEO, deGustibus Hospitality Pvt. Ltd., Mr. Karan Tanna, Founder & CEO, Yellow Tie Hospitality, Mr. Sharad Sachdeva, CEO, Lite Bite Foods talks in the panel over different aspects related to the revolution in the food industry like how innovation is important to create the buzz among the customers further emphasizing on how affordable alcohol with affordable food will bring all together a different spark in the industry and help it boom and all other aspects of franchising and revolutionizing like food trucks in order to succeed.', 'Franchise India, Franchising, Delhi Show 2016, Panel discussion, deGustibus Hospitality Pvt. Ltd., Mr. Sanjay Coutinho, Baskin Robbins, Food, The Food Revolution, Mr. Anurag Katriar, Mr. Karan Tanna , Yellow Tie Hospitality , Mr. Sharad Sachdeva, Lite Bite Foods, Retailer', '55:11', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3369, 'A', '2017-04-19 10:39:31', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2449, 'YBzBA7yuF50', NULL, 'The changing Education Business ', 8, '', NULL, '', 38, 'The Panel discussion in the Delhi show of 2016 heads with different speakers from the Education sector  like Session Moderator: Mr. Suchindra Kumar, Director-Advisory Services, EY LLP, Mr. ShreevatsJaipuria, Vice Chairman, Jaipuria Group, Mr. Amit Agrawal, Chairman, Times & Trends Academy, Mr. S. K. Rathor, Managing Director, Sanfort Group of Schools, Dr. Narendra Shyamsukha, Chairperson, ICA Edu Skills Pvt. Ltd., Mr. Atul Vohra, CEO, Reliance Education and Mr. J.P. Gaur, Director - Principal, MVN Schools addressing the issues related to the emergence of new institution in the Education sector  as a prosperous business in the market and how  is it a not just a business or franchise but a legacy which is built on the social values.\\r\\n\\r\\n', 'Education, Delhi show 2016, Panel Discussion, Franchising, Franchise India, Edupreneurs, ShreevatsJaipuria, Jaipuria Group, Mr. Amit Agrawal, Mr. S. K. Rathor, Sanfort Group of Schools, Dr. Narendra Shyamsukha ICA Edu Skills Pvt. Ltd., Mr. Atul Vohra, Reliance Education, MVN Schools', '44:01', 'V', NULL, 'en', 2, 2, 10, 5985, 'A', '2017-04-19 10:42:46', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2450, 'x2ZhpqYUOms', NULL, 'The trio of consumers, retail brands and e-commerce ', 5, '', NULL, '', 26, 'The ongoing shift from brick and mortar to online mode of shopping was the topic of discussion at one of the sessions in Delhi show 2016 where speakers like Mr. VivekSethi, Director - Retail, LeEco, Mr. Shiv Nirula, Managing Director, Futomic Group of Companies, Mr. BhawantAnand, Chairman, Blau, Mr. Anupam Bansal, Executive Director, Liberty Shoes and Mr. Manav Sarin, Sr. Vice President at Gitanjali Gems Ltd addressed the audience by talking over how have things changed in the retail industry so far and how can retailers grow as a brand by not being carried away watching their competitive brands switching over to some other methods.\\r\\n\\r\\n', 'â€¢	Franchise India, Delhi Show 2016, Retail, Retailer, Panel Discussion, Consumer, LeEco, Mr. Satish Meena, Mr. VivekSethi, Mr. Shiv Nirula, Futomic Group of Companies, Mr. BhawantAnand, Mr. Anupam Bansal, Liberty Shoes,Gitanjali Gems Ltd, Mr. Manav Sarin, Online shopping, Brick and mortar, Offline shopping, Franchising, ', '1:00:33', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3685, 'A', '2017-04-19 10:48:51', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2451, 'FARblQNa5_w', NULL, 'Changing trends in Business opens doors for Franchise Industry: Gaurav Marya', 1, '', NULL, '', 10, 'Mr. Gaurav Marya, Chairman, Franchise India Holdings Ltd. addresses the audience at Delhi show 2016 talking about the tremendous change the franchising industry has gone through since last two years, further listing and discussing the challenges and opportunities of Franchising in India stressing on how the business trends in the country are changing and how is it a benefit for franchising industry in a shopkeeper country like India.', 'Gaurav Marya, Franchising, Challenges in Franchising, Opportunities in Franchising,Franchise India, Delhi show 2016, Changing Business Trends, Franchising in India', '27:47', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2960, 'A', '2017-04-19 10:55:29', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2452, 'NSBPuiEmuHw', NULL, 'Business is all about funds and funding ', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'Ms. Padmaja Ruparel, President & CEO, Indian Angel Network, Mr. Vineet C Nambiar, Co-Founder & Director, Viva Info ventures Pvt. Ltd.,Mr. Aakaar Gandhi, Investment Manager, Redcliffe Capital, Mr. Vinayak Burman, Founder Partner, Vertices Partners along with the Session Moderator Mr. Mragank Jain, Director, Standard Chartered Private Equity talk about the aspects of venturing, funding and networking in business today at the Delhi show 2016.\\r\\n\\r\\n', 'Mr. Mragank Jain, Ms. PadmajaRuparel, Indian Angel Network, Mr. Vineet C Nambiar, Mr. Kumaran Pillai, Mr. Aakaar Gandhi, Mr. Vinayak Burman, Delhi show 2016, Franchise India, Franchising, Investors, Investing, Networking, Connecting, Entrepreneur, Co-founder, Venture, Venturing, Retailer, Business, Brand, Funding, Panel Discussion, Fund raising.', '25:50', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2133, 'A', '2017-04-20 15:35:36', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2453, '6tsnIviqu3M', NULL, 'Funding and capital is what we need in business', 5, '', NULL, '', 26, 'Mr. Ramesh Dharmaji, SIDBI, Mr. Alok Mittal, Indifi Technologies, Mr. Rakesh Kashyap, Canara Bank, Mr. NeerajVikram Singh, ,Tata Capital Financial Services Limited talk about capital lending facilities valid in different banks and companies providing the capital for business.', 'Delhi show 2016, Franchise India, Franchising, Panel discussion, Venturing, bank, loan, debt, capital, funding, Entrepreneur,  Mr. Ramesh Dharmaji, SIDBI, Mr. Alok Mittal, Indifi Technologies, Mr. Rakesh Kashyap, Canara Bank, Mr. NeerajVikram Singh, ,Tata Capital Financial Services Limited, Start up, India, Business, economy, women, lender, borrower', '52:34', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2478, 'A', '2017-04-20 16:02:29', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2454, 'NZTBaASq9QE', NULL, 'How to find the right franchising partner?', 1, '', NULL, '', 10, 'Monil Rambhia, Zee Learn and RupeshBhagchandani, Bata India together interact with audience at Delhi show 2016 in the knowledge series talking about the importance finding a right franchising partner in order to grow the business at a right pace with common passion and philosophy towards work.', 'Franchise India, Franchising, Delhi Show 2016, Franchising offers, The Master Franchise class, Franchise knowledge series, International workshop on Franchising and Business growth, MonilRambhia, RupeshBhagchandani, Bata, Bata India, Zee, Zee Learn', '24:53', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2285, 'A', '2017-04-20 18:27:56', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, 0, 0),
(2455, 'tc6OQ28OOMw', NULL, 'Taking a Master Franchising class', 1, '', NULL, '', 10, 'Mr. Terry watts addresses the audiences taking a Master Franchise Class contributing in the expanding the knowledge of the franchisers and franchisees talking about Enterprises, Franchising offers, benefits and lists of franchising and asking the audience to questions themselves if Franchising is the right thing for their business or not?\\r\\n\\r\\n', 'Franchise India, Franchising, Delhi Show 2016, Franchising offers, The Master Franchise class, Franchise knowledge series, International workshop on Franchising and Business growth, Terry Watts, benefits of franchising, risks of franchising', '49:40', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1816, 'A', '2017-04-20 18:30:35', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2456, '62Csri2T7NA', NULL, 'Technology is one of the indicators of civilization, says Sukhanta Dey', 1, '', NULL, '', 10, 'Taking a Franchise class in Delhi Show 2016 the founder and CEO of Sdela Consulting, Mr. Sukhanta Dey stresses upon how important is franchising in order to grow the business rapidly showing a short video to the audience and pointing out how Technology has become one of the indicators of civilization.', 'Franchise India, Franchising, Delhi Show 2016, Franchising offers, The Master Franchise class, Franchise knowledge series, International workshop on Franchising and Business growth, Sukhanta Dey, Sdela consultant, Business', '42:30', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2394, 'A', '2017-04-20 18:33:20', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2457, 'zrjm4vY871o', NULL, 'Subramanian Swamy Calls India Risk-Averse; Says Cant Achieve Progress Unless We Take Risks', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'Subramanian Swamy feels interest rates in India are way too high for businesses to run. In a chat with Entrepreneur India, Swamy bats for a liberal policy for SMEs, which he calls the backbone of the economy. He calls for entrepreneurs to be independent of the government in their work towards innovations that could put the nation on a growth trajectory. Read complete interview: https://www.entrepreneur.com/article/293468', 'Subramanian Swamy, India, Narendra Modi, entrepreneurship, Indian entrepreneurs, SMEs, risk taking, Vijay Mallya, loans, NPAs, restructuring, Indian banks, RBI, interest rates', '4:17', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1584, 'A', '2017-04-27 14:49:44', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2458, 'gvBqTSZq4KU', NULL, 'This Entrepreneur Feels Big Data Plays a Critical Role In the Fintech Sector', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'Founded by Manish Khera, Arth Impact currently provides digital micro loans to mainly micro customers. In a chat with Entrepreneur India, he gave details about the impact  of big data in the Indian digital lending space.Manish Khera is serial entrepreneur and investor in the impact space particularly Financial Inclusion. Bringing over two decades of experience, he is considered as one of the core enablers of financial Inclusion in India as an applicant of the Small Finance Bank license, his entrepreneurial ventures as well as investments in businesses in impact space.\\r\\n\\r\\n', 'Digital Lending , Alternative Lending, Big data, Digital India, Banking, Startups, Technology, Profit', '4:07', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2587, 'A', '2017-04-27 14:51:54', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2459, 'DCpiNzia5mw', NULL, 'This 100-year old Indian Ayurveda Company Outlines Two Key Industry Challenges \\r\\n', 9, '', NULL, '', 42, 'In a chat with Entrepreneur India, he spoke about the key challenges often faced by industry players and how Ayurveda is helping global countries believe in Indian systems. Anurag Sharma is the Managing Director of Baidyanath Ayurveda Bhawan Pvt. Ltd.and a well-known business leader in the Ayruveda industry.\\r\\n\\r\\n', 'Education, Financial services, Private Equity, Technology,\\r\\nHealthcare, Startups, Startup Ecosystem, Gaja Capital, Investment\\r\\n', '1:27', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3717, 'A', '2017-04-27 15:50:50', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2460, '1dsUnBwtH9A', NULL, 'Indian Salon & Wellness Congress & Awards 2017 Promo on TIMES NOW', 9, '', NULL, '', 42, 'The sixth edition of Salon and Wellness Congress & Awards 2017 concluded on 11 April 2017 at JW Marriott, New Delhi, Aerocity. The event was organised by Franchise India, in association with My Glamm, powered by VLCC and with media partnership Times Now. The grand event saw several successful entrepreneurs and big names from the wellness industry attending and sharing their thoughts and insights on important topics related to salon and wellness. It opened many doors to opportunities for entrepreneurs as everyone got to learn something new and take with them essentials, which will push the industry to achieve a new milestone.\\r\\n\\r\\n', 'Wellness Summit, Wellness Conference, Business Conference, B2B wellness conference, Salon Congress, Fitness Summit, AYUSH conference, Business Awards, Times Now Promo, B2B Awards, Salon Fraternity, Wellness Community\\r\\n\\r\\n', '0:55', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3902, 'A', '2017-04-27 16:13:52', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2461, '5PS_kT_-fw8', NULL, 'MoneyTech17 Summit & Awards Promo on ET NOW ', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'The first edition of MoneyTech17 concluded on the 10 April 2017 at JW Marriott, New Delhi, Aerocity. The event was organised by Business Ex Solutions Ltd., in partnership with Franchise India, and with media partnership with ET Now. The grand event saw several successful entrepreneurs and big names from the FInance industry attending and sharing their thoughts and insights on important topics related to Financial Technology.\\r\\n\\r\\n', 'MoneyTech Summit, MoneyTech Conference, Business Conference, B2B conference, Financial Technology Summit, Digital Finance Conference, Regtech Conference, Online Payments Summit, Business Awards, ET Now Promo, B2B Awards, Finance Fraternity, Financial Community\\r\\n\\r\\n', '1:05', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3099, 'A', '2017-04-28 19:09:01', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2462, 'Mb-yBK74LiA', NULL, 'This School Drop Out Entrepreneur Feels Dropping Out Isn\\\'t a Wise Decision', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'Founded by Trishneet Arora, TAC Security Solution provides protection to corporations against network vulnerabilities and data theft and cyber security training. In a chat with Entrepreneur India, Trishneet shared the importance of education for entrepreneurs. Trishneet Arora is an Indian author, cyber security expert, and entrepreneur. With no family background in computers, Arora, a first-generation entrepreneur, set up his own company - TAC Security Solutions which deals with prominent corporate clients like Reliance Industries, Central Bureau of Investigation, Punjab Police (India) and Gujarat Police.\\r\\n\\r\\n', 'Cybersecurity, Education, Hacking, entrepreneurship, Indian entrepreneurs, Author, Cybercrime, Internet, Young Entrepreneur, Data Theft, Internet Safety', '3:20', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 4608, 'A', '2017-05-06 19:11:14', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2463, 'sxyhlfq69ZM', NULL, 'Indian Salon & Wellness Congress & Awards 2017 Episode on TIMES NOW', 9, '', NULL, '', 42, 'The sixth edition of Salon and Wellness Congress & Awards 2017 concluded on 11 April 2017 at JW Marriott, New Delhi, Aerocity. The event was organised by Franchise India, in association with My Glamm, powered by VLCC and with media partnership Times Now. The grand event saw several successful entrepreneurs and big names from the wellness industry attending and sharing their thoughts and insights on important topics related to salon and wellness. It opened many doors to opportunities for entrepreneurs as everyone got to learn something new and take with them essentials, which will push the industry to achieve a new milestone.', 'Wellness Summit, Wellness Conference, Business Conference, B2B wellness conference, Salon Congress, Fitness Summit, AYUSH conference, Business Awards, Times Now Episode, B2B Awards, Salon Fraternity, Wellness Community\\r\\n\\r\\n', '22:28', 'V', NULL, 'en', 1, 1, 5, 4167, 'A', '2017-05-09 20:23:30', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2464, 'FeK4lwSxCn4', NULL, 'We have 350+ products and aim to touch 650 to 700 products by 2018', 5, '', NULL, '', 27, 'At the Retail and eRetail Congress 2017, Arvind Varchaswi N, Managing Director, SriSri Tattva shared that over the years SriSri Tattva has grown from a brand signifying only Ayurveda to a brand offering FMCG, personal care and home care products. So, the brand has revamped itself from SriSri Ayurveda to SriSri Tatva. According to him SriSri Tatva signifies the elements and essence of purity, quality and authenticity. The brand is more of a niche mass market segment, catering to both, mass market and niche market. According to the observation, the brand expanded in the FMCG sector, namely in food, commodities, masalas, personal care that includes soaps, shower gels and understands the need of natural homecare products. The brand explores the omni-channel route, having distribution in traditional trade, modern trade and eCommerce. Arvind shared that because of digital payments, eCommerce and traditional trade are going to work together for the business to grow. Following this, Arvind spoke about business expansion in Indian and worldwide, store count and business model. ', 'SriSri Ayurveda, SriSri Tatva, Arvind Varchaswi, Indian Retail & eRetail Congress 2017, Franchise India, Ayurveda, Entrepreneur', '05.10', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 5628, 'A', '2017-05-20 11:17:38', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2465, 'COYLwVyAO34', NULL, 'The Agri-tech Industry Needs To Be Patient Because Theres No Scope Of Virality', 2, '', NULL, '', 15, 'Co-founded by Aditya Agarwalla,Y Combinator-backed Kisan Network is an online marketplace for Indian agriculture. It allows the Indian farmer to sell his produce directly to institutional buyers. In a chat with Entrepreneur India, Aditya explained why the future of agri-tech sector looks promising. He also laid emphasis on the fact that the agri-tech industry needs to be patient because theres no scope of virality over here.', 'Agriculture , Agri-tech, Farmers, Digital India, Rural India, Startups, Technology, Village', '4:05', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2432, 'A', '2017-05-24 09:32:38', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2466, 'RcTG6BZVEOo', NULL, 'BBI has 30 stores and will become the largest supplement company by the end of the year', 9, '', NULL, '', 43, 'At the launch of Gym 99 and Ross Nutrition, Dr. Ankush Sabharwal shared with us the concept which gave birth to Gym 99 and the efforts he has taken to make Bodybuilding India a well known brand among the fitness freaks. He said that the brand takes a lot of effort to choose the equipments and the trainers selected are also certified ones as they do not want to tamper the name of the brand. They have been providing with he best supplements and have always given quality the top priority. Further in the conversation, he explained about his franchise models and also explained about the varieties Gym 99 provides.', 'BBI, Bodybuilding India, Dr. Ankush Sabharwal, Wellness, Fitness, Franchise, Franchise India', '21:44', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 6312, 'A', '2017-05-25 12:09:22', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2467, 'SfOsAj9W-6I', NULL, 'The Need For Trust Is Paramount In The Jewellery Segment Whether You Are Selling Online Or Offline', 2, '', NULL, '', 15, 'Founded by Gaurav Singh Kushwaha, BlueStone is online jewellery destination that showcases high quality fine jewellery with strikingly exquisite designs.Gaurav is a Computer Science graduate from IIT Delhi and brings almost 10 years of experience in the fields of Technology, E-Commerce and Internet Marketing. In a chat with Entrepreneur India, Gaurav explained why there are plenty of challenges in the online jewellery space. He also stressed on the importance of trust in a particular brand whether the channel of sale is online or offline.\\r\\n\\r\\n', 'Jewellery , E-commerce, E-tailer, Digital India, Entrepreneur, Startups, Technology, Offline Store, Brand, Trust', '3:23', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3264, 'A', '2017-05-26 13:18:51', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2468, '3tARL_g7S0o', NULL, 'IReC 2017 ET Now Episode', 5, '', NULL, '', 26, 'The Sixth Annual Edition of the Indian Retail & eRetail Congress 2017 held on 15th & 16th May at JW Marriott Hotel, New Delhi Aerocity, was a grand event. The two-day event was jointly organized by Retailer Media, Franchise India Media and Global Entrepreneur Media. In association with broadcast partner ET Now, the Indian Retail & eRetail Congress 2017 focused on how to build a seamless customer experience across online and physical store format, boosting sales and bottom line.rnIt brought together leaders of the retail organization groups and e-commerce businesses that are transforming the customer environments in 2017 both from India and overseas markets. It also witnessed 300-plus international and national industry business leaders, global leaders, brand owners, investors, e-commerce startups, digital payments business experts, consumer tech entrepreneurs, and the policymakers from the Centre. The event broadly highlighted four themes -- digital payments, 21st century consumer experience, the bigger and better e-commerce, and combining bricks & clicks.rnrnThe Congress also witnessed Annual Indian Retail & eRetail Awards 2017 which are considered to be one of the most prestigious awards that recognize excellence in Performance in Retail space. The award ceremony was aimed at felicitating people who have contributed towards the growth of Retail & eRetail Industry in India. rn', 'IReC 2017, Indian Retail Congress 2017, Indian eRetail Congress 2017, Indian Retail Awards 2017, Indian eRetail Awards 2017, ET Now Episode, Retail Convention, Retail Industry conference, Indian Retail exhibition, Business Conference, Retail Summit, B2B Awards, Retail Awards', '23:46', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 5355, 'A', '2017-06-08 15:13:32', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2469, 'p16q1v7lZa8', NULL, 'The Digital Transformation in Education & Training', 8, '', NULL, '', 38, 'The online wind is taking every aspect of business in its leap. The business of Education is not an exception to it. The Indian Education Congress was held on 7th & 8th February, 2017 at JW Marriot Hotel, New Delhi. In the panel we have, Aditya Malik, CEO, Talentedge; Sreenivasan Ramakrishnan, Co-founder, Career Launcher; Gopal Devanhalli, Senior Vice President, Manipal Global Education (Manipal); Prof. Dwarika Uniyal, Assistant Dean & Executive-Education, IIM Kashipur; Narendra K Mohapatra, CEO, Electronic Sector Skill Council of India. The panel discussed the online trends in the Indian Education. How the industry and students are taking Digitized Education and how teachers and institutions need to adapt to it?', 'Digital education, online education, trends in digital education, Aditya Malik, Talentedge, Sreenivasan Ramakrishnan, Gopal Devanhalli, Dwarika Uniyal, Narendra K Mohapatra, franchise india, educationbiz', '38:49', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 5100, 'A', '2017-06-28 14:45:34', NULL, NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0),
(2470, 'sgOsCOXX15s', NULL, 'Entrepreneur India July 2017 Cover Promo \\\" Behind the Scenes  ', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'An entrepreneur is an entrepreneur, be it any country. Focusing outside of India, looking at our neighboring country, Nepal, Entrepreneur found a great visionary who fought all odds. Binod Chaudhary, President of the Chaudhary Group, not only spread the biggest conglomerate in Nepal, but he went on to take it global and is now keen to take Indian market, heads on. Entrepreneur met Binod and his son Varun spearheading the India market to know the story of becoming Nepals first and only billionaire. rnrn', 'Binod Chaudhary, Varun Chaudhary, Wai Wai Noodles, CG Corp, Billionaire, Nepal, Entrepreneur, Chaudhary Group \\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\n', '1:00', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 117, 'D', '2017-07-04 18:01:30', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2471, 'Gmz0eZmWe9c', NULL, 'Innovation in the Retail Store Format', 5, '', NULL, '', 26, 'Innovation in the retail store is yesterdays reality! Retail stores are one of the ways you interact with and entertain your customers. This producer-consumer interface has to be such that it leaves a permanent impression on the consumers mind. Be it the customer communication, or the staff behaviour or the stores lighting system, everything of your store negotiates with the senses of the customer about actually doing the purchase deal!The Indian Retail & e-Retail Congress was held on 15-16th May, 2017 at Hotel JW Marriot, New Delhi. Above is a panel discussion on Innovation in the Retail Store Format. Among the panellists we have, Mr. Sardul Seth, Partner, Advisory Services- Africa, Middle East & India, Consumer Products & Retail, Sector & Risk Analytics Solution Lead; Mr. Vishal Malik, Business Head-Retail, Intex Technologies India Ltd; Mr. Ayush Mehra, Director, Pret Study, Janak Garments Pvt. Ltd; Mr. Rajesh Purohit, Vice President-Operations SPAR Hypermarkets Pvt. Ltd.', 'Franchiseindia, retail, e-retail, Indian Retail & e-Retail Congress, Sardul Seth, Vishal Malik, Intex Technologies India Ltd, Ayush Mehra, Janak Garments Pvt. Ltd, Rajesh Purohit, SPAR Hypermarkets Pvt. Ltd. ', '52:24', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2760, 'A', '2017-07-05 12:50:24', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2472, 'NAnK-jg-CV8', NULL, 'Building Growth from Local to National to International', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Restaurateurs today are trying to expand their reach local restaurants are going international and international brands are focussing on local areas. Because wherever you are doing it you are into consumption business and consumption does not stop. Hence restaurants today have great opportunities. Restaurant India 2017 (West Edition) was held on 4th March, 2017 at Hotel Westin, Pune. In the panel we have Reynold Fernandes, CEO, Oriental Cuisines Pvt. Ltd.; Karan Tanna, CEO, Yellow Tie Hospitality; Kaizad Modi, Sr. Partner & Owner, REISE Hospitality LLP. The Panel shared their ideas on Building Growth from Local to National to International\\r\\n\\r\\n', 'Restaurant India, Franchise India, Ritu Marya, West India Restaurant, Reynold Fernandes, Oriental Cuisines Pvt. Ltd, Karan Tanna, Yellow Tie Hospitality, Kaizad Modi, REISE Hospitality LLP', '29:05', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2392, 'A', '2017-07-22 15:34:46', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2473, 'ZYTXggdd1r8', NULL, 'What is trending in West: Chefs Opinion', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Eminent Chefs gather to discuss What is Trending? Is it really a phenomena called food trend? Or it is the restaurateur who sets the trend? Restaurant India 2017 (West Edition) was held on 4th March, 2017 at Hotel Westin, Pune. On the Panel we have Chef Sabyasachi Gorai, Celebrity Chef & Owner, Mineority by Saby; Chef Milind Sovani, Celebrity Chef & Entrepreneur; Chef Rakhee Vaswani, Celebrity Chef Entrepreneur, Palate Culinary Studio; Aditi Dugar, Director; Safe & Saffron.', 'Restaurant India, Franchise India, What is Trending, Trends in Food, Trends in Restaurant, Sabyasachi Gorai, Mineority by Saby, Milind Sovani,  Rakhee Vaswani, Palate Culinary Studio, Aditi Dugar, Safe & Saffron, The Mask', '34:35', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1527, 'A', '2017-07-22 15:36:19', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2474, 'Oi_04Buu6Qw', NULL, 'Your Food is Here (Delivering Delight to Customers)', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Food Delivery has become an essential need of todays consumer. He would prefer to have that chunk of delight rather than at your restaurant. Restaurant India 2017 (West Edition) was held on 4th March, 2017 at Hotel Westin, Pune. Mr. Mohit Kumar, Co-founder & CEO, Runnr shares at Restaurant India 2017, his deep analysis of the Food-Delivery sector helps us understand how a restaurant can really benefit by including Home- Delivery into his operations. Also he shares his knowledge on Effective Delivery System', 'Restaurant India, Franchise India, Mohit Kumar, Runnr, Food Delivery, home delivery, Your Food is Here, Delivering Delight to Customers', '20:30', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1810, 'A', '2017-07-22 15:37:53', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2475, 'jgaQjFLdf2c', NULL, 'QSR & Cafe Growth', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'QSR Sector has experienced a steady growth of 20 per cent. Knowledge splashes around when some great minds brainstorm on how your restaurant business can capture the profits in this QSR wind! Restaurant India 2017 (West Edition) was held on 4th March, 2017 at Hotel Westin, Pune. On the panel we have Riyaz Amlani, CEO, Empressario, Chairman, Restaurant Association of India; Sandeep Singh, CEO, Papa Johns; Chef Sumant Vikas, Corporate Chef Cremica Food Industries; Aayush Sadana, Director, Rishabh Hotel & Restaurant Services Pvt. Ltd.', 'Restaurant India, Franchise India, QSR, Riyaz Amlani, Empressario, Restaurant Association of India, Sandeep Singh, Papa Johns, Chef Sumant Vikas, Cremica Food Industries, Rishabh Sadana, Ritu Marya', '54:55', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2013, 'A', '2017-07-22 15:39:20', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2476, 'XKbpjFYy4GU', NULL, 'A Bite of West Innovation with Growth', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Restaurant business has always been an industry depending heavily on consumer preferences. As a restaurateur it becomes crucial to understand what a customer, of today and tomorrow, expects when he goes to eat out. Restaurant India 2017 (West Edition) was held on 4th March, 2017 at Hotel Westin, Pune. The theme of the summit was A Bite of West Innovation with Growth. The event involved restaurateurs from all over the West India as delegates. The Cheif Guests were Sh. Shivaji Desai,  Joint Commisioner, Food and Safety, Food and Drug Administration and Sh. Venkatesh Iyer, Co-founder and CEO, Goli Vada Pav. Mr. Desai briefed the conference about the Food & Safety Act whereas Mr. Iyer shared his experience establishing Goli Vada Pav as the only National QSR Food chain.', 'Restaurant India, Franchise India, A Bite of West Innovation, Sh. Shivaji Desai, Food and Safety, Sh. Venkatesh Iyer, Goli Vada Pav, QSR, Indian Food Chain, Ritu Marya, West India Restaurant\\r\\n\\r\\n', '52:54', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1680, 'A', '2017-07-24 16:10:02', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2477, 'anWbxeXDTNY', NULL, 'Meeting the Needs of the Evolving Consumer Trends and the Evolution', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Restaurant business has always been an industry depending heavily on consumer preferences. As a restaurateur it becomes crucial to understand what a customer, of today and tomorrow, expects when he goes to eat out. Restaurant India 2017 (West Edition) was held on 4th March, 2017 at Hotel Westin, Pune. The Panel includes Anurag Katriar, CEO DeGustibus Hospitality; Khodu Irani, Founder, High Spirits; Sahil Jain Co-founder, Dineout; Tanaya Sheralea, Director of Operations, Bellona Hospitality. The panel discussion gives some insights on Meeting the Needs of the Evolving Consumer Trends and the Evolution', 'Restaurant India, Franchise India, Evolving Consumer Trends, Anurag Katriar, DeGustibus Hospitality,  Khodu Irani, , High Spirits, Sahil Jain, Dineout, Tanaya Sheralea, Bellona Hospitality, Ritu Marya, West India Restaurant', '48:56', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1775, 'A', '2017-07-24 16:12:10', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2478, 'DYP52MSb8Mc', NULL, 'Capital Investors on Restaurant Business', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Restaurant business has always been heavily dependent on consumer preferences. As a restaurateur it becomes crucial to understand what a customer, of today and tomorrow, expects when he goes to eat out. Restaurant India 2017 (West Edition) was held on 4th March, 2017 at Hotel Westin, Pune.The Panel includesSriranjan Seshadri, Director, Gaja Capital Partners; Shri Pushkar Mishra, Deputy General Manager, SIDBI, Pune; Ashish Alexander, Leader; Swarup Beria, Principal, Omnivore Venture Partners. Master investors discuss and share what they think before investing in a gingery business like restaurants!', 'Restaurant India, Franchise India, Investment in Restaurant business, Sriranjan Seshadri, Gaja Capital Partners, Shri Pushkar Mishra,SIDBI, Ashish Alexander, Nishith Desai Association, Swarup Beria, Principal, Omnivore Venture Partners, Ritu Marya, West India Restaurant', '55:10', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1730, 'A', '2017-07-24 16:13:47', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2479, 'szI47ctOg6k', NULL, 'Keynote Presentation on Dineout', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Restaurant business has always been an industry depending heavily on consumer preferences. As a restaurateur it becomes crucial to understand what a customer, of today and tomorrow, expects when he goes to eat out. Restaurant India 2017 (West Edition) was held on 4th March, 2017 at Hotel Westin, Pune. Sahil Jain Co-founder, Dineout gives a keynote presentation on Dineout. A unique venture discovered totally based on consumers need!', 'Restaurant India, Franchise India, Dineout, Sahil Jain, Table booking, Dineout plus, Restaurant Services Optimization', '18:26', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1806, 'A', '2017-07-24 16:15:18', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2480, '7_YKeUDfPtM', NULL, 'How Social Media can Help Build Business', 7, '', NULL, '', 34, 'Avelo Roy is Managing Director at Kolkata Ventures. Talking at Restaurant India 2017, East, he shares how restaurant can build their business via social media. ', 'Restaurant Franchise, Restaurant India 2017, Food Investor, Social Media', '25:43', 'V', NULL, 'en', 3, 3, 15, 1473, 'A', '2017-07-27 17:19:30', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2481, 'uIz5l7IYrww', NULL, 'Future of Digital Finance', 1, '', NULL, '', 10, 'Technology has certainly changed the status quo for the financial world. With every other aspect of finance going online, it is crucial for us to adapt as quickly as possible. Moneytech summit 2017, organised by BusinessEx.com was held on 10th April, 2017 at JW Marriot Hotel, New Delhi. An eminent set of speakers pours out remarkable insights on Digital Economy. Mr V. Vaidyanathan, Founder & Chairman, Capital First and Mr. Dhiraj Nayyar, Officer on Special Duty & Head, Economics, Finance and Commerce, NITI Aayog, Government of India talk about The Future of Digital Finance. ', 'moneytech summit, Business Ex, franchiseindia, entrepreneur media, digital economy, finance, commerce, V. Vaidyanathan, Capital First, Dhiraj Nayyar, the future of digital finance', '37:43', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2168, 'A', '2017-08-04 16:11:42', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2482, 'xYVcBSmye1U', NULL, 'Inaugural Address', 1, '', NULL, '', 10, 'Technology has certainly changed the status quo for the financial world. With every other aspect of finance going online, it is crucial for us to adapt as quickly as possible. Moneytech summit 2017, organised by BusinessEx.com was held on 10th April, 2017 at JW Marriot Hotel, New Delhi. An eminent set of speakers pours out remarkable insights on Digital Economy. The chief guest for the event was Sh. Arjun Ram Meghwal, Union Minister of State in Finance. The event begins with an inaugural Address by Miss Ritu Marya, Editor in chief, Franchise India which is followed by an address by the chief guest.', 'moneytech summit, Business Ex, entrepreneur media, franchiseindia, entrepreneur, digital economy, finance, commerce,  Ritu Marya, Arjun Ram Meghwal ', '6:20', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2022, 'A', '2017-08-04 16:13:52', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2483, 'eHazbnf8M7I', NULL, 'Words of Encouragement', 1, '', NULL, '', 10, 'Technology has certainly changed the status quo for the financial world. With every other aspect of finance going online, it is crucial for us to adapt as quickly as possible. Moneytech summit 2017, organised by BusinessEx.com was held on 10th April, 2017 at JW Marriot Hotel, New Delhi. An eminent set of speakers pours out remarkable insights on Digital Economy. The chief guest for the event was Sh. Arjun Ram Meghwal, Union Minister of State in Finance. Honourable minister pours out words of encouragement for the young and dynamic Indian Entrepreneurs.', 'moneytech summit, Business Ex, entrepreneur media, franchiseindia, entrepreneur, digital economy, finance, commerce,  Ritu Marya, Arjun Ram Meghwal ', '9:11', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2156, 'A', '2017-08-04 16:17:25', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2484, 'Ear-r_ByhfI', NULL, 'Entrepreneur India 2017 ET now Promo', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'The largest annual Entrepreneur convention returned on July 18-19, 2017 at JW Marriott Hotel, Aerocity, New Delhi in its 7th Edition. Biggest names from the stakeholders of the industry graced the stage like Shri Amitabh Kant, Niti Ayog; Mr. Suresh Narayan, Nestle India; Mr. Bimal Jalan, Former Governor RBI; Padmashree Kiran Karnik, Author; Mr. Dilip Chhabria, DC Design; Mr. Satya Narayanan, Career Launcher; Mr. Ananya Birla, Swatantra Microfinance; Mr. Mahesh Gupta, Kent RO;  Mr. Bibop Gresta, Hyperloop Transportation Technology and many more. \\r\\n\\r\\nThis year, Entrepreneur India also brings together innovative start-ups to present their ideas in front of the esteemed set of investors who could help them scale up their start-up. The event that saw as many as 11 cutting-edge start-up ideas pitting against each other, among which, four start-ups were short-listed to present their idea on day-two of the convention.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe show concludes with Entrepreneur India 2017 Awards honouring the entrepreneurs with the highest rated entrepreneurship awards along with the silver service gala dinner. The biggest award of the evening went to the visionary Vijay Shekhar Sharma of Paytm as Entrepreneur of the Year. Many other successful entrepreneur were also awarded with the trophy in their respective field of entrepreneurship.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe grand event saw several successful entrepreneurs and big names from the industry attending and sharing their thoughts and insights on important topics. It opened many doors to opportunities for entrepreneurs as everyone got to learn something new and take with them essentials, which will push the industry to achieve a new milestone.\\r\\n\\r\\n', 'Entrepreneur India 2017, Entrepreneur Magazine, Entrepreneur Awards 2017, ET Now Promo, Shri Amitabh Kant, Industry Convention, Entrepreneur Conference, B2B Conference, B2B Awards, Entrepreneur Fraternity, Entrepreneurship\\r\\n\\r\\n', '0:45', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2870, 'A', '2017-08-04 16:19:56', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2485, 'ETWQA9XSxo4', NULL, 'Banking in 21st Century', 1, '', NULL, '', 10, 'Technology has certainly changed the status quo for the financial world. With every other aspect of finance going online, it is crucial for us to adapt as quickly as possible. Moneytech summit 2017, organised by BusinessEx.com was held on 10th April, 2017 at JW Marriot Hotel, New Delhi. Mr. Sibi Sebastian, CEO-Indian Operations, SBM Bank Mauritius & Mr. Sameer Garg, Vice President& Regional Head, New Economy Group, Corporate Banking, Axis Bank elucidate the forthcoming evolution in banking sector due to technology advances like Artificial Intelligence. A revolution similar to the computers revolution in the 90s is on its brim! ', 'moneytech summit, Business Ex, franchiseindia, entrepreneur media, banking in 21st century, Mr. Sibi Sebastian,SBM Bank Mauritius, Mr. Sameer Garg, Axis Bank, Ritu Marya', '1:02:23', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2103, 'A', '2017-08-04 16:52:11', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2486, '5PXTUmfLylI', NULL, 'Modern Credit & Lending Mechanisms', 1, '', NULL, '', 10, 'Technology has certainly changed the status quo for the financial world. With every other aspect of finance going online, it is crucial for us to adapt as quickly as possible. Moneytech summit 2017 was organised by BusinessEx.com was held on 10th April, 2017 at JW Marriot Hotel, New Delhi. Credit and lending is an important aspect of the banking industry. The above discussion is based on technologically driven Modern Credit & Lending Mechanisms. In the panel we have Mr. Naveen Kukreja, Co-founder & CEO, paisabazaar.com; Mr. Manish Khera, Founder & CEO, Arth Impact; Mr. Adhil Shetty, Founder & CEO, bankbazaar.com & Mr. Rahul Sankhlecha, Vice President, Lendingkart.', 'moneytech summit, Business Ex, franchiseindia, entrepreneur media, modern trends in credit and lending, technology driven banking, credit and lending mechanisms . Naveen Kukreja, paisabazaar, Mr. Manish Khera, Arth Impact, Mr. Adhil Shetty, bankbazaar.com , Mr. Rahul Sankhlecha, Lendingkart', '58:54', 'V', NULL, 'en', 2, 2, 10, 2666, 'A', '2017-08-04 16:56:31', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2487, '_jLeS6NvVLs', NULL, 'Entrepreneur India 2017 ET NOW Episode', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'The largest annual Entrepreneur convention returned on July 18-19, 2017 at JW Marriott Hotel, Aerocity, New Delhi in its 7th Edition. Biggest names from the stakeholders of the industry graced the stage like Shri Amitabh Kant, Niti Ayog; Mr. Suresh Narayan, Nestle India; Mr. Bimal Jalan, Former Governor RBI; Padmashree Kiran Karnik, Author; Mr. Dilip Chhabria, DC Design; Mr. Satya Narayanan, Career Launcher; Mr. Ananya Birla, Swatantra Microfinance; Mr. Mahesh Gupta, Kent RO;  Mr. Bibop Gresta, Hyperloop Transportation Technology and many more. \\r\\n\\r\\nThis year, Entrepreneur India also brings together innovative start-ups to present their ideas in front of the esteemed set of investors who could help them scale up their start-up. The event that saw as many as 11 cutting-edge start-up ideas pitting against each other, among which, four start-ups were short-listed to present their idea on day-two of the convention.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe show concludes with Entrepreneur India 2017 Awards honouring the entrepreneurs with the highest rated entrepreneurship awards along with the silver service gala dinner. The biggest award of the evening went to the visionary Vijay Shekhar Sharma of Paytm as Entrepreneur of the Year. Many other successful entrepreneur were also awarded with the trophy in their respective field of entrepreneurship.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe grand event saw several successful entrepreneurs and big names from the industry attending and sharing their thoughts and insights on important topics. It opened many doors to opportunities for entrepreneurs as everyone got to learn something new and take with them essentials, which will push the industry to achieve a new milestone.\\r\\n', 'Entrepreneur India 2017, Entrepreneur Magazine, Entrepreneur Awards 2017, ET Now Episode, Shri Amitabh Kant, Industry Convention, Entrepreneur Conference, B2B Conference, B2B Awards, Entrepreneur Fraternity, Entrepreneurship', '22:09', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3046, 'A', '2017-08-09 16:05:42', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2488, '3lNPaFoUlpk', NULL, 'From Start-up to Scale-up', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'Once you are done starting up, the next step is to Scale Up. Though most of the scaling-up is Technology based, there are yet some of the fundamental ground rules which are hard-core business. Mr. Ashok Soota, Founder & Executive Chairman, Happiest Minds discusses both these areas of scaling up in detail.\\r\\n BusinessEx.com presents Entrepreneur India Congress 2017 was held on 18-19th July, 2017 at JW Marriot Hotel, Aerocity, New Delhi. The event was the host to a large number of brainstorming sessions, panel discussions and key note presentations on Entrepreneurship and related issues.\\r\\n', 'BusinessEx.com, Entrepreneur India Congress 2017, BusinessEx, Entrepreneur India, Ashok Soota, Happiest Minds, Scale up, how to scale up your business, ', '38:25', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1134, 'A', '2017-08-09 16:37:48', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2489, '-Kc8lr4niUk', NULL, 'Hallmarks of an Innovator ', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, ' I think the essence of the seed was, you have to be fearless, says Mr. Dilip Chhabria, Indian car designer & Founder, DC Design. This is perhaps the utmost important quality in an entrepreneur, or an innovator. Ones passion for something cannot be less than obsession. BusinessEx.com presents Entrepreneur India Congress 2017 was held on 18-19th July, 2017 at JW Marriot Hotel, Aerocity, New Delhi. The event was the host to a large number of brainstorming sessions, panel discussions and key note presentations on Entrepreneurship and related issues.rnrn', 'BusinessEx.com, Entrepreneur India Congress 2017, BusinessEx, Entrepreneur India, qualities of an innovator, qualities of an entrepreneur, how to be an entrepreneur, Dilip Chhabria, DC Design', '30:36', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1488, 'A', '2017-08-09 16:39:46', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2490, 'fv9frleUGSc', NULL, 'Hyperloop: The Future Transport', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'Ideas of today are the realities of tomorrow. Transportation has been an important aspect in human life and so weve been continually innovating with wheel, steam engine, airplane and so on. Heres another idea which can totally change ourlives. It  is Elon Musks Hyperloop. Mr.\\\'Bibop\\\' Gabriele Gresta, co-founder & chairman, hyperloop technology, talks about the highly efficient yet feasible transportation technology.\\r\\n BusinessEx.com presents Entrepreneur India Congress 2017 was held on 18-19th July, 2017 at JW Marriot Hotel, Aerocity, New Delhi. The event was the host to a large number of brainstorming sessions, panel discussions and key note presentations on Entrepreneurship and related issues.\\r\\n', 'BusinessEx.com, Entrepreneur India Congress 2017, BusinessEx, Entrepreneur India, hyperloop, Bibop Gabriele Gresta, Elon Musk, Future Transport, Next Generation', '43:28', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1739, 'A', '2017-08-09 16:41:28', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2491, '7Zs37so2BMU', NULL, 'Family Ventures: The Investors view', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'The transition of the Indian preference from job to venture has begun. Though family business has been inherent in the typical Indian business space, India is still scratching the surface in the corporate-family concept with a very few players present in the category.  Mr. Rajmohan Krishnan Principal, Founder & Managing Director, Entrust Family Office Investment Advisors; Mr. Sumit Dhanuka, Venture Advisor, SAR Family Office - SAR Group Family Office and Angela De Giacomo, Investment Manager - Bissell Family Office & Founder, Wundernova, talk about the investment trends and triggers in family businesses.\\r\\n BusinessEx.com presents Entrepreneur India Congress 2017 was held on 18-19th July, 2017 at JW Marriot Hotel, Aerocity, New Delhi. The event was the host to a large number of brainstorming sessions, panel discussions and key note presentations on Entrepreneurship and related issues.\\r\\n\\r\\n', 'BusinessEx.com, Entrepreneur India Congress 2017, BusinessEx, Entrepreneur India, family business in India, family venture, Rajmohan Krishnan, , Entrust Family Office Investment Advisors, Sumit Dhanuka, SAR Group Family Office, Angela De Giacomo, Bissell Family Office & Founder', '39:46', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2124, 'A', '2017-08-09 16:45:26', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2492, 'bLXsDVChgOM', NULL, 'Disruption from the front line ', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'What are the ideas that are a moon shot? Can Robots and Humans co-exist in business? Is Blockchain the answer for a safer digital world? How the businesses can use or are using technologies like Augmented Reality, Virtual Reality, Artificial Intelligence and the Machine Learning technology? An Eminent set of panellists discuss how these technologies can bring the much awaited Disruption in the business space. The panel includes Dr Anne Kerr, Global Head, Cities Mott MacDonald Group; Aronin P, CEO and CO-founder of Sastra Robotics India; Srikanth Sundararajan, Partner, Ventureast; Tarun Mehta, Chief Executive Officer and Co-Founder, Ather Energy.\\r\\n BusinessEx.com presents Entrepreneur India Congress 2017 was held on 18-19th July, 2017 at JW Marriot Hotel, Aerocity, New Delhi. The event was the host to a large number of brainstorming sessions, panel discussions and key note presentations on Entrepreneurship and related issues.\\r\\n', 'BusinessEx.com, Entrepreneur India Congress 2017, BusinessEx, Entrepreneur India, Disruption in business,  new technologies,  Augmented Reality, Virtual Reality, Artificial Intelligence, Machine Learning technology, Blockchain, safer digital world,  Anne Kerr, Cities Mott MacDonald Group, Aronin P, Sastra Robotics India, Srikanth Sundararajan, Ventureast, Tarun Mehta, Ather Energy\\r\\n\\r\\n', '37:28', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1669, 'A', '2017-08-09 16:47:11', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0);
