(2493, 's-GWc74Y_fQ', NULL, 'Future of Work', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, ' BusinessEx.com presents Entrepreneur India Congress 2017 was held on 18-19th July, 2017 at JW Marriot Hotel, Aerocity, New Delhi. The event was the host to a large number of brainstorming sessions, panel discussions and key note presentations on Entrepreneurship and related issues.\\r\\nIn the Key-note presentation, Karan Virwani, Director at WeWork (India), discusses the concept of WeWork, the importance of doing what you love and adding meaning to the lives of working community.\\r\\n', 'BusinessEx.com, Entrepreneur India Congress 2017, BusinessEx, Entrepreneur India, Karan Virwani, WeWork, workplace innovation ', '18:00', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1252, 'A', '2017-08-09 16:48:37', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2494, 'hhad_e1tMn8', NULL, 'Game of Consumers', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'Mr. Mriganka Shome, Founder & CEO, Varenia CIMS, pours out some tips and strategies that a young entrepreneur has to keep in mind. Comparing the whole business space with the Game of Thrones series he says that the entrepreneur who learns to be customer-empathetic is the one who sirs om the Iron Throne\\r\\n BusinessEx.com presents Entrepreneur India Congress 2017 was held on 18-19th July, 2017 at JW Marriot Hotel, Aerocity, New Delhi. The event was the host to a large number of brainstorming sessions, panel discussions and key note presentations on Entrepreneurship and related issues.\\r\\n\\r\\n', 'BusinessEx.com, Entrepreneur India Congress 2017, BusinessEx, Entrepreneur India, Mriganka Shome,  Varenia, consumer-centric, consumer empathy', '36:53', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1404, 'A', '2017-08-09 16:50:03', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2495, '3jxRdi6s4c4', NULL, 'The Leader, The Entrepreneur', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'Description: BusinessEx.com presents Entrepreneur India Congress 2017 was held on 18-19th July, 2017 at JW Marriot Hotel, Aerocity, New Delhi. The event was the host to a large number of brainstorming sessions, panel discussions and key note presentations on Entrepreneurship and related issues.\\r\\nThis is a talk by a self-made leader, Managing Director and Chairman of Nestle India, Suresh Narayanan. Suresh discusses his own journey with Nestle and along with shares some golden lessons he learnt. These lessons are no less than diamonds to aspiring Entrepreneurs and leaders!\\r\\n', 'BusinessEx.com, Entrepreneur India Congress 2017, BusinessEx, Entrepreneur India, Suresh Narayanan, Nestle India, Lessons for Entrepreneurs, Lessons for Leaders, Maggi Crisis, Crisis Management in business', '31:26', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1136, 'A', '2017-08-09 16:51:34', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2496, 'IyDXu_VIhlk', NULL, 'Go Global ', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'BusinessEx.com presents Entrepreneur India Congress 2017 was held on 18-19th July, 2017 at JW Marriot Hotel, Aerocity, New Delhi. The event was the host to a large number of brainstorming sessions, panel discussions and key note presentations on Entrepreneurship and related issues. Above you will find the three of our visionary speakers and successful entrepreneurs sharing their experiences in taking their brand Global. The speakers include Mahesh Gupta Chairman & Managing Director, Kent RO Systems Ltd; Mr. Mahesh Lingareddy, Founder and Chairman, Smartron and Guilherme Mota, Country Manager, SalaryFits. \\r\\n\\r\\n', 'BusinessEx.com, Entrepreneur India Congress 2017, BusinessEx, Entrepreneur India, Franchise India,  going global, Mahesh, Gupta Chairman, Kent RO Systems Ltd, Mr. Mahesh Lingareddy, Smartron, Guilherme Mota, SalaryFits', '34:29', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1158, 'A', '2017-08-11 10:01:17', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2497, 'LZa9hLsyL9o', NULL, 'Innovation at the top', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'Innovation is the root of any great business. An innovative idea has the power of transforming and giving birth to a business. After all, it is neither the sword, nor the pen but the thought which is the mightiest! The speakers include Gajendra Chandel, Member of executive committee & CHRO, TATA Motors; Jagdish Mitra, Chief Strategy & Head of Growth Factories, Tech Mahindra;  Farid Talhame, Chief Innovation Culture Officer, Innovation Centre, Godrej & Boyce Mfg co. ltd\\r\\n\\r\\nBusinessEx.com presents Entrepreneur India Congress 2017 was held on 18-19th July, 2017 at JW Marriot Hotel, Aerocity, New Delhi. The event was the host to a large number of brainstorming sessions, panel discussions and key note presentations on Entrepreneurship and related issues.\\r\\n\\r\\n', 'BusinessEx.com, Entrepreneur India Congress 2017, BusinessEx, Entrepreneur India, Franchise India, Innoavtion in business, startup, Gajendra Chandel, TATA Motors, Jagdish Mitra, Tech Mahindra, Farid Talhame, Godrej & Boyce Mfg co. Ltd', '40:15', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1364, 'A', '2017-08-11 10:06:25', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2498, 'ewysh6in5Sc', NULL, 'Wheres the Money', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'BusinessEx.com presents Entrepreneur India Congress 2017 was held on 18-19th July, 2017 at JW Marriot Hotel, Aerocity, New Delhi. The event was the host to a large number of brainstorming sessions, panel discussions and key note presentations on Entrepreneurship and related issues.\\r\\nAbove is a group of successful and learned investors discussing on where they would actually like to invest. The panel includes Mr. Rahul Chandra, Co-Founder and Managing Director, Helion Venture Partners; Mr. Parag Dhol, Managing Director, Inventus Capital Partners; Ms. Ruchira Shukla, Regional Lead, South Asia, Venture Capital, IFC; Mr. Tarun Davda, Managing Director, Matrix Partners India; Mr. Vineet Rai, Founder, Aavishkaar Intellecap Group\\r\\n', 'BusinessEx.com, Entrepreneur India Congress 2017, BusinessEx, Entrepreneur India, Franchise India, Rahul Chandra, Helion Venture Partners, Parag Dhol, Inventus Capital Partners, Ruchira Shukla,  IFC, Tarun Davda, Mayrix Partners,  Vineet Rai, Aavishkaar Intellecap Group', '01:08:42', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1769, 'A', '2017-08-11 10:07:56', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2499, 'f5uVWyApnCY', NULL, 'Startups & Investors', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'BusinessEx.com presents Entrepreneur India Congress 2017 was held on 18-19th July, 2017 at JW Marriot Hotel, Aerocity, New Delhi. The event was the host to a large number of brainstorming sessions, panel discussions and key note presentations on Entrepreneurship and related issues. Startups put up their business plans and ideas in front of investors and answer their queries so as to fetch the gold coins! We have Mr. Rishi Kumar, Founder, Groctaurant; Arunabh SInha, Founder, UClean; Baljeet Singh & Naresh G from Elogi with their business plans and ideas.', 'BusinessEx.com, Entrepreneur India Congress 2017, BusinessEx, Entrepreneur India, Franchise India, innovative indian start-ups, how to get investors, Rishi Kumar, Groctaurant, Arunabh Sinha, UClean, Baljeet Singh, Naresh G, Elogi.', '46:37', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1895, 'A', '2017-08-11 10:09:41', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2500, 'o2_luGoOjRo', NULL, 'Think G-Local', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'BusinessEx.com presents Entrepreneur India Congress 2017 was held on 18-19th July, 2017 at JW Marriot Hotel, Aerocity, New Delhi. The event was the host to a large number of brainstorming sessions, panel discussions and key note presentations on Entrepreneurship and related issues. The markets thought process has very well reached the idea of making an international globalised presence. But once you reach in a region, knowing your audience is equally crucial and that involves  knowing the local taste. Hence the term Glocalisation. Ambarish Mitra, Founder & CEO, Blippar, talks about his venture going Glocal!', 'BusinessEx.com, Entrepreneur India Congress 2017, BusinessEx, Entrepreneur India, Franchise India, glocal, market research, knowing your audience, Ambarish Mitra, Blippar\\r\\n\\r\\n', '28:37', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1271, 'A', '2017-08-11 16:47:07', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2501, 's9T_Qal-glE', NULL, 'Win-Win Culture', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'BusinessEx.com presents Entrepreneur India Congress 2017 was held on 18-19th July, 2017 at JW Marriot Hotel, Aerocity, New Delhi. The event was the host to a large number of brainstorming sessions, panel discussions and key note presentations on Entrepreneurship and related issues. Above is a talk by Mr. Dr. Finn Majlergaard, Professor - Global Leadership Expert - Keynote Speaker /Workshop Facilitator - Author - Post-merger integration expert; shares with us the importance and advantages of the Win-Win Culture.\\r\\n\\r\\n', 'BusinessEx.com, Entrepreneur India Congress 2017, BusinessEx, Entrepreneur India, Franchise India, Finn Mallergaard, Win-Winn Culture', '14:18', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1232, 'A', '2017-08-11 16:49:03', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2502, 'iYgMMPvsWgg', NULL, 'Banking & Alternative Lending', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'BusinessEx.com presents Entrepreneur India Congress 2017 was held on 18-19th July, 2017 at JW Marriot Hotel, Aerocity, New Delhi. The event was the host to a large number of brainstorming sessions, panel discussions and key note presentations on Entrepreneurship and related issues.  The panel above discuses the trends in banking and the scope of alternative lending in context of entrepreneurship. In the panel we have  Mr. Chet Jain, Founder, Crowdera; Mr. Rishi Kohli, Managing Director, Pro-Alpha Systematic Capital; Mr. Sanjay Chamria, Vice Chairman & Managing Director, Magma Fincorp Ltd; Shri. S.P. Singh, General Manager, SIDBI', 'BusinessEx.com, Entrepreneur India Congress 2017, BusinessEx, Entrepreneur India, Franchise India, banking, alternative lending, Ashika Jain', '26:50', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1399, 'A', '2017-08-11 16:51:03', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2503, 'aM7EchRIEqQ', NULL, 'What makes India unique?', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'BusinessEx.com presents Entrepreneur India Congress 2017 was held on 18-19th July, 2017 at JW Marriot Hotel, Aerocity, New Delhi. The event was the host to a large number of brainstorming sessions, panel discussions and key note presentations on Entrepreneurship and related issues.  Japan is known for teamwork, Germany for Precision and America for Marketing. But what is it which makes India unique and important? According to Mr. Arvind Varchaswi, Managing Director, Sriveda Sattva Pvt. Ltd., it is the countrys Spiritualism which makes India unique. Hence going back to our roots is crucial.\\r\\n\\r\\n', 'BusinessEx.com, Entrepreneur India Congress 2017, BusinessEx, Entrepreneur India, Franchise India,  Arvind Varchaswi, Sriveda Sattva, India & Spiritualism', '38:32', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1630, 'A', '2017-08-11 16:56:42', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2504, 'P_W-fyTnlAk', NULL, 'Design Thinking in Business', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'BusinessEx.com presents Entrepreneur India Congress 2017 was held on 18-19th July, 2017 at JW Marriot Hotel, Aerocity, New Delhi. The event was the host to a large number of brainstorming sessions, panel discussions and key note presentations on Entrepreneurship and related issues. Design has been an ever important component in manufacturing. Now with the advent of Make in India campaign, design has gained even more importance. Viraj Kalyani, Founder and Chairman, Kalyani Studio talks about the importance of design in creating true innovation. He shares the significance of putting user experience at the heart of design.\\r\\n\\r\\n', 'BusinessEx.com, Entrepreneur India Congress 2017, BusinessEx, Entrepreneur India, Franchise India, Viraj Kalyani, Kalyani Studio, Design Thinking, Importance of design', '15:27', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1288, 'A', '2017-08-11 16:58:00', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2505, 'MtQ1YEo58bg', NULL, ' Disruption through Digital Innovation', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'BusinessEx.com presents Entrepreneur India Congress 2017 was held on 18-19th July, 2017 at JW Marriot Hotel, Aerocity, New Delhi. The event was the host to a large number of brainstorming sessions, panel discussions and key note presentations on Entrepreneurship and related issues. Mr. Rana Kapoor, Managing Director & CEO, Yes Bank, talks about perhaps the greatest of the technological advances of the decade, Digital innovation and how can it cause disruption.', 'BusinessEx.com, Entrepreneur India Congress 2017, BusinessEx, Entrepreneur India, Franchise India,  Rana Kapoor, Yes Bank, Digital, Digital innovation, Digital Marketing, Digital disruption', '24:56', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1010, 'A', '2017-08-11 16:59:37', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
