(2600, 'HMK771hf9nA', NULL, 'Franchise India 2017 (Times Now Promo)', 1, '', NULL, '', 13, 'The Franchise India 2017 held at Pragati Maidan on 7th & 8th November, 2017- the biggest ever franchise networking and knowledge sharing platform in Asia, saw entrepreneurs in franchising space, who were on a lookout primarily to buy and sell business opportunities, as well as exchange ideas, knowledge, technologies and services to enhance their businesses potentials, prospects and profitability. Arguably Indias biggest such platform, it has over 500 leading Indian and international business and consumer brands exhibiting their products for over 43000 business investors offering a vast range of franchise opportunities. Along with the exhibition, there were 2 parallel conferences as Opportunity Summit 2017 & Brand Licensing Conference 2017. Thousands of prospective business owners and entrepreneurs from throughout India and 11 countries across the globe got opportunity to meet top franchise brands.\\r\\n\\r\\nOn the second day i.e. 7th November 2017, Franchise Awards 2017 & Star Retailer Awards 2017 also took place in Hotel Lalit, Connaught Place, Delhi. The Awards are considered to be one of the most prestigious awards that recognize Excellence in Performance in Retail as well as franchising space. The award ceremony was aimed at felicitating people who have contributed towards the growth of Retail & Franchise Industry in India.\\r\\n', 'Franchise India 2017, Opportunity Summit 2017, Brand Licensing conference 2017, Star Retailer Awards, Franchise Awards, Franchising Exhibition, Biggest Franchise Expo, Retail Awards, Vivek Oberoi, Times Now, Industry Convention, B2B Retail Convention Franchising Exhibition, Industry Awards, Mahesh Bhupati, Lara Dutta, Industry Expo', '0:33', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1305, 'A', '2018-02-23 13:28:31', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2601, '7L56mrsaLLU', NULL, 'STARTUP 2018 (ZEE Business Full Episode)', 1, '', NULL, '', 13, 'Indias biggest startup and entrepreneurship carnival, Startup 2018, was held on January 22, 2018 at IIT Delhi. Organized by Entrepreneur & Franchise India, Startup 2018 proved to be the platform where one found inspiration to start their own startup, indulged in competition amongst peers, and got recognition for one\\\'s efforts as an entrepreneur. The event comprised of 3 parts &quot; Founders Summit, Startup Superhero Hunt & Entrepreneur Startup Awards 2018. The Founders Summit had celebrated entrepreneurs such as Mr. Sanjeev Bhikchandani (Exec. VC, Info Edge India), Mr. Rahul Sharma (Co-founder Micromax Informatics Ltd.), Mr. Habil Khorakiwala (Founder Chairman, Wockhardt Group) and many others delivering inspiring addresses. The Startup Superhero hunt, a competition that had gone to 10 cities, and had gotten participation from over 10,000 startups, reached its culmination when the winner was announced at the Startup 2018. Superstar Akshay Kumar, who was present at the event crowned the champion. The Entrepreneur Startup Awards saw the presence of a bevy of startup heavyweights who were honoured for the achievements.', 'Startup 2018, Akshay Kumar, Padman, Ritu Marya, Franchise India ', '21:35', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1681, 'A', '2018-02-23 13:32:03', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2602, 'naVEWm6V_WU', NULL, 'Estate Awards 2018 (ET Now Promo)', 3, '', NULL, '', 21, 'After 9 prestigious Editions, Remax India & Franchise India in media partnership with ET NOW proudly presented Asias Biggest Real Estate Awards- 10th Estate Awards on 27th January at Hotel JW Marriott, New Delhi.\\r\\n\\r\\nThere were Indeed Marvellous Group of People, Individuals, Teams And Brands Behind Every Mega Structure And Beautiful Habitat Being Developed To Make The World A Better Place To Co-Exist. And To Honour Those Supremely Talented People, We Bring To You The 10th Estate Awards 2018, Where This Year\\\'s Line-Up saw The Stalwarts And Emerging Names On The Podium Rubbing Shoulders With Fame. \\r\\n\\r\\nEach year Awards attracted around 300 industry members including Developers, Builders and Real Estate professionals from various industry sectors such as law, finance, construction, development, brokerage and appraisal. The platform offers a great opportunity for delegates to not only gain new insights about what the future holds for Real Estate, in the region and beyond , but also, to build new relationships and seek new opportunities in the Real Estate industry.\\r\\n\\r\\nFrom last year along with Estate Awards, Hotel & Resorts Award and Design & Architect awards also got introduced which got the overwhelming response from the respective industry in the second edition too.\\r\\n', 'Estate Awards, Hotel & Resort Awards, Design & Architect Awards, ET Now Promo, Estate Industry Awards, Estate Fraternity, B2B Awards, Franchise India Estate, Home & Residential Awards, Commercial & Retail Awards', '0:50', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2774, 'A', '2018-03-01 14:13:09', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2603, 've1i318j_fA', NULL, 'Women to Watch in 2018', 2, '', NULL, '', 15, 'Entrepreneur Media is back with its annual Shepreneus: Women to Watch edition. It features women visionaries, who are changing India one spirited woman one step at a time. Women, who have empowered an enterprise either solely of by inheritance or as co-founder. Featuring women like Neerja Birla who have given mid-age Indian women a reason to believe that just because you have not worked for a certain time of your life, does not mean that you cannot do it ever. It is never too late to start something. This March get inspired by women power. ', 'entrepreneur, woman entrepreneur, shepreneur, Neeti mohan, masaba gupta, bala deshpande, jyotsna suri, neerja Birla, schuana chauhan', '0:54', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 747, 'A', '2018-03-06 19:09:05', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2604, 'o4Cqsds0LUY', NULL, 'Small Business Awards 2018 (Times Now Promo)', 6, '', NULL, '', 30, 'To recognize the efforts of SMEs and SMB, Franchise India organized Small Business Awards 2018 on 14th February at Hotel JW Marriott, New Delhi which is a glorious opportunity for the businesses to get countrywide acclaim and recognition. It is considered as the most coveted awards show complementing the league\\\'s best across SMEs, SMB and new and emerging small scale ventures. After an insightful deliberation through intuitive illustration at the Entrepreneur 35Under35 special issue also get launched. As many as 44 SME and SMB entrepreneurs were awarded at the event.', 'Small Business Awards 2018, Business Awards, National Awards, Awards 2018, 35 under 35 Awards, Young Entrepreneurs Awards, Biggest Small Business Awards', '0:20', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 3200, 'A', '2018-03-06 19:27:22', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2605, 'tFQdefO7w2g', NULL, 'Indian Education Congress & Awards 2018 Promo on Times Now', 8, '', NULL, '', 38, 'Indian Education Congress 2018, Indias biggest  thought leadership platform on Education industry was held on February 13-14, 2018. Organized by Franchise India to showcase a product or service in the education space, suppliers and allied industries. This national event was a grand success with over 400 successful educationists, school & college principals, manufacturers, industry veterans, key suppliers, consultants and individuals belonging to the Education category attended the event from across the country. The conference talked about all aspects of Education sector in India and provided a direct B2B engagement to many Indian leading educationists and an understanding around how they are re-writing and implementing new retail practices over traditional ones.\\r\\n\\r\\nAlong with the Congress, Annual Indian Education Awards 2018 were also took place. The Awards are considered to be one of the most prestigious awards that recognize Excellence in Performance in Education space. The award ceremony was aimed at felicitating people who have contributed towards the growth of Education Industry in India. From Achievers, Innovators to Suppliers, the awards applauded their efforts in making the Education presence felt in this increasingly competitive world.\\r\\n', 'Indian Education Congress 2018, Indian Education Awards 2018, Times Now, Indian Education Congress Promo, Education Convention, Education Industry conference, Indian Education exhibition, Times Now Promo, Business Conference, Education Summit', '0:31', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2534, 'A', '2018-03-06 19:29:46', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
