(2615, 'i2pIN5VTsP4', NULL, 'Suresh Narayanan, CMD, Nestle India on how FMCG and retail can work together for better customer service', 5, '', NULL, '', 27, 'FMCG and retail have one common goal &quot; to ensure a happy customer. With growing dominance of ecommerce, the FMCG firms have built a great understanding of how to look at consumers and consumer trends in the medium to long term while retailers have often been short of strategic thinking because its all about the here and now in retail. In conversation with Retailer Media, Suresh Narayanan, CMD, Nestle India shares his thoughts on how FMCG and retail can work together to achieve this goal.', 'Suresh Narayanan, Nestle India, FMCG, Retail, Retailer Media', '1:13', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 2411, 'A', '2018-03-13 14:42:14', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
