(2621, 'ZyiiZ-vDPV8', NULL, 'Franchise India 2017 (Times Now Episode)', 1, '', NULL, '', 13, 'The Franchise India 2017 held at Pragati Maidan on 7th & 8th November, 2017- the biggest ever franchise networking and knowledge sharing platform in Asia, saw entrepreneurs in franchising space, who were on a lookout primarily to buy and sell business opportunities, as well as exchange ideas, knowledge, technologies and services to enhance their businesses potentials, prospects and profitability. Arguably Indias biggest such platform, it has over 500 leading Indian and international business and consumer brands exhibiting their products for over 43000 business investors offering a vast range of franchise opportunities. Along with the exhibition, there were 2 parallel conferences as Opportunity Summit 2017 & Brand Licensing Conference 2017. Thousands of prospective business owners and entrepreneurs from throughout India and 11 countries across the globe got opportunity to meet top franchise brands.rnrnOn the second day i.e. 7th November 2017, Franchise Awards 2017 & Star Retailer Awards 2017 also took place in Hotel Lalit, Connaught Place, Delhi. The Awards are considered to be one of the most prestigious awards that recognize Excellence in Performance in Retail as well as franchising space. The award ceremony was aimed at felicitating people who have contributed towards the growth of Retail & Franchise Industry in India.rnrn', 'Franchise India 2017, Opportunity Summit 2017, Brand Licensing conference 2017, Star Retailer Awards, Franchise Awards, Franchising Exhibition, Biggest Franchise Expo, Retail Awards, Vivek Oberoi, Times Now, Industry Convention, B2B Retail Convention Franchising Exhibition, Industry Awards, Mahesh Bhupati, Lara Dutta, Industry Expo', '13:47', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 1612, 'A', '2018-03-17 14:55:18', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
