(2793, 'FwbT02NVvZM', NULL, 'Entrepreneur 2018 Zee Business Promo', 2, '', NULL, '', 14, 'The largest annual Entrepreneur convention held on July 16-17, 2018 at JW Marriott Hotel, Aerocity, New Delhi in its 8th Edition. Biggest names from the stakeholders of the industry graced the stage like Chief Guest C.R.Chaudhary, Honble MoS for Commerce & Industry, GOI; Manish Sisodia, Deputy CM, Delhi; Neerja Birla, Founder and Chairperson, Mpower; Ritesh Agarwal, Founder & CEO, OYO Rooms; Anand Ahuja, Founder, and CEO, Bhane; Tushar Chhabra, CEO  & Co-Founder, Cron Systems; Naina Lal Kidwai, former country head of HSBC India, Chairman of the India Advisory Board of Advent International Private Equity & Author and many more. \\r\\n\\r\\nThis year, Entrepreneur India also brings together innovative start-ups to present their ideas in front of the esteemed set of investors who could help them scale up their start-up. The event that saw as many as 11 cutting-edge start-up ideas pitting against each other, among which, three start-ups were short-listed to present their idea on day-two of the convention.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe show concludes with Entrepreneur Awards 2018 honouring the entrepreneurs with the highest rated entrepreneurship awards along with the silver service gala dinner. Among the few awardees were Anand Ahuja, Founder, and CEO, Bhane; YES BANK MD & CEO Rana Kapoor; Stand-up comedian Amit Tandon and Keshav Bansal, Director of Intex Technologies. The huge gathering of guests cheered and applauded the awardees. Many other successful entrepreneur were also awarded with the trophy in their respective field of entrepreneurship.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe grand event saw several successful entrepreneurs and big names from the industry attending and sharing their thoughts and insights on important topics. It opened many doors to opportunities for entrepreneurs as everyone got to learn something new and take with them essentials, which will push the industry to achieve a new milestone.\\r\\n', 'Entrepreneur 2018, Entrepreneur Magazine, Entrepreneur Awards 2018, Zee Business Promo, Industry Convention, Entrepreneur Conference, B2B Conference, B2B Awards, Entrepreneur Fraternity, Entrepreneurship, Startup Convention,  Startup Awards, Investors.', '0.30', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 615, 'A', '2018-08-09 09:56:28', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0),
