(3311, '1L-kk5WfeF8', NULL, 'PICASSO Theory of Franchising | Gaurav Marya | Franchise India', 1, '', NULL, '', 0, '<p>Franchise Guru Mr. Gaurav Marya reveals Picasso Theory of Franchising where PICASSO stands for P - Proof of Concern, I - Innovations, C - Capital, A - Accountability, S - Sustainability, S - Scalability, O - Ownership. Watch &amp; Stay Tuned for more such Business Content.</p>', '', '3:30', 'V', NULL, 'en', 0, 0, 0, 69, 'A', '2023-10-05 15:30:00', '2023-10-26 09:01:50', '2023-10-26 09:01:50', 0, 0, 0, 0),
